\id 2CH
\h 2 Imezruyen
\toc1 2 Imezruyen
\toc2 2 Imezruyen
\toc3 2 Im.
\mt1 2 Imezruyen
\c 1
\s1 Tutra n Suliman - Aḍhar amezwaru n SIDI i Suliman
\m 
\v 1 Suliman, mmis n Dawud, ittwaḍmen di tgelda nnes, minzi SIDI, AREBBI nnes, tuɣa-t akides uca yarni di řemɣaret nnes ař ṭṭarf. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt [1 Ij. 3:1-15]\x*
\v 2 Suliman issiweř ak-d marra Israil, ak-d imeqqranen x wařef u x mya, ak-d řquḍat u ak-d marra řḥukkam n marra Israil, izeǧifen x ibabaten \add n řaǧat\add*.
\v 3 Nitni ṭṭfen abrid, Suliman d marra agraw \add n řgens\add* akides, ɣar řgeɛɛdet nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar Jibɛun, minzi dinni i tuɣa Aqiḍun n Umsagar n AREBBI i igga Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, di řexřa.
\v 4 Maca Dawud yiwi Ttabut n AREBBI zi Qaryat-Yaɛarim \add ɣar wemcan\add* i dd as issewjed Dawud, minzi netta iwta ijj n uqiḍun i \add Ttabut\add* di Urcalim.
\v 5 Aɛalṭar n nnḥas nni igga Baṣaliyil, mmis n Uri, mmis n Ḥur, \add tuɣa\add* din \add di Jibɛun\add* zzat i Uqiḍun n Umsagar n SIDI. Suliman yuyur din \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra agraw \add n řgens\add*
\v 6 uca iqeddem din Suliman, zzat i wudem n SIDI, ict n tɣarṣt x uɛalṭar n nnḥas nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar. Netta iqeddem xas ařef n tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ.
\m 
\v 7 Di ǧiřet nni, iban-dd AREBBI i Suliman, inna as: “Ttar min \add texsed\add* ad ac \add t\add* wceɣ!”
\v 8 Suliman inna i AREBBI: “Cek tessecned i baba Dawud tamexsiwt \add nnec\add* icewwaren u teggid ayi d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* SIDI AREBBI, ejj ad iffeɣ wawař nnec i tessiwřed ak-d baba Dawud s tidett, minzi teggid ayi d ajeǧid x ijj n řgens iwseɛ am tɛejjajt n temmurt.
\v 10 Ewc ayi řexxu tiɣit d tussna, ḥima ad ffɣeɣ u ad dd-dewřeɣ zzat i wudem n řgens-a \add am řḥakem nsen\add*, minzi wi izemmaren ad iḥkem x řgens-a ameqqran s řḥeqq?”
\b
\m 
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna AREBBI i Suliman: “Minzi aya ɣarek deg wuř u minzi cek war tᵉttared agřa, řeksibet niɣ ccan niɣ tudart n yinni i cek icarrhen, u war tᵉttared tudart tazirart, maca minzi tᵉttared tiɣit d tussna ḥima ad tgewwded řgens inu s řḥeqq, i wenni umi xef ggiɣ cek d ajeǧid,
\v 12 aqa temmewc ac \add řexxu\add* tiɣit d tussna, u ad ac wceɣ ɛawed agřa d řeksibet d ccan am mammec war \add ten\add* iṭṭif uřa d ijj n ujeǧid qbeř nnec u war \add ten\add* ttᵉṭṭifen \add ɛad ammu\add* awarni ac.
\b
\s1 Afeyyeḍ n wagřa n Suliman
\m 
\v 13 Zi řgeɛɛdet \add i x ttnuman ttwehhben tiɣarṣa\add*, \add řgeɛɛdet\add* nni \add iǧan\add* di Jibɛun arendad n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, yiweḍ-dd Suliman \add ɣar\add* Urcalim uca iḥkem x Israil. \x ◘ \xo 1:13 \xt [1 Ij. 10:26-29]\x*
\v 14 Suliman issmun ikarruten d imnayen. Netta tuɣa ɣares ařef u-arebɛa-mya n ikarruten d tenɛac-ařef n imnayen uca yiwyi ten ɣar tneddam n ikarruten u ɣar ujeǧid di Urcalim.
\v 15 Ajeǧid igga nnuqart di Urcalim anect n yeẓra \add nni tuɣa din iǧan\add* uca igga ticejjura n tengelt anect izemmuren nni \add tuɣa din iǧan\add* di Temmurt Iwaṭan s waṭṭas.
\v 16 Iwyen-dd iysan i Suliman zi Miṣra, zi Qiwi. Isebbaben n ujeǧid iwyen ten s yijj n ttaman \add imetnen\add* zi Qiwi.
\v 17 Iwyen-dd ijj n ukarru uca ssuffɣen t-i-dd zi Miṣra s \add ijj n ttaman n\add* setta-mya \add ciqlu\add* n nnuqart u ijj n uyis s mya u-xemsin \add ciqlu\add*. Ammu i ssuffɣen ten s ufus nsen i marra ijeǧiden n Iḥittiyyen u i ijeǧiden n Aram.
\v 18 Suliman yumur, ḥima ad tᵉttwabna ict n Taddart i Yisem n SIDI d ict n taddart i tgelda nnes.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Asewjed i řebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 Suliman iḥseb sebɛin-ařef n yeryazen i trebbut n řehmeř d tmenyin-ařef n yeryazen ḥima ad xeddmen am yisuydayen x idurar uřa d třata-ařaf u setta-mya n yinni xasen \add iǧan\add* d iweqqafen. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt [1 Ij. 5:15-32]\x*
\v 2 Xenni issekk Suliman \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar Ḥiram, ajeǧid n Ṣur, inna: “\add Egg akidi\add* am mammec teggid ak-d baba Dawud, tessekked ɣares akeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt maḥend ad ibna taddart i yixef nnes ḥima ad dayes izdeɣ.
\v 3 Xzar, necc xseɣ ad bniɣ ict n Taddart i Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI inu, ḥima ad as tt ssqeddseɣ, ḥima ad ssbexxareɣ \add din\add* řebxur ittfuḥen zzat i wudem nnes, u ḥima ad \add din\add* ssarseɣ řebda \add aɣrum n wescan\add* u ḥima \add ad din qeddmeɣ\add* tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ, ɣar tuffut u ɣar tmeddit, deg wussan n ssebt, deg wussan n uyur n jdid u di řeɛyudat ittwaggen n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ. D man aya \add ittwagg\add* x Israil i řebda.
\m 
\v 4 Taddart i ɣa bniɣ, ad tiři d tameqqrant, maɣar AREBBI nneɣ d ameqqran x marra irebbiten.
\v 5 Man wen i ɣar teǧa tzemmar ad as ibna ict n Taddart? Aqa ajenna, \add wah,\add* ajenna n ijenwan, war izemmar ad t iksi! U min ɛniɣ necc, aqa necc ad as bniɣ ict n Taddart mɣir ḥima ad as ssbexxareɣ zzat i wudem nnes?
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, sekk ayi-dd ijj n weryaz i izemmar ad ixdem s wureɣ d nnuqart d nnḥas d wuzzař uřa s \add ufiřu\add* adeḥmi d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d udehmani, ijj n weryaz i issen ad igg inqacen, \add wah, sekk i-t jmiɛ\add* ak-d imiɣisen nni ɣari di Yahuda u di Urcalim, inni dd-yiwi baba Dawud.
\v 7 Siweḍ ayi-dd uřa d akeccuḍ \add n tcejjart\add* n tengelt d umerzi d ukeccuḍ \add n tcejjart\add* n ṣandel azeggʷaɣ, minzi necc ssneɣ, aqa imsexxaren nnec ttḥakan deg unezdam n tcejjura n Lubnan, u xzar, imsexxaren inu \add ad wcen afus\add* i imsexxaren nnec, \f ◼ \fr 2:7 \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\v 8 maḥend ad ayi sswejden marra akeccuḍ \add nni\add*, maɣar Taddart nni i ɣa bniɣ, ad tiři d tameqqrant d řeɛjeb.
\v 9 Xzar, necc ad wceɣ i imsexxaren nnec, zeɛma i inezdamen nni izeddmen ticejjura, ɛicrin-ařef \add n řqedd\add* n ukuru n yirden d ɛicrin-ařef \add n řqedd n\add* ukuru n imendi d ɛicrin-ařef \add n řqedd\add* n ubatu n binu d ɛicrin-ařef \add n řqedd\add* n ubatu n zzect.” \f ◼ \fr 2:9 \fk abatu\ft - ijj n ‘ubatu’ ɛraḥař 20 niɣ 40 litru.\f*
\m 
\v 10 Ḥiram, ajeǧid n Ṣur, yarra-dd s tira uca issekk \add tabrat-a\add* ɣar Suliman: “Maɣar SIDI ittexs řgens nnes, igga cek d ajeǧid xasen.”
\v 11 Uca \add xenni\add* inna Ḥiram: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, wenni iggin ajenna d temmurt, aqa Netta iwca i Dawud ijj n uḥenjir d amiɣis, \add wenni\add* ɣar teǧa řefhamet d řeɛqeř, wenni i ɣa ibnan ict n Taddart i SIDI uřa d ict n taddart i tgelda nnes!
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* řexxu ad ssekkeɣ ijj n weryaz d amiɣis zi baba Ḥiram, wenni ɣar teǧa tussna d řefhamet,
\m 
\v 13 mmis n ict n temɣart zeg yessis n Dan. Babas d ijj n weryaz zi Ṣur wenni ɣar iǧa tussna ḥima ad ixdem s wureɣ, nnuqart, nnḥas, uzzař u s weẓru d ukeccuḍ, s \add ufiřu\add* arjuwani d udehmani, s řeqṭen azdad u s \add ufiřu\add* azeggʷaɣ iḥedqen, ḥima ad inqec ɛřam kuř ineqqacen, u ḥima ad yarcem ɛřam kuř ireqqamen nni d as immewcen, \add u man aya jmiɛ\add* ak-d imiɣisen nnec d imiɣisen n babac Dawud.
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ad issekk sidi inu irden d imendi d zzect d binu, min xef tuɣa issawař, ɣar imsexxaren nnes.
\v 15 Neccin ad nezdem ticejjura n Lubnan anect i d ac ittxeṣṣan uca ad ac tent i-dd-nawi x tɣarruba n tḥenya x řebḥar ɣar Yafa, u cek s yixef nnec ad tent tessgeɛɛded \add ssenni\add* ɣar Urcalim.”
\v 16 Suliman iḥseb marra iryazen ibarraniyyen nni \add iǧan\add* di temmurt n Israil, awarni i řeḥsab umi ten iḥseb babas Dawud. Ufin \add aqa din\add* mya u-třata u-xemsin-ařef u-setta mya \add n yeryazen\add*.
\m 
\v 17 Sebɛin-ařef zzaysen igga i-ten d imsexxaren i trebbut n řehmeř u tmenyin-ařef d isuydayen x idurar d setta u-třatin-mya \add igga\add* i-ten d iweqqafen ḥima ad ggen řgens ad ixdem.
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Řebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 Suliman ibda řebni n Taddart n SIDI di Urcalim x wedrar n Muriya, mani dd-iban \add SIDI\add* i babas Dawud \add u\add* mani issewjed Dawud ijj n wemcan x unedrar n Uyabusi Urnan. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt [1 Ij. 6:1-38; 7:13-51]\x*
\v 2 Netta ibda řebni deg uyur wiss tnayen, deg wass wiss tnayen deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n tgelda nnes.
\v 3 Wanita d dsas \add i issars\add* Suliman i řebni n Taddart n AREBBI: tuzzeggart \add nnes\add* deg iɣaǧen ɛlaḥsab řeqyas amezwaru \add tuɣa-tt\add* settin n iɣaǧen, d tiru \add nnes\add* \add tuɣa-t\add* ɛicrin n iɣaǧen.
\v 4 Asqif n wadaf, nni \add tuɣa iǧan\add* ɣar zzat n tuzzeggart \add n Taddart\add*, \add tuɣa-t\add* dayes ɛicrin n iɣaǧen \add umi t ɛebbaren\add* ɣar zzat n tiru n Taddart, u řuɛřa \add nnes\add* tuɣa-t dayes mya u-ɛicrin n iɣaǧen. Tuɣa idřa \add wesqif n wadaf\add* ɣar daxeř s wureɣ iṣfan.
\v 5 Taddart tameqqrant igga as taẓeqqa s ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* umerzi uca yarni xas wureɣ iṣfan u izewweq i-t s tcejjura n tini d ssnaseř \add izewwqen\add*. \f ◼ \fr 3:5 \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\v 6 Ɛawed izewweq netta Taddart s yiẓra iɣřan. Ureɣ tuɣa d ureɣ zi Farawayim.
\v 7 Ammu i idřa netta Taddart, tiḥenya, tinebdatin, řeḥyuḍ nnes d tewwura nnes s wureɣ, uca inqec ikiruben di řeḥyuḍ. \f ◼ \fr 3:7 \fk ikiruben\ft - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*
\m 
\v 8 Netta igga uřa d axxam n Weqdas x Uqeddas. Tuzzeggart nnes dayes ɛicrin n iɣaǧen \add umi t ɛebbaren\add* ɣar zzat n tiru n Taddart. Uřa d tiru nnes \add tuɣa-t dayes\add* ɛicrin n iɣaǧen. Netta idřa \add řeḥyuḍ ɣar daxeř n\add* wexxam s setta-mya talint n wureɣ iṣfan.
\v 9 Řewzen n imesmaren isekkwa xemsin ciqlu n wureɣ. Idřa uřa d tiɣurfatin n sennej s wureɣ.
\v 10 Deg wexxam n Weqdas x Uqeddas igga tnayen n ikiruben, \add am\add* řxedmet n wenqac, u iřeḥḥef i-ten s wureɣ.
\v 11 Afriwen n ikiruben \add jmiɛ\add* \add ɛebbaren\add* ɛicrin n iɣaǧen di tuzzeggart. Afriw amezwaru \add iɛebbar\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen n tuzzeggart, ittakkʷaḍ řḥiḍ n Taddart, uca afriw nneɣni n xemsa n iɣaǧen ittakkwaḍ afriw n ukirub nneɣni.
\v 12 Afriw n ukirub nneɣni \add iɛebbar uřa d\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen, ittakkwaḍ řḥiḍ n Taddart. Afriw nneɣni n xemsa n iɣaǧen iřeqqef afriw n ukirub nneɣni.
\v 13 Afriwen n ikiruben-a ttwabezzɛen ɛicrin n iɣaǧen u nitni bedden x iḍaren nsen d iɣembab nsen \add ssewḍen\add* ɣar daxeř.
\v 14 Netta igga uřa d ařeḥḥaf s \add řeqṭen\add* adeḥmi d arjuwani d azeggʷaɣ iḥedqen u s řeqṭen azdad, uca igga xas ikiruben.
\b
\m 
\v 15 Ɣar zzat n Taddart igga netta tnayen n ipilaren s ict n tuzuggart n xemsa u-třatin n iɣaǧen. Ttajj x tqiccat nnes \add tuɣa-t\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen.
\v 16 Netta igga uřa d ssnaseř \add izewwqen\add* am tinni deg Wexxam n Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* uca igga i-tent x tqiccatin n ipilaren. Igga uřa d mya n iremmamen uca icedd i-ten ɣar ssnaseř \add izewwqen\add*.
\v 17 Netta issbedd ipilaren ɣar zzat n Zzawect Tameqqrant, ijjen x yefus u ijjen x uzeřmaḍ. Wenni ɣar yefus igga as Yaxin u wenni x uzeřmaḍ igga as Buɛaz.
\b
\b
\c 4
\m 
\v 1 Netta igga uřa d aɛalṭar n nnḥas. Tuzzeggart nnes \add tuɣa-tt\add* ɛicrin n iɣaǧen u řuɛřa nnes ɛecra n iɣaǧen.
\v 2 Xenni igga netta tarimant ifesyen. \add Tuɣa řeɛbar nnes\add* ɛecra n iɣaǧen zi ṭṭarf ař ṭṭarf \add nneɣni\add*, \add tuɣa-tt d\add* taquract. Tiddi nnes \add tuɣa-tt\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen u ict n ufiřu n řeɛbar n třatin n iɣaǧen inneḍ as-dd. \f ◼ \fr 4:2 \fk tarimant\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řebḥar’ niɣ ‘il’.\f*
\v 3 Sadu nnes beddent řexyařat n ifunasen, aqa nnḍent as-dd qaɛ. \add Nnuwarat i war dd-ffiɣent ɛad\add* tuɣa i d as dd-innḍen qaɛ, ɛecra di kuř ijj n uɣiř, tuɣa qqnent ak-d wayawya am quwwarent i trimant \add di\add* tnayen n iseddiyyen. \add Nnuwarat i war dd-ffiɣent ɛad\add* tuɣa ttwafesyent d ijjen \add ak-d trimant\add*.
\v 4 Tarimant tbedd x tenɛac n ifunasen. Třata zzaysen arrin udem nsen ɣar ccamal, třata zzaysen arrin udem nsen ɣar řɣarb, třata zzaysen arrin udem nsen ɣar ljanub u třata zzaysen arrin udem nsen ɣar ccarq. Tarimant \add tarsa\add* xasen u marra zzɛenquqat nsen dewřent ɣar daxeř.
\v 5 Tuɣa \add tarimant\add* tegdar ijj n cbar n ufus u tma nnes tuɣa am mammec tteggen tma n ijj n ufenjař, \add am\add* tnewwact n ict n tlillect. Teksi twawit nnes teřt-ařaf n ibatuten. \f ◼ \fr 4:5 \fk talillect\ft - ict n marka n nnuwarat daysen aẓri aṭṭas. \fk abatu\ft - ijj n ‘ubatu’ ɛraḥař 20 niɣ 40 litru.\f*
\v 6 Igga netta ɛecra n tbanyutin uca igga xemsa \add zzaysent\add* x yefus u xemsa \add zzaysent\add* x uzeřmaḍ, ḥima ad daysent ssirden iziynat ittwasswejden i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, ssirden \add tent\add* daysent. \add Maca\add* tarimant tuɣa-tt i ikehhanen, maḥend ad dayes ssirden ixef nsen.
\v 7 Netta igga ɛecra n řeqnadeř n wureɣ ɛlaḥsab lfariḍa u netta issbedd i-ten di Zzawect Tameqqrant, xemsa x yefus u xemsa x uzeřmaḍ.
\v 8 Netta igga ɛecra n tzewḍiwin uca igga i-tent di Zzawect Tameqqrant, xemsa x yefus u xemsa x uzeřmaḍ. Igga uřa d mya n ṭṭawyat i urucci n wureɣ.
\v 9 Netta igga řemraḥ iḥṣaren i ikehhanen d řemraḥ ameqqran ak-d tewwura i řemraḥ, uca iřeḥḥef tiwwura nsen s nnḥas.
\v 10 Tarimant igga i-tt x uɣezdis afusi ɣar zzat, ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq, jjihet n ljanub.
\v 11 Ḥiram igga uřa d tiydurin d iɣenjajen d ṭṭawyat i urucci. Ammu i ikemmeř Ḥuram cɣeř i řeqcuɛ i igga i ujeǧid Suliman i Taddart n AREBBI.
\m 
\v 12 \add Igga\add* tnayen n ipilaren d iquraren, d ttijan \add i iǧan\add* x uzeǧif n tnayen n ipilaren, d tnayen n tracciwin ḥima ad \add zzaysent\add* dřen tnayen n iquraren n ttijan \add i iǧan\add* x uzeǧif n ipilaren,
\v 13 uřa d arebɛa-mya n iremmamen i tnayen n tracciwin: tnayen n iseddiyyen i kuř tracca ḥima ad \add zzaysen\add* dřen tnayen n iquraren n ttijan nni \add iǧan\add* tiwa sennej x wudem n ipilaren.
\v 14 Igga tikarrutin u x tkarrutin igga tibanyutin \add i usird\add*.
\v 15 \add Igga uřa d\add* tarimant d icten, uřa d tenɛac n ifunasen sadu nnes.
\v 16 Igga Ḥiram \add ak-d\add* babas uřa d teydurin d iɣenjajen d furcayat d marra řeqcuɛ nnes, i ujeǧid Suliman, i Taddart n SIDI, zi nnḥas ittwassuydan.
\v 17 Ajeǧid ikebb i-ten deg udewwar n L’Urdun, di třaxt igdaren jar Sukkut d Ṣaradata. \x ◘ \xo 4:17 \xt Yac. 3:16\x*
\b
\m 
\v 18 Suliman igga marra řeqcuɛ-a x ubarru ameqqran, ařami war beqqcen ca \add ɛad\add* di řewzen n nnḥas.
\v 19 Suliman igga marra řeqcuɛ i Taddart n AREBBI: aɛalṭar n wureɣ, tizewḍiwin min xef \add ittwammars\add* weɣrum n wescan,
\v 20 řeqnadeř ak-d řefnarat nsen nni ittxeṣṣan ad arɣen ɛlaḥsab lfariḍa zzat i \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add*, \add marra\add* zeg wureɣ izedgen.
\v 21 \add Igga ɛawed\add* nnuwwar, řefnarat d tjeqqaḍin \add n teftič\add*, \add marra\add* zeg wureɣ. Tuɣa-t d wureɣ qaɛ.
\v 22 Uřa d tijeqqaḍin, ṭṭawyat i urucci, tiɣenjayin d tqedduḥin n jjawi \add tuɣa atent\add* zeg wureɣ izedgen. Adaf n Taddart, tiwwura n daxeř zzat i Weqdas x Uqeddas d tewwura n Taddart n Zzawect Tameqqrant, \add tuɣa atent\add* zeg wureɣ.
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Adeccen n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 Ammu i tᵉttwakemmeř marra řxedmet i igga Suliman i Taddart n SIDI. Uca issidef Suliman marra řeqcuɛ iqeddsen n babas Dawud: nnuqart d wureɣ d marra řeqcuɛ, uca issars \add man aya marra\add* deg ixxamen n txubay n Taddart n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt [1 Ij. 8:1-66]\x*
\v 2 Xenni issmun Suliman imeqqranen n Israil, marra izeǧifen n tqebbař d řḥukkam n \add tudrin n\add* ibabaten n ayt n Israil. Netta issmun i-ten di Urcalim ḥima ad ssgeɛɛden Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI zi tendint n Dawud, tenni d Ṣihyun.
\v 3 Marra iryazen n Israil munen-dd ɣar ujeǧid ɣar řɛid. Tuɣa-tt deg uyur wiss sebɛa.
\m 
\v 4 Marra imeqqranen n Israil usin-dd uca ssgeɛɛden Ilawiyyen Ttabut.
\v 5 Ssgeɛɛden Ttabut n SIDI ak-d Uqiḍun n Umsagar uřa d marra řeqcuɛ iqeddsen i tuɣa din iǧan deg Uqiḍun. Ssgeɛɛden aya ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen.
\v 6 Marra tamesmunt n Israil, tenni tuɣa ɣares imunen, tuɣa tbedd ak-d ujeǧid Suliman zzat i Ttabut. Nitni wehhben uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin nni iǧan břa řeḥsab, war zemmaren ad ten qeddaren di ssibbet n ubarru nsen.
\v 7 Iwyen ikehhanen Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI ɣar wemcan nnes, ɣar \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* n Taddart, deg Weqdas x Uqeddas, ař sadu wafriwen n ikiruben. \f ◼ \fr 5:7 \fk ikiruben\ft - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*
\v 8 Ikiruben bezzɛen tnayen n wafriwen nsen x wemcan n Ttabut uca \add ammu i\add* dřin ikiruben Ttabut d iɛumad nnes \add i tarebbut\add* zi sennej.
\v 9 Awarni aya ssřeḥmen iɛumad \add n tarebbut\add*, maḥend ad banent texfawin n iɛumad, inni dd-iffɣen zi Ttabut, ɣar uɣezdis n zzat n \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add*, \add maca\add* war dd-ttbinint zi barra. \add Ttabut\add* aqa-tt din ař ass-a.
\v 10 Tuɣa war iǧi ca di Ttabut, mɣir tnayen n teřwiḥin i dayes issars Musa ɣar Hurib, řami igga SIDI Řɛahd ak-d ayt n Israil umi dd-ffɣen zi Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt 1 Ij. 8:9\x*
\m 
\v 11 Ařami dd-ffɣen ikehhanen zeg Uqeddas - maɣar marra ikehhanen nni tuɣa zemmaren ad afen, tuɣa ssqeddsen ixef nsen břa ma ad wcen taynit i terbiɛin nsen -
\v 12 \add am\add* tuɣa Ilawiyyen - \add ixs ad yini\add* marra imedyazen: inni ɣar Asaf d yinni ɣar Hayman d yinni ɣar Yadutun, d yinni n iḥenjiren nsen d yinni n aytmatsen - yarḍen řeqṭen azdad, uca bedden s taǧunin n wuzzař d lharpat d řgambriyat ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq n uɛalṭar u tuɣa akidsen ɛřaḥař mya u-ɛicrin n ikehhanen i ittsuḍen di řebwaq. \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt Řex. 1:15\x*
\v 13 Suḍen nitni di řɣayṭa u ɣennjen am yijj \add n weryaz\add*, ḥima ad ittwaseř řḥess d ijjen am ssemɣaran u ttqadan nitni SIDI. Nitni ssgeɛɛden tmijja \add nsen ɣar ujenna\add* s řebwaq d taǧunin n wuzzař d dduzanat n ǧɣa nneɣni, ssemɣaran SIDI: ‘Maɣar Netta iṣbeḥ, maɣar tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren tᵉttɣima i řebda!’ \add Xenni\add* imsar aqa Taddart, Taddart n SIDI, tᵉttwaccur s useynu,
\v 14 uca ikehhanen war zemmaren ad qqimen bedden maḥend ad sexxaren di ssibbet n useynu, minzi aɛuǧi n SIDI tuɣa iccur Taddart n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Asa. 15:8. \x*
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Suliman ɣar udeccen n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 Xenni inna Suliman:
\b
\m “SIDI inna aqa Netta ad izdeɣ deg yijj n useynu ibbumbes.
\v 2 \add S tidett\add* necc bniɣ ict n Taddart, ict n Tzeddiɣt i Cek, ijj n wemcan imten ḥima ad \add din\add* tzedɣed i řebda.”
\v 3 Issneqřeb ujeǧid aɣembub nnes uca ibarek marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil umi marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil tuɣa ibedd.
\v 4 Netta inna: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, wenni issiwřen s uqemmum nnes ɣar baba Dawud d \add wenni\add* \add t\add* ikemmřen s ufus nnes umi inna:
\v 5 ‘Zeg wass i di nedheɣ řgens inu Israil zi Miṣra, war ixḍareɣ uřa d ict n tendint zi marra tiqebbař n Israil ḥima ad \add dinni\add* bniɣ Taddart ḥima ad \add din\add* yiři Isem inu, u war ixḍareɣ aryaz ḥima ad yiři d řḥakem x řgens inu Israil, \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:8; 1 Ij. 8:16-53\x*
\v 6 \add maca řexxu\add* ixdareɣ Urcalim, ḥima ad \add din\add* yiři Isem inu, u Necc ixḍareɣ Dawud, ḥima ad yiři \add d řḥakem\add* x řgens inu Israil.’
\v 7 Tuɣa deg wuř n baba Dawud maḥend ad ibna Taddart i Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 8 \add Maca\add* SIDI inna i baba Dawud: ‘Umi teggid deg wuř nnec ḥima ad tebnid Taddart i Yisem inu, aqa mliḥ umi teggid man aya deg wuř nnec.
\v 9 Maca war iǧi d cek i ɣa ibnan Taddart nni, maca mmic i dd-iffɣen zi tejɛinna nnec d netta i ɣa ibnan Taddart i Yisem inu.’
\v 10 SIDI issemten awař nnes nni issiweř, maɣar necc dewřeɣ beddeɣ deg wemcan n baba Dawud u qqimeɣ x řɛarc n Israil, am mammec tuɣa issiweř SIDI, u necc bniɣ Taddart i Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 11 Necc ssarseɣ dinni Ttabut wenni di iǧa Řɛahd n SIDI i igga Netta ak-d ayt n Israil.”
\b
\m 
\v 12 Netta ibedd zzat i uɛalṭar n SIDI, arendad n marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil, uca netta iksi ifassen nnes ɣar ujenna.
\v 13 Minzi Suliman tuɣa igga ict n tenhirt n nnḥas u igga i-tt di řwesṭ n řemraḥ. Tuɣa dayes xemsa n iɣaǧen n tuzzeggart, xemsa n iɣaǧen n tiru d třata n iɣaǧen n tiddi. Netta ibedd xas, ibendeq x ifadden nnes qibač i tiṭṭawin n marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil uca iksi ifassen nnes ɣar ujenna, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 14 “\add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, deg ujenna sennej u x temmurt swadday war iǧi uřa d ijj n AREBBI am Cek, wenni iḥḍan Řɛahd d tmexsiwt icewwaren i imsexxaren nnec nni igguren zzat i wudem nnec s marra uř nsen,
\v 15 wenni iḥḍan i umsexxar nnec, baba Dawud, x min xef akides tessiwřed, minzi s uqemmum nnec i tessiwřed u s ufus nnec i t tkemmřed, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, ḥḍa di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar nnec, baba Dawud, x min xef kides tessiwřed umi tennid: ‘War ittwaqess zzayek uřa d ijj n weryaz zi zzat i wudem inu wenni iqqimen x řɛarc n Israil, min ɣa kken arrawen nnec ḥeṭṭan ad uyuren abrid nsen ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa am mammec tuyured cek zzat i wudem inu.’
\v 17 Xenni řexxu, \add a\add* AREBBI n Israil, egg ad dewřen d tidett awařen nni tessiwřed ak-d umsexxar nnec, ak-d Dawud.”
\m 
\v 18 “Maɣar ma s tidett ad izdeɣ AREBBI x temmurt? Xzar ajenna, \add wah,\add* ajenna n ijenwan war izemmar ad Cek iksi, mecḥař s drus \add xenni\add* Taddart-a i ssbeddeɣ necc!
\v 19 Meyyeř ɣar tẓaǧit n umsexxar nnec u ɣar uḥeccem nnes, \add a\add* SIDI, AREBBI inu, ḥima ad tesřed ɣar uřaɣi u ɣar tẓaǧit nni iẓẓuǧ umsexxar nnec zzat i wudem nnec.
\v 20 Ejj tiṭṭawin nnec ad ttwarzment ass d ǧiřet tiwa i Taddart-a, tiwa i wemcan-a min xef tessiwřed aqa Isem nnec ad ittwassemten din, ḥima ad tesřed ɣar tẓaǧit i iẓẓuǧ umsexxar nnec deg wemcan-a.
\v 21 Seř i uḥeccem n umsexxar nnec u n řgens nnec Israil, i tutra i ttẓaǧan nitni deg wemcan-a u seř Cek \add xenni\add* zi Tzeddiɣt nnec, zeg ujenna, \add wah,\add* seř u ɣfar.”
\m 
\v 22 “Mařa ixḍa ijj ak-d jjar nnes u tᵉttwagg xas ict n tjaǧit, ḥima ad tt ijjuǧ u wanita yusa-dd uca ijjuǧ zzat i uɛalṭar nnec di Taddart-a,
\v 23 seř \bd Cek\bd* \add xenni\add* deg ujenna u kkar u ḥkem x imsexxaren nnec, \add ḥima\add* ad ittwaɛaqeb uɛeffan, ejj abrid nnes ad ihwa x uzeǧif nnes u egg s tsegda i umsegged u ewc i-t ɛlaḥsab tasegda nnes.”
\m 
\v 24 “Mařa řgens nnec Israil ittwaɣřeb zzat i wudem n řeɛdu, minzi nitni xḍan akidek u nitni ad ɣarek dd-dewřen uca ad neɛmen s Yisem nnec u ad ẓẓaǧen ad ḥeccmen zzat i wudem nnec di Taddart-a,
\v 25 seř \bd Cek\bd* \add xenni\add* zeg ujenna u ɣfar ddenb n řgens nnec Israil uca ndeh i-ten ad dd-dewřen ɣar temmurt nni i d asen tewcid u i řejdud nsen.”
\m 
\v 26 “Mařa ajenna ittwabelleɛ ařami war din ittiři wenẓar, minzi nitni xḍan akidek, u nitni ad ẓẓaǧen am arrin azeǧif ɣar wemcan-a, ad neɛmen s Yisem nnec u ad dd-dewřen zi ddnub nsen umi ten teḥṣared Cek,
\v 27 seř-dd \bd Cek\bd* \add xenni\add* deg ujenna u ɣfar asen ddenb n imsexxaren nnec u n řgens nnec Israil, minzi Cek tessřemded asen abrid aṣebḥan nni ittxeṣṣa ad kken, u ewc Cek \add xenni\add* anẓar i temmurt nni tewcid d řwart i řgens nnec.”
\m 
\v 28 “Mařa din řaẓ di temmurt, \add niɣ\add* ṭṭaɛun, \add niɣ\add* ittwassecmeḍ \add imendi zeg usemmiḍ\add*, \add niɣ mařa din\add* jjriḥect n wefsu \add niɣ\add* tamuɣri \add tenni\add* iṣarrḍen, \add niɣ\add* mařa iḥṣar i-t řeɛdu \add ɣar\add* tewwura nnes, \add niɣ\add* teřqef i-t mammec ma tegga ca n jjriḥect \add niɣ\add* ca n řeḥřac,
\v 29 \add seř Cek xenni\add* min ma i ɣa iẓẓuǧ ijj n bnadem zi marra řgens nnec Israil u min ma i ɣa ittar, \add am\add* ssnen nitni kuř ijj jjriḥect nsen d řeḥriq nsen, u netta iksi \add xenni\add* ifassen nnes ɣar Taddart-a.
\v 30 \add Wah\add* seř \bd Cek\bd* \add xenni\add* zeg ujenna, zeg wemcan imten mani tzeddɣed, u ɣfar u ewc kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab tibridin nnes, am mammec Cek tessned uř nnes, maɣar Cek waha i issnen uř n bnadem,
\v 31 ḥima ad Cek ggʷeden u ad uyuren di tebridin nnec marra ussan i ɣa kken ddaren x wudem n temmurt nni tewcid i řejdud nneɣ.”
\m 
\v 32 “Uřa mařa netta d abarrani, wenni war \add iǧin\add* zi řgens nnec, maca ad dd-yas di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem nnec zeg ict n temmurt tiggʷej di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem nnec ameqqran d ufus nnec ijehden d uɣiř nnec isswiẓẓḍen, \add xenni mařa\add* dd-yusin nitni, uca ad ẓẓaǧen am arrin azeǧif ɣar Taddart-a,
\v 33 seř \bd Cek\bd* \add xenni\add* zeg ujenna, zeg wemcan imten mani tzeddɣed, u egg ɛlaḥsab marra min xef ɣarek i ɣa iřaɣa ubarrani, ḥima marra řegnus n ddunect ad ssnen Isem nnec, ḥima nitni ad cek ggʷeden, am řgens nnec Israil, u ad ssnen aqa Isem nnec ittwabarreḥ tiwa i Taddart-a i bniɣ.”
\m 
\v 34 “Mařa řgens iffeɣ ɣar umenɣi ak-d řɛedyan nnes deg webrid i x i ten tessekked, u nitni ad ẓẓaǧen i Cek \add am\add* arrin azeǧif ɣar tendint-a i tixḍared Cek, u ɣar Taddart i bniɣ i Yisem nnec,
\v 35 seř Cek \add xenni\add* zeg ujenna i tẓaǧit nsen u i uḥeccem nsen uca aɣ asen tasɣart.”
\m 
\v 36 “Mařa nitni xḍan akidek - maɣar war iǧi uřa d ijj n bnadem i war ixeṭṭin - u Cek tesɛared xasen, ad ten tsellmed zzat i wudem n řeɛdu uca nitni ad ten nedhen d imeḥbas ɣar temmurt n řeɛdu, tiggʷej niɣ tudes \add i teǧa\add*,
\v 37 u \add mařa\add* \add xenni\add* ad tuben deg wuř nsen di temmurt mani ttwaḥebbsen, \add wah,\add* ad tuben u ad xak dd-řaɣan di temmurt n tḥebbast nsen, ad inin: neccin nexḍa u negga min war iseggden, aqa negga tuɛeffna!,
\v 38 \add wah,\add* ad ɣarek dd-dewřen s marra uř nsen u s marra řeɛmar nsen di temmurt n řɛedyan nsen mani ttwaḥebbsen uca ad ɣarek ẓẓaǧen \add am\add* arrin azeǧif ɣar temmurt nni tewcid i řejdud nsen, ɣar tendint-a i tixḍared Cek u ɣar Taddart-a i bniɣ i Yisem nnec,
\v 39 seř Cek \add xenni\add* zeg ujenna, amcan imten mani tzeddɣed, i tẓaǧit nsen u i uḥeccem nsen uca aɣ asen tasɣart. Ɣfar \add xenni\add* řgens nnec min zi xak xḍan.”
\m 
\v 40 “\add Xenni\add* řexxu, AREBBI inu, ejj tiṭṭawin nnec ad iřint arzment d imezzuɣen nnec ad iřin ḥḍan i tẓaǧit deg wemcan-a.
\v 41 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* SIDI AREBBI, \add adef\add* ɣar arraḥet nnec, Cek d Ttabut n jjehd nnec. Ejj ad iřin ikehhanen nnec, \add a\add* SIDI AREBBI, arḍen s usenjem, uca iři ad farḥen imtiqqan nnec s řxar.
\v 42 \add A\add* SIDI AREBBI, war tarri aɣembub n umedhun nnec, idar di tmegga n tmexsiwt icewwaren n umsexxar nnec Dawud.”
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Aɛuǧi n SIDI iccur Taddart
\m 
\v 1 Umi ikemmeř Suliman taẓaǧit \add nnes\add*, tehwa-dd tmessi zeg ujenna tecca taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uřa d tɣarṣa \add inneɣni\add*, uca iccur uɛuǧi n SIDI Taddart.
\v 2 Ikehhanen war zemmaren ad adfen ɣar Taddart n SIDI, minzi aɛuǧi n SIDI tuɣa iccur Taddart n SIDI.
\v 3 \add Umi\add* ẓrin marra ayt n Israil belli tehwa-dd tmessi nni, uřa d aɛuǧi n SIDI iban-dd tiwa n Taddart, uḍaren nitni s uɣembub nsen ɣar temmurt x tisi n zzellij, bendqen, qadan SIDI: “Maɣar Netta iṣbeḥ u tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren \add tᵉttɣima\add* i řebda”.
\m 
\v 4 Ajeǧid, u marra Israil akides, wehhben tiɣarṣa zzat i wudem n SIDI.
\v 5 Ajeǧid Suliman iwehheb tnayen u-ɛicrin-ařef n ifunasen d tfunasin d mya u-ɛicrin ařef n wuǧi d taɣarṣt n řehna. Ammu i ideccen ujeǧid d marra ayt n Israil Taddart n AREBBI.
\v 6 Ikehhanen \add tuɣa bedden\add* ɣar tsexxart nsen uca Ilawiyyen \add bedden\add* ak-d dduzan n ǧɣa n SIDI, inni igga ujeǧid Dawud ḥima ad qadan SIDI - ‘Maɣar tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren \add tᵉttɣima\add* i řebda!’ - s \add izřan n\add* uṣebbeḥ n Dawud deg ufus nsen, u arendad nsen suḍen ikehhanen di řebwaq, am tuɣa ibedd marra Israil.
\v 7 Suliman issqeddes řwesṭ n řemraḥ n zzat, wenni \add iǧan\add* zzat i Taddart n SIDI, minzi yiwi din tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tadunt n tewhibin \add n řɣiǧet\add*, maɣar aɛalṭar n nnḥas nni igga Suliman tuɣa war izemmar ad iksi taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tadunt.
\m 
\v 8 Di řweqt nni iɛeyyed Suliman Řɛid i yijj n řmijar n sebɛa n wussan d marra Israil akides, ijj n wegraw \add n řgens\add* d ameqqran, zi mani ɣa tiwḍed ɣar Ḥamat ař Taɣzart n Miṣra.
\v 9 Deg wass wiss tmenya ggin ijj n umuni ifarzen, minzi di sebɛa n wussan ggin nitni adeccen n uɛalṭar uca uřa d Řɛid \add awarni man aya\add* ɣares \add ɛawed\add* ijj n řmijar n sebɛa n wussan.
\v 10 Deg wass wiss třata u-ɛicrin n uyur wiss sebɛa yarxu netta i řgens ad raḥen ɣar iqiḍan nsen s wuř ifarḥen u s řxaḍar s marra řxar i igga SIDI i umsexxar nnes Dawud d Suliman u i řgens nnes Israil.
\b
\s1 Aḍhar wiss tnayen n SIDI i Suliman
\m 
\v 11 \add Ammu i\add* ikemmeř Suliman řebni n Taddart n SIDI d taddart n ujeǧid. Marra min tuɣa deg wuř n Suliman ḥima ad t igg di Taddart n SIDI u di taddart nnes, aqa ifřeḥ \add ad igg\add* aya. \x ◘ \xo 7:11 \xt [1 Ij. 9:1-9]\x*
\v 12 SIDI iban-dd i Suliman di ǧiřet, inna as:
\m “Necc sřiɣ i tẓaǧit nnec u farzeɣ amcan-a i Yixef inu ḥima ad yiři d Taddart \add i tewhibt n\add* tɣarṣt.
\v 13 Xmi ɣa bellɛeɣ ajenna maḥend war iccit wenẓar \add ɛad\add*, niɣ mařa umureɣ tamuɣri iřeḥḥfen maḥend ad tecc temmurt niɣ xmi dd-ssekkeɣ ṭṭaɛun jar řgens inu,
\v 14 uca řgens inu x min xef ittwařaɣa Isem inu ad issehwa ixef nnes, ad iẓẓaǧ, u nitni ad arzun udem inu u ad tuben zi tebridin nsen tiɛeffanin, \add xenni\add* Necc ad ɣarsen sřeɣ zeg ujenna, ad asen ɣfareɣ u ad ssgenfiɣ tammurt nsen.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, tiṭṭawin inu ad iřint arzment d imezzuɣen inu ad ḥḍan x tẓaǧit zeg wemcan-a,
\v 16 maɣar řexxu ixḍareɣ Taddart-a u ssqeddseɣ tt ḥima ad ssmetneɣ din Isem inu i řebda u tiṭṭawin inu d wuř inu \add ad\add* din \add iřin\add* marra ussan.
\m 
\v 17 Mařa cek tuyured zzat i wudem inu am mammec tuɣa iggur babac Dawud, u ad tegged am mammec marra i d ac umureɣ uca ad teḥḍid tiweṣṣa inu d lfarayiḍ inu,
\v 18 \add xenni\add* ad ssmetneɣ řɛarc n tgeldit nnec am mammec Řɛahd i ggiɣ ak-d babac Dawud, nniɣ: ‘War d ac ittxeṣṣa uřa d ijj n weryaz nni iḥekkmen di Israil!’
\m 
\v 19 Maca mařa kenniw tḥeyydem zi tweṣṣa inu d řumurat inu nni wciɣ zzat i wudem nwem, uca ad tuyurem ad tɛebdem i irebbiten nneɣni, ad asen tbendqem,
\v 20 xenni ad qḍiɣ x Israil zi temmurt nni d asen wciɣ, uca Taddart-a, i ssqeddseɣ i Yisem inu, ad tt nḍareɣ zeg wudem inu u Israil ad idweř d umedya \add uřa d řqecɛet\add* n ubehdeř itteqqsen jar marra řegnus.
\v 21 U x Taddart-a tenni yuɛřan qaɛ, marra wi xas i ɣa ikken, ad itebhet, ad yini: ‘Mayemmi igga SIDI ammu di temmurt-a u di Taddart-a?’
\v 22 Ad inin: ‘Minzi nitni semḥen di SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen, wenni ten dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, u minzi nitni cebbaren di irebbiten nneɣni u Israil yuyur ad asen isjed u ad ten iɛbed, x uya isseɣḍeř Netta marra řɣar-a xasen.’”
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Řebniyat d tsexxart di Zzawect Iqeddsen d wureɣ
\m 
\v 1 Awarni ɛicrin n iseggʷusa i di ibna Suliman tnayen n tudrin, Taddart n SIDI u taddart n ujeǧid, imsar, \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt [1 Ij. 9:10-28]\x*
\v 2 aqa Suliman ibna \add ɛawed\add* tineddam i d as iwca Ḥiram uca issezdeɣ din ayt n Israil.
\v 3 Awarni as iffeɣ Suliman ɣar Ḥamat-Ṣuba uca iṭṭef i-tt.
\v 4 Netta ibna Tadmur di řexřa. Ibna \add ɛawed\add* marra tineddam n řexzen di Ḥamat. \x ◘ \xo 8:4 \xt 1 Ij. 9:17-18\x*
\v 5 Netta ibna uřa d Bayt-Ḥurun n nnej d Bayt-Ḥurun n wadday, tneddam ifaryen s řeḥyuḍ d tewwura d iɛumad i ubelleɛ,
\v 6 uřa d Baɛlat d marra tineddam n řexzen nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar Suliman, d marra tineddam n ikarruten d marra tineddam n imnayen u \add xenni\add* marra min issitem Suliman ad tt ibna di Urcalim u di Lubnan u di marra tammurt n řeḥkam nnes.
\m 
\v 7 X marra řgens i iqqimen - \add x řgens\add* n Iḥittiyyen, n Imuriyyen, n Ifiriziyyen, n Iḥiwiyyen u n Iyabusiyyen, inni war \add iǧin\add* ca zeg ayt n Israil,
\v 8 u x warrawen nsen nni iqqimen awarni asen di temmurt, inni war ttwaqḍan s ufus n ayt n Israil - igga xasen Suliman ddquřat qesḥent ař ass-a.
\v 9 \add Maca\add* zeg ayt n Israil war iggi Suliman d isemɣan i řexdayem nnes, minzi nitni tuɣa aten d iɛeskariyyen d imeqqranen x ineɣrafen nnes \add zi řɛeskar\add*, d imeqqranen n ikarruten nnes d imnayen nnes.
\m 
\v 10 Ina d imeḥḍayen imeqqranen nni tuɣa ɣar ujeǧid n Suliman, mitayen u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nni tuɣa ittḍebbaren x řgens.
\m 
\v 11 Suliman issgeɛɛed yeǧis n firɛun zi tendint n Dawud ɣar taddart i tuɣa i d as ibna, minzi inna: “Tamɣart inu war tzeddiɣ ca di taddart n Dawud, ajeǧid n Israil, minzi imucan mani dd-tusa Ttabut n SIDI, aqa aten qeddsen.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Xenni issgeɛɛed Suliman tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i SIDI x uɛalṭar n SIDI nni tuɣa ibna zzat i wesqif n wadaf \add n Zzawect Tameqqrant\add*,
\v 13 ɛlaḥsab lfariḍa i kuř ass i tewhibt n tɣarṣa, am mammec \add teqqar\add* tewṣeyyet n Musa i wussan n ssebt, i wussan n uyur n jdid u i třata řeɛyudat i ittwaggen i kuř aseggʷas: di Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun, di Řɛid n Ssimanat u di Řɛid n Iɛuccuten.
\v 14 Am mammec dd-tusa lfariḍa n babas Dawud issbedd \add ɛawed\add* tirbiɛin n ikehhanen i řxedmet nsen, d \add terbiɛin\add* n Ilawiyyen i tsexxart nsen, ḥima ad ssemɣaren \add di Zzawect Tameqqrant\add* u ad sexxaren i ikehhanen ɛlaḥsab awař \add n lfariḍa\add* i kuř ass, uca \add issbedd uřa\add* d iɛessasen n tewwart di terbiɛin nsen ɣar kuř tawwart, minzi ammu i yeǧa řumur n Dawud, aryaz n AREBBI.
\v 15 Nitni war ḥeyyden ca řa deg ict n jjihet x řumur n ujeǧid i ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen, war iǧi uřa zi jjihet n ixxamen n txubay.
\v 16 \add Ammu\add* i tᵉttwasseqfeř marra řxedmet n Suliman zeg wass \add n usarsi n\add* dsas n Taddart n SIDI ař akemmeř nnes, \add wah ammu\add* i tᵉttwakemmeř Taddart n SIDI.
\b
\m 
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* iruḥ Suliman ɣar Ɛiṣyun-Jabir u ɣar Aylat, ɣar tma n řebḥar, di temmurt n Idum.
\v 18 S ufus n imsexxaren nnes issekk Ḥiram ɣares iɣarruba, uca imsexxaren nni issnen řebḥar, u nedhen ak-d imsexxaren n Suliman ɣar Ufir uca iwyen-dd ssenni \bd arebɛa-mya u xemsin talint n wureɣ\bd* uca usin-dd \add zzayes\add* ɣar ujeǧid Suliman.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Tawasit n tjeǧidt n Saba ɣar Suliman
\m 
\v 1 Tajeǧidt n Caba tesřa x ccennɛet n Suliman uca, ḥima ad tqeǧeb Suliman s tḥuja n twafit, tusa-dd ɣar Urcalim s ijj n ukaravan s ddqeř \add n wagřa\add* aṭṭas, s iřeɣman nni yarebbun řeɛṭur d waṭṭas n wureɣ d iẓra iɣřan u nettat tusa-dd ɣar Suliman uca tessiweř akides x marra min ɣares deg wuř. \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt [1 Ij. 10:1-3]\x*
\v 2 Suliman icarḥ marra awařen nnes. War din uřa d ijj n wawař \add s řemɛani\add* innuffaren i Suliman ařami war izemmar ad as t icarreḥ.
\m 
\v 3 \add Řami\add* teẓra tjeǧidt n Caba tiɣit n Suliman d taddart i ibna,
\v 4 d macca x ṭṭabřa nnes, d mammec qqimen imsexxaren nnes, d mammec bedden ixeddamen nnes, d warruḍ nsen d iwarraden nnes d warruḍ nsen d mammec igeɛɛed am dd-igeɛɛed ɣar Taddart n SIDI, war iqqim dayes \add ɛřaḥař\add* buḥbeř \add ɛad\add*.
\v 5 Nettat tenna i ujeǧid:
\b
\m “Awař nni sřiɣ di temmurt inu x wawařen nnec u x tiɣit nnec, nican d tidett.
\v 6 Necc war umineɣ ca s wawařen nni, ařami dd-usiɣ danita u \add xenni\add* tiṭṭawin inu ẓrint aya. Xzar, azyen n tiɣit nnec tameqqrant war d ayi ittwanna. Aqa cek sennej x řexbar i \add xak\add* sřiɣ.
\v 7 Sseɛd n yeryazen nnec, sseɛd n imsexxaren nnec, inni ibedden zzat i wudem nnec řebda u ittesřan ɣar tiɣit nnec!
\v 8 Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni umi dd-tusid x řxaḍar ḥima ad cek yegg d ajeǧid i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, x řɛarc nnes. Minzi AREBBI ittexs aṭṭas ad yejj Israil ad teqqim i řebda, s uya igga cek d ajeǧid xasen i řebda, maḥend ad tegged řḥeqq d tsegda.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 Nettat tewca i ujeǧid mya u-ɛicrin talint n wureɣ d waṭṭas n řebzer d iẓra iɣřan. Řebzer am wanita i tewca tjeǧidt n Caba i ujeǧid Suliman, ɛemmarṣ war iǧi \add ɛad\add*.
\m 
\v 10 Imsexxaren n Ḥiram i dd iwyen ureɣ zeg Ufir ak-d imsexxaren n Suliman, iwyen ɛawed akeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ṣandal azeggʷaɣ d yeẓra iɣřan.
\v 11 Ajeǧid igga zeg ukeccuḍ nni n \add tcejjart n\add* ṣandel azeggʷaɣ ddrujat timeqqranin i Taddart n SIDI u i taddart n ujeǧid, uřa d řgambriyat d lharpat i imedyazen. Am man aya war t ẓrin ɛemmarṣ qbeř di temmurt n Yahuda.
\m 
\v 12 Ajeǧid Suliman iwca i tjeǧidt n Caba marra min tuɣa dayes d meẓri, min ma tᵉttar, \add wah, ktar zi\add* min dd ttiwi ɣar ujeǧid. \add Xenni\add* tenneqřeb u teɛqeb ɣar temmurt nnes, nettat d imsexxaren nnes.
\b
\s1 Aṭṭas n wagřa n Sulimand řmewt nnes
\m 
\v 13 Řqedd n wureɣ i ittadfen ɣar Suliman deg ijj n useggʷas tuɣa setta-mya u-setta u-settin talint n wureɣ, \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt [1 Ij. 10:14-29] — 1 Ij. 10:14; Ɛiz. 2:13; Asa. 17:9. \x*
\v 14 nhřa arbeḥ zeg iryazen imsewwqen i dd-ittennḍen \add di temmurt\add* u zi tsebbabt n isebbaben, u nhřa arbeḥ n wureɣ d nnuqart i Suliman zeg marra ijeǧiden n temmurt n Ɛarabiyya u zi lwulat n temmurt.
\m 
\v 15 Ajeǧid Suliman igga \add ɛawed\add* mitayen n tseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* timeqqranin s wureɣ ittwaddzen. X ict n tseddart ttwaggen setta-mya \add ciqlu\add* n wureɣ.
\v 16 \add Yarni igga netta\add* teřt-mya n tseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* s wureɣ ittwaddzen. Ttwaggent teřt-mya \add cciqlu\add* n wureɣ deg ict n tseddart. Ajeǧid issars i-tent di Taddart n Wezɣar n Lubnan. \f ◼ \fr 9:16 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\m 
\v 17 Ajeǧid igga ɛawed ijj n řɛarc ameqqran n řɛaj uca iɣeřf i-t s wureɣ iṣfan. \f ◼ \fr 9:17 \fk řɛaj\ft - ixs ad yini ‘accawen n lfil’.\f*
\v 18 Řɛarc wanita ɣares setta n tareffidin u tᵉttwacedd ict n tneddabt n wureɣ i yiḍaren i řɛarc. Ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen n řkursi tuɣa ǧan iɣaǧen u tnayen n wayraden tuɣa bedden zzat i iɣaǧen \add n řɛarc\add*.
\v 19 Tenɛac n wayraden bedden ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen x setta n tareffidin. Am netta war ittwagg \add ɛad\add* uřa deg ict n tgeldit.
\m 
\v 20 Marra iɣarrafen n tissit n Suliman \add tuɣa aten\add* n wureɣ u marra řeqcuɛ n Taddart n Wezɣar n Lubnan \add tuɣa aten\add* s wureɣ izedgen, war din nnuqart \add dayes\add*, \add maɣar\add* deg wussan n Suliman tuɣa ḥessben tt d walu.
\v 21 Maɣar ajeǧid tuɣa ɣares iɣarruba nni inedhen ɣar Tarcic ak-d imsexxaren n Ḥiram. Ict n twařa di třata n iseggʷusa usin-dd iɣarruba zi Tarcic, iwyen-dd ureɣ d nnuqart, řɛaj d ibaɣusen d iṭawsen.
\v 22 Ajeǧid Suliman iɛdu marra ijeǧiden n ddunect deg wagřa d tiɣit.
\v 23 Marra ijeǧiden n ddunect arzun \add ad ẓaren\add* udem n Suliman, maḥend ad sřen ɣar tiɣit nnes i tuɣa issars AREBBI deg wuř nnes.
\v 24 Nitni usin-dd aseggʷas awarni i umas, kuř ijj s tarzeft nnes, \add s\add* řeqcuɛ n nnuqart, řeqcuɛ n wureɣ, arruḍ, řesnaḥ, řeɛṭur, iysan d isardan.
\m 
\v 25 Suliman tuɣa ɣares arebɛa-ařaf n řkurit i iysan d ikarruten u i tenɛac-ařef n imnayen. Igga i-ten di tneddam n ikarruten u ɣar ujeǧid di Urcalim.
\v 26 Netta iḥkem x marra ijeǧiden zeg iɣzar \add Lfuraṭ\add* ař tammurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen u ař aymir n Miṣra.
\v 27 Ajeǧid igga nnuqart di Urcalim am yeẓra u \add ticejjura n\add* tengelt igga \add i-ten\add* am yizemmuren nni \add iǧan\add* aṭṭas di Temmurt Iwaṭan.
\v 28 Iwyen-dd iysan i Suliman zi Miṣra u zi marra timmura.
\b
\m 
\v 29 Min iqqimen n imezruyen n Suliman, imezwura d ineggura, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n unabi Natan u di nnubuwa n Axiya Axiluni u deg iweḥḥan n umwařaw Yaɛdu x Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ? \x ◘ \xo 9:29 \xt [1 Ij. 11:41-43]\x*
\v 30 Suliman iḥkem di Urcalim arebɛin n iseggʷusa x marra Israil.
\v 31 Suliman igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes uca neḍřen t di tendint n babas Dawud. Mmis Raḥabɛam idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Abeṭṭu n tgeldit
\m 
\v 1 Raḥabɛam yuyur ɣar Cakim, maɣar marra Israil tuɣa yusa-dd ɣar Cakim, ḥima ad t ggen d ajeǧid. \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt [1 Ij. 12:1-24]\x*
\v 2 Umi isřa Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, x man aya, umi t tuɣa ɛad di Miṣra - zeɛma netta tuɣa yarweř zeg wudem n ujeǧid Suliman - imsar \add as\add* aqa iɛqeb-dd.
\v 3 Ssekken-dd \add ɣares\add*, jjin ad xas řaɣan. Yusa-d Yarubɛam ak-d marra tamesmunt n Israil, ssiwřen nitni ak-d Raḥabɛam, nnan:
\v 4 “Babac igga xaneɣ ijj n uzayřu iqseḥ. Xenni řexxu, sarxu řxedmet iqesḥen n babac uřa d azayřu ideqřen i xaneɣ igga, \add xenni\add* ad cek nexdem.”
\v 5 Netta inna asen: “Uyurem u ɛeqbem awarni i třata n wussan.” Uca yuyur řgens.
\m 
\v 6 Imcawar ujeǧid Raḥabɛam ak-d imeqqranen nni tuɣa ibedden zzat i wudem n babas Suliman umi tuɣa ɛad iddar, inna: “S minzi i d ayi tweṣṣam ad dd-arreɣ x řgens-a?”
\v 7 Nitni ssiwřen akides, nnan: “Mařa cek teggid s tcuni ak-d řgens-a, ad kidsen tegged ɣar řxaḍar nsen uca ad kidsen tessiwřed s wawařen icnan, \add xenni\add* ad dewřen d imsexxaren nnec marra min iqqimen n ussan.”
\v 8 \add Maca\add* netta inḍar ccwar i d as tuɣa wcin imeqqranen uca imcawar ak-d iḥudriyyen nni tuɣa akides imɣaren u bedden řexxu zzat i wudem nnes.
\v 9 Netta isseqsa i-ten: “S minzi i d aneɣ tweṣṣam ad narr x wawař n řgens, minzi sswiřen akidi, nnan: ‘Sarxu azayřu i xaneɣ igga babac.’”
\v 10 Iḥudriyyen nni tuɣa mɣaren akides, ssiwřen akides, nnan: “Ammu i dd ɣa tarred x řgens i kidek issiwřen u nnan: ‘Babac issedqeř azayřu nneɣ, maca \add řexxu\add* cek sarxu t xaneɣ!’, \add wah,\add* ammu i kidsen i ɣa tessiwřed: ‘\add Aḍaḍ\add* ameẓyan inu ad yiři d ameqqran x tejɛinna n baba.
\v 11 Mařa baba iqqen awem ijj n uzayřu iqseḥ, \add xenni\add* necc ad t ssdeqřeɣ \add ɛad\add*. Mařa baba yarebbi kenniw s urekkuḍ, necc ad kenniw arebbiɣ s iɣarḍmiwen.’”
\m 
\v 12 Deg wass wiss třata yusa-dd Yarubɛam ak-d marra řgens ɣar Raḥabɛam, am mammec tuɣa issiweř ujeǧid, tuɣa inna: “Ɛeqbem-dd ɣari awarni i třata n wussan!”
\v 13 Ajeǧid yarra-dd x řgens s ijj n webrid iqesḥen, maɣar ajeǧid Raḥabɛam ismeḥ di ccwar n imeqqranen.
\v 14 Issiweř akidsen ɛlaḥsab ccwar n iḥudriyyen, inna: “Necc ad ssdeqřeɣ ɛad azayřu nwem. Baba yarebbi kenniw s urekkuḍ, necc ad kenniw arebbiɣ s iɣarḍmiwen.”
\v 15 Ajeǧid war isři ca ɣar řgens, maɣar aneqřeb-a tuɣa yusa-dd zi AREBBI, ḥima ad issemten SIDI awař i tuɣa issiweř s uqemmum n Axiya, Aciluni, ak-d Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ.
\m 
\v 16 \add Umi\add* iẓra marra Israil aqa ajeǧid war ɣarsen dd-isři ca, yarra-dd řgens x ujeǧid, inna: “Man tasɣart i ɣarneɣ ak-d Dawud? Neccin war ɣarneɣ bu tesɣart ak-d mmis n Yassa. Marra \add kenniw,\add* uyurem ɣar iqiḍan nwem, \add a\add* Israil! Řha řexxu ak-d taddart nnec, Dawud!” Uca marra Israil yuyur ɣar iqiḍan nsen. \f ◼ \fr 10:16 \fk Marra \bdit kenniw\bdit* uyurem ɣar iqiḍan nwem\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Aryaz ɣar iqiḍan nnec!’.\f*
\v 17 Tuɣa Raḥabɛam d ajeǧid x ayt n Israil nni tuɣa izeddɣen di tneddam n Yahuda.
\v 18 Ajeǧid Raḥabɛam issekk \add ɣarsen\add* Aduram, wenni \add iǧan\add* x ljizya, u ayt n Israil arjmen t s yeẓra ařami immut. Ajeǧid Raḥabɛam inya deɣya x ukarru, ḥima ad yarweř ɣar Urcalim.
\v 19 \add Ammu i\add* iɣewweɣ Israil x taddart n Dawud ař ass-a.
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Ajeǧid Raḥubɛam iḥekkem x Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Raḥabɛam yusa-dd ɣar Urcalim uca issmun marra taddart n Yahuda d Binyamin, mya u-tmenyin-ařef \add n iryazen\add* ittwafarzen, ttwadarrben x umenɣi, ḥima ad mmenɣen ak-d taddart n Israil, ḥima ad dd-arren tageldit ɣar Raḥubɛam.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n AREBBI ɣar Camɛiya, aryaz n AREBBI, inna:
\v 3 “Siweř ak-d Raḥabɛam, mmis n Suliman, ajeǧid n Yahuda, u ak-d marra Israil di \add temmurt n\add* Yahuda d Binyamin, uca ini:
\v 4 ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: War ttgeɛɛadem ca u war ttmenɣim ca ak-d aytmatwem. Ittxeṣṣa ad iɛqeb \add kuř ijj n\add* weryaz ɣar taddart nnes, maɣar d man aya i imsaren zi ɣari.’” Nitni sřan ɣar wawař n SIDI uca ɛeqben, war uyuren ca ɣar Yarubɛam.
\b
\m 
\v 5 Raḥabɛam izdeɣ di Urcalim uca igga tineddam di Yahuda ad dewřent faryent.
\v 6 Ibna Bayt-Laḥam, Ɛiṭam, Taquɛa,
\v 7 Bayt-Ṣur, Suku, Ɛadullam,
\v 8 Jat, Marica, Zif,
\v 9 Adurayim, Laxis, Ɛaziqa,
\v 10 Ṣurɛa, Ayyalun d Ḥabrun nni \add iǧan\add* di Yahuda d Binyamin. Aqa-tent d tneddam ifaryen.
\v 11 Issejhed lqelɛat u igga xasen řḥukkam u ixzen \add daysent\add* macca, zzect d binu.
\v 12 \add Issars\add* tiseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* timeqqranin d iḥricen di kuř tendint uca issejhed i-tent ař ṭṭarf. \add Ammu i\add* tuɣa Yahuda d Binyamin \add deg ufus\add* nnes.
\m 
\v 13 Ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen nni \add iǧan\add* di marra Israil, qqnen ɣares zi marra jjwayeh nsen.
\v 14 Minzi Ilawiyyen jjin ddmani nsen d wagřa nsen uca usin-dd ɣar Yahuda d Urcalim, maɣar Yarubɛam d iḥenjiren nnes mmenḍaren ten zi tukehhant n SIDI.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* yařeqqem Yarubɛam ikehhanen i yixef nnes i řegɛudi, i \add řexyařat n\add* imuyan \add ijennen\add* u i \add řexyařat n\add* iɛejmiyyen nni tuɣa igga. \f ◼ \fr 11:15 \fk iɛejmiyyen\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*
\v 16 Awarni asen usin-dd \add ɛawed\add* zi marra tiqebbař n Israil inni iwcin ixef nsen s wuř ḥima ad arzun SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, ḥima ad wehhben tiɣarṣa i SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen.
\v 17 \add Ammu\add* ssjehden tageldit n Yahuda u ssmetnen Raḥabɛam, mmis n Suliman, třata n iseggʷusa. Maɣar nitni uyuren třata n iseggʷusa deg webrid n Dawud d Suliman.
\m 
\v 18 Raḥabɛam yiwi Maḥlat, yeǧis n Yarimut, mmis n Dawud, uřa d Abiḥayil, yeǧis n Iliyab, mmis n Yassa, d tamɣart i yixef nnes.
\v 19 Nettat turuw as-dd iḥenjiren\add -a\add*: Yaɛuc, Camarya d Zaham.
\v 20 Awarni as yiwi Maɛka, yeǧis n Abcalum \add d tamɣart\add*. Nettat turuw as-dd Abiya, Ɛattay, Ziza d Calumit.
\v 21 Raḥabɛam tuɣa ittexs Maɛka, yeǧis n Abcalum, aṭṭas x temɣarin nnes nneɣnit d x tiyya nnes. Aqa yiwi Raḥabɛam tmenṭac n temɣarin d settin n tiyya. Netta yejj-dd tmenya u-ɛicrin n iḥenjiren d settin n yessis.
\v 22 Raḥabɛam igga Abiya, mmis n Maɛka, d azeǧif, ḥima ad yiři d řḥakem jar aytmas, ḥima ad t yarr d ajeǧid.
\v 23 \add Raḥabɛam\add* igga s řeɛqeř uca ibḍa marra iḥenjiren nnes x marra timmura n Yahuda d Binyamin u di marra tineddam ifaryen. Netta iwca asen macca s waṭṭas u yarzu asen ijj n ubarru n temɣarin.
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Ahejjem x Yahuda s ufus n Sisak, ajeǧid n Miṣra
\m 
\v 1 Umi tuɣa Raḥabɛam issemten tagelda \add deg ufus nnes\add* u tuɣa ijhed, iwḍa netta zi Ccariɛa n SIDI, netta uřa d marra Israil akides. \x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt [1 Ij. 14:21-31]\x*
\v 2 Deg useggʷas wiss xemsa n ujeǧid Raḥabɛam, imsar - minzi nitni tuɣa ɣewwɣen x SIDI - aqa Cicak, ajeǧid n Miṣra, igeɛɛed ḍidd Urcalim
\v 3 s mitayen-ařef n ikarruten \add n řɛeskar\add*, settin-ařaf n imnayen d ijj n řgens war izemmar ad ittwaḥseb ca i dd-yusin akides zi Miṣra: Ilibiyyen, Isukkiyyen d Ikuciyyen.
\v 4 Netta iṭṭef tineddam ifaryen n Yahuda uca yusa-dd ɣar Urcalim.
\m 
\v 5 Xenni yusa-dd unabi Camɛiya ɣar Raḥabɛam u ɣar řḥukkam n Yahuda, inni tuɣa imunen di Urcalim di ssibbet n Cicak, inna asen: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Minzi kenniw tḥeyydem xafi, x uya ḥeyydeɣ uřa d Necc xawem, jjiɣ kenniw deg ufus n Cicak.’”
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* ssehwan řḥukkam n Israil d ujeǧid ixef nsen, nnan: “SIDI d amsegged!”
\v 7 Umi iẓra SIDI, aqa nitni ssehwan ixef nsen, iffeɣ wawař n SIDI ɣar Camɛiya, inna: “Nitni ssehwan ixef nsen. Necc war ten teḥḥiɣ ca, maca ad asen dd-awyeɣ asenjem deɣya, maḥend asɛar inu s ufus n Cicak war ittwaziǧiɛ ca x Urcalim,
\v 8 maca ad dewřen d imsexxaren nnes, ḥima ad ssnen \add řfarq jar\add* tasexxart i Necc d tsexxart i tgeldiwin n temmura.”
\m 
\v 9 Uca Cicak, ajeǧid n Miṣra, igeɛɛed ḍidd i Urcalim u yiwi marra tixubay n Taddart n SIDI d txubay n taddart n ujeǧid. Netta yiwi \add akis\add* marra, uřa d tiseddariyyin \add n uɛeskari\add* n wureɣ i tuɣa igga Suliman.
\b
\m 
\v 10 Deg wemcan nsent igga ujeǧid Raḥabɛam tiseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* n nnḥas. Igga i-tent deg ifassen n imeqqranen x ireqqasen n tazřa nni tuɣa ittɛessan ɣar wadaf n taddart n ujeǧid.
\v 11 Meřmi ma i ɣa yadef ujeǧid ɣar Taddart n SIDI, imsar, aqa ireqqasen n tazřa usin-dd, arebbun tent u iwyen tent xenni ɛawed ɣar wexxam n ireqqasen n tazřa.
\m 
\v 12 Umi isswaḍeɛ Řaḥabɛam ixef nnes, ijja weɣḍab n SIDI xas, ařami war t iḍeyyeɛ marra. Tuɣa din ɛad di Yahuda timesřayin ṣebḥent.
\v 13 Ajeǧid Raḥabɛam issejhed ixef nnes uca iqqim iḥekkem. Raḥabɛam \add tuɣa\add* ɣares waḥit u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa umi idweř netta d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem sbeɛṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim, di tendint i ixḍar SIDI zi jar marra tiqebbař n Israil ḥima ad din issemten Isem nnes. Yemmas qqaren as Niɛma, \add tenni d\add* Taɛammunit. \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt 1 Ij. 14:21, 31\x*
\v 14 Igga min iǧan d aɛeffan, maɣar war issewjed uř nnes maḥend ad yarzu x SIDI.
\m 
\v 15 Imezruyen n Raḥabɛam, imezwura d ineggura, uřa d imenɣan jar Raḥabɛam d Yarubɛam di marra ussan, ma nitni war ttwazemmemen ca deg wawařen n unabi Camɛiya d umwařaw Ɛiddu di ṭṭweɛ n listat n jjadira?
\v 16 Raḥabɛam igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud. Mmis Abiya idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 Aɣelleb n Abiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, x Yarubɛam
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenṭac n ujeǧid Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, idweř Abiya d ajeǧid x Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt [1 Ij. 15:1-8]\x*
\v 2 Netta iḥkem třata n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Mixa-Yahu, yeǧis n Uriyil zi Jibɛa. Tuɣa \add din\add* umenɣi jar Abiya d Yarubɛam.
\v 3 Abiya issekkar amenɣi s ijj n řɛeskar n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, arebɛa-myat-ařef n yeryazen ittwafarzen, uca Yarubɛam igga aseddi s temn-myat-ařef n yeryazen ittwafarzen, ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen.
\v 4 Ibedd Abiya x tqiccat n wedrar n Ṣamarayim nni \add iǧan\add* x idurar n Ifrayim, inna: “Sřem ɣari, Yarubɛam d marra Israil!
\v 5 Ma war tessinem ca aqa SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, iwca tagelda x Israil s yijj n řɛahd n tmeǧaḥt i Dawud u i iḥenjiren nnes i řebda?
\v 6 \add Maca\add* Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, amsexxar n Suliman, mmis n Dawud, ikkar uca iɣewweɣ x sidis nnes.
\v 7 Iryazen ixwan, ayt i war isekkwin, usin-dd ɣares uca ssjehden ixef nsen ḍidd i Raḥabɛam, mmis n Suliman, umi Raḥabɛam tuɣa ɛad d ameẓyan d aḥnin n wuř u war izemmar akidsen imqudda.
\v 8 Uca řexxu, ittɣiř awem ad tiřim tjehdem x tgeldit n SIDI, tenni \add iǧan\add* deg ifassen n iḥenjiren n Dawud. Waxxa, kenniw s yijj n řɣaci ameqqran i teǧam, maca ɣarwem iɛejmiyyen n wureɣ nni igga Yarubɛam d irebbiten i kenniw. \f ◼ \fr 13:8 \fk iɛejmiyyen\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*
\v 9 Ma war tenḍarem kenniw ikehhanen n SIDI, arraw n Harun d warraw n Lawi, u teggim i yixef nwem ikehhanen am mammec \add tt tteggen\add* řegnus di \add marra\add* timmura? Marra wenni dd-yusin s yijj n ufunas, ameẓyan n tfunast, u s sebɛa n icarriyyen i ixsen ad ittwagg d akehhan, aqa idweř d akehhan n yinni war iǧin ca d irebbiten.
\v 10 Maca xaneɣ, aqa SIDI d AREBBI nneɣ, u neccin war xas nḥeyyed ca, u ikehhanen nni isexxaren i SIDI, aqa aten d arraw n Harun, u Ilawiyyen \add bedden akidsen\add* di řxedmet.
\v 11 Kuř ṣṣbeḥ d tmeddit ssbexxaran tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i SIDI. Uca \add ḥḍan\add* ɛawed x řebxur ittfuḥen d usettef n weɣrum n wescan x tzewḍa tezdeg u x řqendiř n wureɣ u x řefnarat, ḥima ad tent ssarɣen kuř tameddit, maɣar neccin nxezzar ɣar tsexxart n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, maca kenniw tḥeyydem xas.
\v 12 Xzarem, AREBBI aqa-t akidneɣ ɣar zzatneɣ, u ɣarneɣ uřa d ikehhanen nnes ak-d řebwaq i usuḍi s wesruddeḥ, maḥend ad daysen suḍen s wesruddeḥ. \add A\add* ayt n Israil, war ttmenɣam ca ak-d SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, maɣar kenniw war tfřiḥim ca.”
\b
\m 
\v 13 \add Maca\add* Yarubɛam ijja \add ict n tesɣart n yeryazen nnes\add* ad ggen ict n ddura maḥend ad ggen taxceft ɣar ḍeffar nsen. Nitni tuɣa aten zzat i wudem n Yahuda, u ɣar ḍeffar \add n yeryazen n Yahuda\add* tuɣa din řfex.
\v 14 \add Umi\add* nqeřben \add ayt n\add* Yahuda, ẓrin, aqa amenɣi tuɣa-t zi zzat d zi ḍeffar. Nitni sɣuyen ɣar SIDI uca suḍen ikehhanen di řebwaq.
\v 15 Iryazen n Yahuda ssgeɛɛden deg iɣuyyan n umenɣi u řami ssgeɛɛden iryazen n Yahuda deg iɣuyyan, imsar, aqa AREBBI iwta Yarubɛam d marra Israil zzat i tiṭṭawin n Abiya d Yahuda.
\v 16 Arrawen n Israil arewřen zzat i wudem n Yahuda uca AREBBI igga i-ten deg ufus nsen.
\v 17 Abiya ak-d řgens nnes, wtin ten s ict n tecti d tameqqrant, minzi wḍan \add zzaysen\add* xemsa-myat-ařef n yeryazen ittwafarzen zi Israil.
\v 18 \add Ammu\add* i dewřen ayt n Israil nnbehtřen di řweqt nni, maca ayt n Yahuda dewřen jehden, minzi ttecřen x SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen.
\v 19 Abiya iḍfar Yarubɛam uca iṭṭef zzayes tineddam Bayt-Il ak-d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen, Yacana ak-d dcurat nnes d Ifrun ak-d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen.
\v 20 War teqqim ɛad jjehd ɣar Yarubɛam deg wussan n Abiya. Ɣar uneggar iwta i-t SIDI, ařami immut.
\m 
\v 21 Abiya \add maca\add* idweř yarenni di jjehd. Netta yiwi arbeɛṭac n temɣarin i yixef nnes u ijja-dd tnayen u-ɛicrin n warrawen d seṭṭac n yessis.
\v 22 Min iqqimen n imezruyen n Abiya, am tebridin nnes am wawařen nnes, aqa man aya \add marra\add* ittwazemmem deg wedlis n tɣuri n unabi Ɛiddu.
\v 23 Abiya igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes uca neḍřen t di tendint n Dawud, uca mmis Asa idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. Deg wussan nnes tuɣa din ɛecra n iseggʷusa n řhudnet di temmurt.
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Aɣelleb n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda, x Zaraḥ
\m 
\v 1 Asa igga \add min iǧan\add* nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nnes. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt [1 Ij. 15:9-12]\x*
\v 2 Netta ikkes iɛalṭaren n \add irebbiten\add* iɣriben d řegɛudi uca yarẓa imayḍuten \add iqeddsen\add* uca ihdem tirebbin n cwarti.
\v 3 Netta inna i Yahuda, ad arzun SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen uca ad ḍfaren Ccariɛa d tewṣeyyet.
\v 4 Netta ikkes \add ɛawed\add* řegɛudi d ipilaren n arebbi n tfuct zi marra tineddam n Yahuda. Tageldit tuɣa ɣares řhudnet sadu netta.
\v 5 Ibna tineddam ifaryen di Yahuda maɣar tammurt tuɣa dayes řhudnet. War tuɣi din amenɣi akides deg iseggʷusa nni, minzi SIDI iwca as řhudnet.
\v 6 Netta inna i Yahuda: “Ejj aneɣ ad nebna tineddam-a uca ad tent nessar s řeḥyuḍ d lburjat d tewwura d iɛumad i ubelleɛ, maɣar tammurt ɛad zzatneɣ \add s řhudnet\add*, minzi neccin narzu x SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, narzu xas u Netta iwca aneɣ řhudnet.” U nitni bnan uca feřḥen.
\m 
\v 7 Asa tuɣa ɣares ijj n řɛeskar n teřt-myat-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* zi Yahuda, inni iksin taseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* tameqqrant d lansa, mitayen u-tmenyin-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* zi Binyamin, inni yarebbun taseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* u zemmaren x řqews. Nitni marra tuɣa aten d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen.
\m 
\v 8 Iffeɣ Akuci, qqaren as Zaraḥ \add i umenɣi\add* akidsen s yijj n řɛeskar n ijj n melyun \add n yeryazen\add* d teřt-mya n ikarruten. Netta yusa-dd ař Marica.
\v 9 Iffeɣ Asa i umsagar akides uca sedden nitni ixef nsen i umenɣi di teɣzurt n Ṣafata ɣar Marica.
\v 10 Asa iřaɣa ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnes, inna: “\add A\add* SIDI, aya isheř xak ḥima ad tadfed jar \add yenni deg\add* waṭṭas d \add yenni\add* war ɣar iǧi jjehd. Ɛawen aneɣ, \add a\add* SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, maɣar nettceř xak u nusa-dd qibač i řɣaci-ya s Yisem nnec. \add A\add* SIDI, Cek d AREBBI nneɣ, war ttejji uřa d ijj n weryaz ad akidek immɛařa.”
\v 11 Uca SIDI iwta ayt n Kuc zzat i wudem n Asa d Yahuda, uca arewřen \add ayt n\add* Kuc.
\v 12 Asa d řgens i tuɣa akides, ḍfaren ten ař Jarar. Wḍan aṭṭas zeg \add ayt n\add* Kuc ařami war zemmaren ad bedden ɛad, minzi nitni ttwaɣeřben zzat i wudem n SIDI d řɛeskar nnes. Nitni ṭṭfen ict n tkeccaḍt d tameqqrant.
\v 13 Nitni wtin marra tineddam i dd-innḍen i Jarar, maɣar arrehbet n SIDI \add tewḍa-dd\add* xasent. Nitni keccḍen marra tineddam, maɣar tuɣa tban-dd daysent aṭṭas n tkeccaḍt.
\v 14 Nitni hedmen uřa d iqiḍan n řmař uca ṭṭfen uǧi d iřeɣman. \add Xenni\add* ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim.
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Amenɣi n Asa ḍidd i weɛbed n l’aṣnam
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd Arruḥ n AREBBI x Ɛazarya, mmis n Ɛudid.
\v 2 Netta yuyur ibedd zzat i Asa, inna as: “Seř-dd ɣari, Asa d marra \add ayt n\add* Yahuda d Binyamin! SIDI aqa-t akidwem u kenniw akides. Mařa tarezzum xas, Netta ad kenniw yarr ad t tafem, maca mařa kenniw tḥeyydem xas, ad xawem iḥeyyed uřa d Netta.
\v 3 Aṭṭas n wussan i iqqim Israil břa AREBBI n tidett u břa ijj n ukehhan issɣaran u břa Ccariɛa.
\v 4 Mařa dewřen-dd nitni ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, di řeḥṣaret u arzun xas, ijja i-ten ad t afen.
\v 5 Deg wussan nni war din tuɣi řehna i wenni dd-iffɣen u i wenni yareggʷḥen, maɣar aqa din aṭṭas n řeḥweř jar marra imezdaɣ n temmura.
\v 6 \add Ijj n\add* řgens ittwaɛfes zeg ijj n řgens \add nneɣni\add*, u ict n tendint zeg ict n tendint \add nneɣnit\add*, maɣar AREBBI issiggʷed i-ten s kuř řeḥṣařet.
\v 7 Kenniw \add maca\add* iřim d iryazen, war ttejjim ad arxun ifassen nwem, maɣar aqa din řmunet i řxedmet nwem.”
\v 8 Umi Asa isřa awařen-a d nnubuwa n unabi Ɛudid, issejhed ixef nnes uca issbeɛɛed nnɛawat n l’aṣnam zi marra tammurt n Yahuda d Binyamin u zi marra tineddam nni tuɣa iṭṭef x idurar n Ifrayim uca iɛdeř aɛalṭar n SIDI, wenni \add iǧan\add* zzat i wesqif n wadaf \add i Zzawect Tameqqrant\add* n SIDI.
\v 9 Issmun marra Yahuda d Binyamin, uřa d ibarraniyyen zeg Ifrayim, Manassa u Cimɛun, maɣar aṭṭas zi Israil ɛdun ɣares, umi nitni ẓrin, aqa SIDI, AREBBI nnes, tuɣa-t akides.
\v 10 Nitni munen di Urcalim deg uyur wiss třata, deg useggʷas wiss xemmesṭac n tgelda n Asa.
\v 11 Deg wass nni wehhben nitni sebɛa-mya n ifunasen d tfunasin d sebɛa-ařaf n wuǧi d tɣarṣt i SIDI zi tkeccaḍt i kidsen iwyen.
\v 12 Nitni udfen ɣar ijj n Řɛahd maḥend ad arzun SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen, s marra uř nsen u s marra řeɛmar nsen.
\v 13 Marra wenni war yarezzun x SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaneɣ, am umeẓyan am umeqqran, am weryaz am temɣart.
\v 14 Nitni jjuǧen i SIDI s tmijja tejhed u s usřewřiw, ɣar wesruddeḥ n řebwaq d waccawen n icarri.
\v 15 Marra Yahuda tfarḥ x tjaǧit, maɣar nitni ggin tt s marra uř nsen umi nitni arzun xas s marra arḍa nsen, u Netta ijja i-ten ad t afen uca SIDI iwca asen řhudnet zi marra iɣezdisen nsen.
\v 16 Issḥeyyed Asa uřa d ḥennas Maɛka zi jjehd nnes, maɣar nettat tuɣa tegga ict n jjɛifect n řexyař i trebbit n cwarti. Asa iceqqar jjɛifect nnes, iřbez i-tt uca isscemḍ i-tt ɣar teɣzart n Qidrun. \x ◘ \xo 15:16 \xt 1 Ij. 15:13\x*
\v 17 War ttwaḥeyydent řegɛudi, maca uř n Asa tuɣa icḍar \add nican i SIDI\add*, marra ussan \add n tudart\add* nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:17 \xt 1 Ij. 15:14\x*
\v 18 Tiwhibin iqeddsen n babas d min tuɣa issqeddes netta \add s yixef nnes\add* yiwyi-t di Taddart n AREBBI, uřa d tiwhibin nnes iqeddsen: nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ \add nneɣni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 15:18 \xt 1 Ij. 15:15\x*
\v 19 War din iqqim \add ɛad\add* umenɣi ař aseggʷas wiss xemsa u-třatin n tgelda n Asa.
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Řɛahd n Asa ak-d Aram ḍidd i Israil
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss setta u-třatin n tgelda n Asa, iffeɣ Baca, ajeǧid n Israil, \add i umenɣi\add* ak-d Yahuda. Ibna Rama, ḥima war ittejji uřa d ijj ad iffeɣ ɣar barra niɣ ad dd-iɛqeb ɣar Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 16:1 \xt [1 Ij. 15:16-24]\x*
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* iksi Asa marra nnuqart d wureɣ zeg ixxamen n txubay zi Taddart n SIDI u zi taddart n ujeǧid uca issekk \add marra\add* aya ɣar Binhadad, ajeǧid n Aram, wenni tuɣa izeddɣen di Dimacq, inna:
\v 3 “\add Aqa din\add* ijj n řɛahd jar ayi d cek, jar baba d babac. Xzar, necc ad ac dd-ssekkeɣ nnuqart d wureɣ. Ruḥ cek, fsiy řɛahd nnec ak-d Baɛca, ajeǧid n Israil, maḥend netta ad igeɛɛed ad xafi iggʷej.”
\v 4 Binhadad isřa ɣar ujeǧid Asa u issekk ikumandaren n řɛeskar nni ɣares \add iǧan\add* ɣar tneddam n Israil. Nitni ɣeřben x Ɛiyun d Dan d Abal-Mayim uřa x marra tineddam n řexzen n Naftali.
\v 5 Umi isřa Baɛca man aya, imsar, aqa netta issbedd řebni n Rama uca ismeḥ di řxedmet nnes.
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* yiwi ujeǧid Asa marra \add ayt n\add* Yahuda u nitni ksen iẓra n Rama uřa d tiḥenya nnes i zi tuɣa tt ibna Baɛca, uca ibna zzayes Jabɛa d Miṣfa.
\m 
\v 7 Deg wussan nni yusa-dd umwařaw Ḥanani ɣar Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda, inna as: “Minzi tᵉttecřed x ujeǧid n Aram u war iǧi x SIDI, AREBBI nnec, x uya yarweř řɛeskar n ujeǧid n Aram zeg ufus nnec. \f ◼ \fr 16:7 \fk Deg wussan nni\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘di řweqt nni ...’\f*
\v 8 Ma war tuɣi uřa d \add ayt n\add* Kuc d \add ayt n\add* Libiya s yijj n řɛeskar ameqqran ak-d waṭṭas n ikarruten d imnayen? Maca minzi tᵉttecřed x SIDI, iwca i-ten Netta deg ufus nnec,
\v 9 maɣar tḥewwment tiṭṭawin n SIDI x tammurt am tekmeř, ḥima ad ibedd s jjehd ak-d yinni iǧan s wuř imun \add akides\add*. Di man aya teggid tubbuheřya, maɣar zi řexxu d tsawent ad \add din\add* iřin imenɣan akidek.”
\v 10 Asa ihaj x umwařaw uca ijja ad t ggen deg ukeccuḍ di řeḥbes, maɣar \add ammu i\add* d as tuɣa isxeḍ x uya. Di řweqt nni d ict iḥṣar Asa \add ca\add* zi řgens.
\m 
\v 11 Xzar, imezruyen n Asa, imezwura d ineggura, xzar, aqa ttwazemmemen deg wedlis n ijeǧiden n Yahuda d Israil.
\v 12 Deg useggʷas wiss tesɛa u-třatin n tgelda nnes ihřec Asa zeg iḍaren. \add Maca\add* di tqiccet n řehřac nnes uřa řami tuɣa ihřec, war yarzu ca x SIDI, maca x imesgenfan \add waha\add*.
\v 13 Asa igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Immut deg useggʷas wiss waḥit u-rebɛin zi řeḥkamet nnes.
\v 14 Neḍřen t deg wenḍeř i tuɣa igga i yixef nnes di tendint n Dawud uca ssarsen t x qama i tuɣa tɛemmar s řeɛṭur d marra min iǧan d ddarbat \add ifarzen\add* zi min ixeǧḍen s ufus n uḥrayfi. Nitni qqden as timessi d tameqqrant aṭṭas.
\b
\b
\c 17
\s1 Řehkamet ijehden n Yahucafaṭ x Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Mmis Yahucafaṭ idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes u netta issejhed ixef nnes ḍidd i Israil.
\v 2 Netta yiwi řɛeskar ɣar marra tineddam ifaryen n Yahuda u igga řɛeskarat \add n uḥewwes\add* di temmurt n Yahuda u di tneddam n Ifrayim, tinni i tuɣa iṭṭef babas Asa.
\v 3 SIDI tuɣa-t ak-d Yahucafaṭ, maɣar netta iḍfar ibriden imezwura n babas Dawud, war yarzu ca x ‘Ibaɛlen’, \f ◼ \fr 17:3 \fk Ibaɛlen\ft - irebbiten iɣriben, war ǧin ca d Arebbi, maca d ccwaṭen. Isem n yijj: ‘Baɛl’.\f*
\v 4 maca \add yarzu\add* x AREBBI n babas uca yuyur di tweṣṣa nnes, war iggi am \add t igga\add* Israil.
\v 5 SIDI issemten tagelda \add tenni\add* deg ufus nnes, u marra Yahuda yiwi tarzifin i Yahucafaṭ. Idweř ɣares aṭṭas n wagřa d ccan.
\v 6 Uř nnes ittwassemḥeḍ deg ibriden n SIDI u netta ikkes uřa d řegɛudi d trebbin n cwarti zi Yahuda.
\m 
\v 7 Deg useggʷas wiss třata n řeḥkamet nnes issekk \add ict n tebrat\add* i řḥukkam nnes, i Bin-Ḥayil, Ɛubadya, Zakariyya, Nataniyil d Mixa-Yahu, ḥima ad ssɣaren di tneddam n Yahuda.
\v 8 \add Ruḥen\add* akidsen Ilawiyyen Camɛiya, Natanya, Zabadya, Ɛasa’il, Camiramut, Yunatan, Tubiya d Ṭub-Aduniya, \add marra nitni d\add* Ilawiyyen, uca uřa d ikehhanen Alicamaɛ d Yahuram \add ruḥen\add* akidsen.
\v 9 Nitni ssɣaren di Yahuda u tuɣa ɣarsen adlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n SIDI. Kkin marra tineddam n Yahuda uca ssɣaren řgens.
\v 10 Tusa-dd arrehbet n SIDI x marra tigeldiwin n temmura i-dd-innḍen i Yahuda, ařami war ssekkarent amenɣi ak-d Yahucafaṭ.
\v 11 Zeg Ifilisṭiniyyen iwyen tarzifin d nnuqart am ljizya i Yahucafaṭ. Uřa d Aɛraben ssekken as uǧi: sebɛa-ařaf u-sebɛa-mya n icarriyyen d sebɛa-ařaf u-sebɛa-mya n imuyan.
\v 12 Ammu i idweř Yahucafaṭ yarni di řemɣaret ař ṭṭarf uca ibna lqelɛat d tneddam n řexzen di Yahuda.
\v 13 Tuɣa ɣares aṭṭas n řxedmet di tneddam n Yahuda, uřa d iɛeskariyyen, ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, di Urcalim.
\v 14 D wanita d řqedd nsen ɛlaḥsab tudrin n ibabaten nsen. Di Yahuda \add aqa ina\add* d řqebṭanat x řuřuf: ameqqran Adna u akides teřt-myat-ařef n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen.
\v 15 Ɣar uɣezdis nnes řqebṭan Yahunatan, akides mitayen u-tmanyin-ařef \add n yeryazen\add*.
\v 16 Ɣar uɣezdis nnes \add ameqqran\add* Ɛamasya, mmis n Zikri, wenni tuɣa isebbřen ixef nnes s řxaḍar, u akides mitayen-ařef n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen.
\v 17 Zi Binyamin \add tuɣa\add* Aliyadaɛ, ijj n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, \add d ameqqran nsen\add*, u akides mitayen-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* s řqews d tseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* i umenɣi.
\v 18 Ɣar uɣezdis nnes \add ameqqran\add* Yahuzabad u akides mya u-tmanyin-ařef \add n yeryazen\add*, \add marra\add* ḥezzmen i umenɣi.
\v 19 Ina tuɣa ttsexxaren i ujeǧid, břa inni i tuɣa igga ujeǧid x tneddam ifaryen di marra Yahuda.
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Řɛahd n Yahucafaṭ ak-d Axab
\m 
\v 1 Yahucafaṭ ɣares agřa d ccan s ufeyyeḍ, u netta igga ad idweř d aḍeggʷař ak-d Axab. \x ◘ \xo 18:1 \xt [1 Ij. 22:2-36]\x*
\v 2 Awarni ca n iseggʷusa ihwa-dd ɣar Axab, ɣar Samarya. Axab iɣarṣ i waṭṭas n wuǧi d ifunasen i řgens i tuɣa akides iǧan uca iɣwa t ad iffeɣ \add ɣar umenɣi\add* ɣar Ramut-Jilɛad.
\v 3 Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, inna i Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda: “Zeɛma ad kidi teffɣed ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad?” Inna Yahucafaṭ i ujeǧid n Israil: “Necc \add ad iřiɣ\add* am cek, řgens inu am řgens nnec u neccin ad kidek \add neffeɣ\add* ɣar umenɣi.”
\m 
\v 4 Inna Yahucafaṭ \add ɛawed\add* i ujeǧid n Israil: “Seqsa ɛafak ass-a x wawař n SIDI.”
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* issmun ujeǧid n Israil inabiyyen, arebɛa-mya n yeryazen, inna asen: “Ma ad ffɣeɣ ɣar umenɣi ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad niɣ ad ggeɣ bnaqes?” Nnan: “Geɛɛed, maɣar AREBBI ad ten iwc deg ufus n ujeǧid.”
\v 6 \add Maca\add* Yahucafaṭ inna: “Ma war da ca ɛad anabi n SIDI, maḥend ad \add nzemmar\add* ad t nesseqsa?”
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid n Israil i Yahucafaṭ: “Aqa da ɛad ijj n weryaz zzayes i nzemmar ad nesseqsa SIDI. Maca necc carheɣ t, maɣar netta war d ayi ittnebba ɛemmarṣ s min iṣebḥen, maca mɣir s \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan. Aqa d Mixa-Yahu, mmis n Yimla.” Inna Yahucafaṭ “War ttejji ajeǧid ad issiweř amenni!”
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa-dd ujeǧid n Israil i yijj n umsexxar amcenneɛ, inna: “Deɣya awi-dd Mixa-Yahu, mmis n Yimla.”
\v 9 Ajeǧid n Israil d Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, qqimen \add din\add*, kuř ijj x řɛarc nnes, yarḍen arruḍ n ijeǧiden, \add qqimen\add* x unedrar ɣar wadaf n tewwart \add n tendint\add* n Samarya u marra inabiyyen tuɣa ttnebban zzat i wudem nsen.
\v 10 Ṣidqiya, mmis n Kanɛana, tuɣa igga i yixef nnes accawen n wuzzař, inna: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘S yina i ɣa tessnuqqbed ayt n Aram ař ten ɣa teqḍiḍ marra.’”
\v 11 Marra inabiyyen tuɣa ttnebban kifkif, nnan: “Geɛɛed ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad, ad tiřid tfeřḥed, minzi SIDI ad ten iwc deg ufus n ujeǧid.”
\m 
\v 12 Areqqas nni tuɣa iṭṭfen \add abrid\add* ḥima ad iřaɣa i Mixa-Yahu, issiweř akides, inna: “Xzar xenni, awařen n inabiyyen \add axmi dd-ffɣen\add* zeg ijj n uqemmum s řxir ɣar ujeǧid. Ttzawgeɣ ad iřin wawařen nnec am wawařen nsen, ini min iṣebḥen.”
\v 13 \add Maca\add* Mixa-Yahu inna: “S tidett am iddar SIDI, min d ayi ɣa yini AREBBI, ad t iniɣ.”
\v 14 \add Umi\add* dd-yusa netta ɣar ujeǧid, inna as ujeǧid: “Mixa, ma ad neffeɣ neccin ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad niɣ ad negg bnaqes?” Inna as netta: “Gaɛɛdem, ad tiřim tfeřḥem, minzi nitni ad ttwaggen deg ufus nwem.”
\v 15 Inna as ujeǧid: “Mecḥař n twařawin i d ayi ittxeṣṣa ad ac ssjaǧeɣ, war d ayi tennid mɣir tidett s Yisem n SIDI?”
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inna wanita: “Necc ẓriɣ marra Israil ttwabezzɛen x idurar am wuǧi i war ɣar iǧi Umeksaw. Iqqar SIDI: ‘Ina war ɣarsen bu isiditen, ejj \add kuř\add* aryaz ad dd-idweř ɣar taddart nnes di řehna.’”
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid n Israil i Yahucafaṭ: “Ma war d ac nniɣ: ‘Netta war xafi ittnebba ca di min iṣebḥen, \add maca\add* mɣir s \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan’?”
\m 
\v 18 \add Xas uca\add* inna wanita \add ɛawed\add*: “S uya seř i wawař n SIDI. Aqa ẓriɣ SIDI iqqim x řɛarc nnes u marra řɛeskar n ujenna ibedd x yefus nnes d uzeřmaḍ nnes,
\v 19 uca SIDI inna: ‘Man wen i ɣa iɣwan Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, ḥima ad igeɛɛed, ad iwḍa di Ramut di Jilɛad?’ Wa inna ammu u win inna ammu.
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ-dd ijj n arruḥ, ibedd-dd zzat i wudem n SIDI, inna: ‘Necc ad t ɣwiɣ.’ Isseqsa t SIDI: ‘S min zi?’ \x ◘ \xo 18:20 \xt Ayub 1:6\x*
\v 21 Netta inna: ‘Necc ad dd-ffɣeɣ u ad dewřeɣ d ijj n buḥbeř issxarriqen deg uqemmum n marra inabiyyen nnes.’ U Netta inna: ‘Ad tawḍed maḥend ad t teɣwid. Ffeɣ, egg amenni!’
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, xzar, SIDI iwca ijj n buḥbeř issxarriqen deg ufus n inabiyyen nnec u SIDI ibarreḥ xak s min iǧan d aɛeffan.”
\m 
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* iqarreb-dd Ṣidqiya, mmis n Kanɛana, ɣar Mixa-Yahu, iwwet i-t ɣar uɣesmir, inna: “X man abrid tuɣa izemmar ad zzayi iɛdu Arruḥ n SIDI ḥima ad kidek issiweř?”
\v 24 Inna Mixa-Yahu: “Xzar, ad t tẓared deg wass nni di ɣa temhafed zeg \add ijj n\add* wexxam ɣar wexxam nneɣni ḥima ad tessnuffared ixef nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 18:24 \xt 1 Ij. 20:30; 1 Ij. 22:25\x*
\v 25 Ajeǧid n Israil inna: “Ṭṭfem Mixa-Yahu, nedhem ɛawed t ɣar Amun, ameqqran n tendint, u ɣar Yuwac, mmis n ujeǧid,
\v 26 ad tinim: ‘Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid: Nḍarem wa di řeḥbes u seccem t s weɣrum n řeḥṣaret u s waman n řeḥṣaret ař ɣa dewřeɣ di řehna.’”
\v 27 \add Xas uca\add* inna Mixa-Yahu: “Mařa tɛeqbed-dd \add ca n wass\add* di řehna, xenni SIDI war xafi issiweř!” Uca inna \add ɛawed\add*: “Sřem-dd a řegnus, marra \add kenniw\add*!”
\m 
\v 28 Awarni as iffeɣ-dd ujeǧid n Israil ak-d Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad.
\v 29 Inna ujeǧid n Israil i Yahucafaṭ: “Necc ad beddřeɣ arruḍ, \add xenni\add* ad dd-ffɣeɣ ɣar umenɣi. \add Maca\add* cek \add tzemmared\add* ad tyarḍed arruḍ nnec!” Ajeǧid n Israil igga arruḍ war iǧi nnes uca ffɣen-dd ɣar umenɣi.
\v 30 Ajeǧid n Aram tuɣa yumur imeqqranen n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add* nni ɣares \add iǧan\add*, inna: “Ittxeṣṣa awem war tᵉttmenɣim ca ak-d umeqqran niɣ ak-d umeẓyan, mɣir ak-d ujeǧid n Israil!”
\v 31 Umi imeqqranen n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add* ẓrin Yahucafaṭ, imsar, aqa nitni nnan: “Aqa d wa, ajeǧid n Israil!” Nitni nnḍen as ḥima akides mmenɣen, maca Yahucafaṭ isɣuy, uca SIDI iwca as afus u AREBBI issḥeyyed i-ten xas.
\v 32 Umi ẓrin imeqqranen n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add*, aqa netta tuɣa war iǧi d ajeǧid n Israil, imsar, aqa dewřen-dd x webrid nsen, war t areddfen ɛad.
\m 
\v 33 \add Xenni\add* iɛeyyen ijj n weryaz řqews s řbař nnes d acemřař uca iřqef \add fřitca\add* ajeǧid n Israil jar wawaḍ n iɣaǧen n warruḍ nnes n wuzzař. \add Řexdenni\add* inna wanita i wenni ineddhen akarru: “Qřeb afus nnec, suffeɣ ayi-dd zi řɛeskar, maɣar aqa yezmeɣ.”
\v 34 Deg wass nni idweř umenɣi iwɛar aṭṭas. Iqqim ujeǧid n Israil ibedd deg ukarru ař tameddit \add deg umenɣi\add* ak-d ayt n Aram, immut ɣar řweqt n uɣeǧay n tfuct.
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 Yahucafaṭ d umwařaw
\m 
\v 1 Iɛqeb-dd Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ɣar taddart nnes di Urcalim di řehna.
\v 2 Yahu, mmis n Ḥanani, amwařaw, iffeɣ-dd ɣares ḥima ad t iřqa, inna i ujeǧid Yahucafaṭ: “Ma cek teggid twiza i uɛeffan u ad texsed inni iɛiffen SIDI? Ammu i xak dd-yusa uduqqez n weɣḍab zi zzat n wudem n SIDI.
\v 3 Waxxa amenni ittwaf dayek min iṣebḥen, maɣar tekksed tirebbin n cwarti zi temmurt uca tesswejded uř nnec i tarezzut x AREBBI.”
\m 
\v 4 Yahucafaṭ iqqim izeddeɣ di Urcalim uca iffeɣ ɛawed jar řgens, zi Bi’r-Sebɛa ɣar idurar n Ifrayim, uca yarra i-ten ad dd-dewřen ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen.
\v 5 Netta yařeqqem řquḍat di temmurt, di marra tineddam ifaryen n Yahuda, zi tendint ař tandint.
\v 6 Netta inna i řquḍat: “Xzarem min ɣa teggem, maɣar war tḥekkmem i iwdan, maca i SIDI u Netta aqa iḥḍar akidwem deg weḥkam.
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ad xawem tiři tiggʷudi n SIDI. Ḥḍam u ggem t, maɣar ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, war iǧi řɣecc, Netta war ittegg s wudmawen u war ikessi tirzifin.”
\m 
\v 8 Umi dd-ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim, igga Yahucafaṭ di Urcalim ɛawed \add ca\add* n Ilawiyyen d ikehhanen d izeǧifen n \add tudrin n\add* ibabaten n Israil i udebbar n řeḥkam n SIDI u i ddɛawi.
\v 9 Netta yumur i-ten, inna: “Ggem s tiggʷudi n SIDI, s řaman u s yijj n wuř \add nican\add* imun.
\v 10 Ɣar kuř ddeɛwet i d awem i d ɣa yawyen aytmatwem nni izeddɣen di tneddam nsen, jar idammen d idammen u jar Ccariɛa d řumur d tweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ, ittxeṣṣa ad asen tɛeřmem, maḥend war xawem ssarebbun ddenb zzat i SIDI, ařami xawem dd ɣa iwḍa uduqqez d ameqqran n weɣḍab u x aytmatwem. Ggem amenni, ařami war tᵉssarebbum ddenb x yixef nwem.
\v 11 Xzarem, Amarya d akehhan ameqqran i xawem iǧan di marra ddeɛwet n SIDI, u Zabadya, mmis n Ismaɛil, řḥakem x taddart n Yahuda, aqa-t x kuř ddeɛwet n ujeǧid. Uřa d imeḥḍayen, Ilawiyyen, \add aqa aten din\add* zzat i wudem nwem. Iřim d iryazen u ggem \add t\add*, uca SIDI ad yiři ak-d wenni iṣeřḥen.”
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Aɣelleb n Yahucafaṭ x Mu’ab d Ɛammun
\m 
\v 1 Awarni uya imsar, aqa ayt n Mu’ab d ayt n Ɛammun, d \add inneɣni\add* akidsen zeg Imaɛuniyyen usin-dd maḥend ad mmenɣen ak-d Yahucafaṭ.
\v 2 Usin-dd \add ireqqasen\add*, ɛawden i Yahucafaṭ, nnan: “Aqa aṭṭas n řɣaci usin-dd ḥima ad kidek mmenɣen zeg ujemmaḍin n řebḥar, zi Aram. Xzar, nitni di Ḥaṣṣun-Tamar, ixs ad yini Ɛayn-Jadi.”
\m 
\v 3 Yahucafaṭ iggʷed uca inḍar tiṭṭawin nnes ɣar SIDI. Netta ijja ad barrḥen s uẓummi di marra Yahuda.
\v 4 Ssmunen \add ayt n\add* Yahuda maḥend ad arzun twiza n SIDI. Nitni usin-dd uřa zi marra tineddam n Yahuda, ḥima ad arzun x SIDI.
\v 5 Ibedd Yahucafaṭ deg wegraw \add n řgens\add* n Yahuda d Urcalim, di Taddart n SIDI, zzat i řemraḥ n jdid, inna:
\m 
\v 6 “\add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nneɣ, ma Cek war teǧid ca d AREBBI n ijenwan d Řḥakem x marra tigeldiwin n řegnus? Deg ufus nnec \add immars\add* jjehd d tzemmar, ařami war izemmar uřa d ijj ad iqqim ibedd zzatek.
\v 7 \add A\add*, AREBBI nneɣ, ma war tuẓẓiřed ca x imezdaɣ n temmurt-a zzat i wudem n řgens nnec Israil uca tewcid \add tammurt\add* i řebda i zzariɛet n Ibrahim, \add ameddukkeř\add* nnec iɛizzen?
\v 8 Nitni qqimen zeddɣen dayes uca bnan dayes ict n Zzawect Iqeddsen i Cek, i Yisem nnec, uca nnan:
\v 9 ‘Mařa iřqef aneɣ ca n řɣar, \add axmi\add* ssif n řeḥkam niɣ ṭṭaɛun niɣ řaẓ, xenni ad nbedd zzat i Taddart-a u zzat i wudem nnec, maɣar Isem nnec aqa-t di Taddart-a. Ad xak dd-nřaɣa zi řeḥṣaret nneɣ uca \add xenni\add* Cek ad \add ɣarneɣ\add* tesřed u ad \add aneɣ\add* tessnejmed.
\v 10 Uca řexxu, xzar, ayt n Ɛammun d \add ayt n\add* Mu’ab d yinni zeg idurar n Saɛir - inni i umi war tejjid ca ayt n Israil ad ɣarsen dd-adfen \add ɣar temmurt nsen\add*, umi dd-usin zi temmurt n Miṣra, minzi kkin asen-dd \add zeg webrid nneɣni\add* u war ten areddǧen,
\v 11 xzarem, nitni xsen ad aneɣ xeǧṣen uca usin-dd ḥima ad aneɣ ssuffɣen zi tesɣart nnec i d aneɣ tewcid d řwart.
\v 12 \add A\add*, AREBBI nneɣ, ma Cek war xasen tḥekkmed ca? Maɣar neccin war xasen nzemmar x řɣaci-ya ameqqran wanita i ɣarneɣ dd-iffɣen u war nessin min ɣa negg, maca \add aqa narra-dd\add* tiṭṭawin nneɣ ɣarek.”
\b
\m 
\v 13 Marra \add ayt n\add* Yahuda bedden zzat i wudem n SIDI, uřa d iḥenjiren imeẓyanin nsen d temɣarin nsen d iḥenjiren nsen.
\v 14 Uca ihwa-dd Arruḥ n SIDI \add din\add* di řwest n wegraw \add n řgens\add* x Yaḥziyil, mmis n Zakariyya, mmis n Banaya, mmis n Yaɛiyil, mmis n Ulawi Mattanya, zeg iḥenjiren n Asaf.
\v 15 Netta inna: “Sřem-dd ɣari, marra \add ayt n\add* Yahuda uřa d kenniw, imezdaɣ n Urcalim, u cek, \add a,\add* ajeǧid Yahucafaṭ! Ammu i d awem iqqar SIDI: ‘War tteggʷdem ca, war ttnexřiɛem ca zi řɣaci-ya ameqqran wanita, minzi amenɣi war iǧi s ufus nneɣ, maca s ufus n AREBBI.
\v 16 Hwam ɣarsen tiwecca. Xzar, nitni ad geɛɛden zi tsawent n Ṣiṣ, u kenniw ad xasen txeccem ɣar uneggar n teɣzurt zzat i řexřa n Yaruwil.
\v 17 Kenniw \add maca\add* war tᵉttmenɣim ca. Kkarem, \add qqimem\add* tbeddem u xzarem, asenjem n SIDI \add ad yiři\add* akidwem, \add a\add* Yahuda d Urcalim! War tteggʷdem ca u war ttnexřiɛem. Tiwecca ffɣem i umsagar akidsen, minzi SIDI aqa-t akidwem.’”
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* yuḍar Yahucafaṭ s uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt, u marra \add ayt n\add* Yahuda d marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim wḍan \add x temmurt\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI ḥima ad bendqen i SIDI.
\v 19 Kkaren Ilawiyyen zeg ayt n Quhat u zeg ayt n Quraḥ ḥima ad ssɛuǧan SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, s ict n tmijja tejhed aṭṭas.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Tiwecca zic kkaren uca ffɣen ɣar řexřa n Taquɛa. Ɣar wuffuɣ nsen ibedd-dd Yahucafaṭ \add din\add*, inna: “Sřem-dd ɣari, \add a\add* Yahuda, d kenniw, imezdaɣ n Urcalim. Amnem di SIDI, AREBBI nwem, \add xenni\add* ad tiřim di řaman. Amnem zi inabiyyen, \add xenni\add* ad tfeřḥem.”
\v 21 Netta imcawar ak-d řgens uca issbedd imedyazen zzat i SIDI d yinni d as i ɣa iṣebbḥen acewwaḍ n Umqeddas, am ɣa yuyuren zzat i wudem n \add yeryazen\add* i iḥezzmen s řesnaḥ, ad inin: “Qadam SIDI, maɣar tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren \add tᵉttɣima\add* i řebda!”
\v 22 Di řweqt řami bdan nitni s usřiwřew d uṣebbeḥ, igga SIDI řefxux x ayt n Ɛammun d Mu’ab u x \add yenni\add* i tuɣa dd-iffɣen ḍidd i Yahuda zeg idurar n Saɛir, uca ttwaɣellben nitni.
\m 
\v 23 Ayt n Ɛammun d \add ayt n\add* Mu’ab kkaren x imezdaɣ n idurar n Saɛir, ḥima ad ten sshellken u ad ten areddǧen. Umi qḍan nitni x imezdaɣ n Saɛir, sshellken ijj wenneɣni.
\v 24 \add Umi\add* dd-yiwiḍ Yahuda ɣar ṣṣumɛet n uḥeṭṭu di řexřa, nḍaren tamuɣři nsen awani asen x řɣaci, u xzar, \add ẓrin\add* mɣir řxecbat tuɣa wḍant x temmurt, uřa d ijj war injim.
\v 25 Yahucafaṭ d řgens nnes usin-dd ḥima ad ṭṭfen takeccaḍt nsen uca ufin ɣarsen aṭṭas n sseřɛet d řxecbat d řeqcuɛ iɣřan uca kksen \add ɛřam kuř zzayes\add* i yixef nsen, ařami war zemmaren ad t arbun. Ttkeccaḍen třata n wussan, maɣar \add tuɣa\add* din aṭṭas.
\b
\m 
\v 26 Deg wass wiss arebɛa munen nitni di řewḍa n Teɣzurt n Lbaraka, minzi din barken SIDI. X uya ggin as i wemcan nni: taɣzurt n Lbaraka, ɣar i řexxu.
\v 27 Awarni uya dewřen-dd marra iryazen n Yahuda d Urcalim. Yuyur Yahucafaṭ ɣar zzat, ḥima ad ɛeqben ɣar Urcalim \add ccuren\add* s řefraḥet, maɣar SIDI tuɣa issfarḥ i-ten x řɛedyan nsen.
\v 28 Am \add ttiraren s\add* lharpat d řgambriyat d řebwaq usin-dd ɣar Urcalim, ɣar Taddart n SIDI.
\v 29 Tuɣa tiggʷudi n AREBBI teřqef marra tigeldiwin n temmura umi sřint, aqa SIDI immneɣ ak-d řɛedyan n Israil.
\v 30 Tufa tgeldit n Yahucafaṭ řhudnet uca AREBBI nnes iwca as řehna zi marra iɣezdisen.
\b
\s1 Řeḥkamet n ujeǧid Yahucafat
\m 
\v 31 Ammu i iḥkem Yahucafaṭ x Yahuda. \add Tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-třatin n iseggʷusa, umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Ɛazuba, yeǧis n Cilḥi. \x ◘ \xo 20:31 \xt [1 Ij. 22:41-51]\x*
\v 32 Netta iḍfar ibriden n babas Asa, war xasen iḥeyyed ca u netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.
\v 33 Mɣir řegɛudi war ttwakksent, maɣar řgens war tuɣi ɛad yarra uř nnes ɣar AREBBI n řejdud nsen.
\v 34 Min iqqimen n imezruyen n Yahucafaṭ, imezwura d ineggura, xzar, aqa man aya \add marra\add* ittwazemmem deg wedlis n imezruyen n Yahu, mmis n Ḥanani, inni igga ad ttwazemmemen deg wedlis n ijeǧiden n Israil.
\m 
\v 35 Awarni uya igga Yahucafaṭ ijj n řɛahd ak-d Axazya, ajeǧid n Israil, wenni iggin tuɛeffna aṭṭas di \add marra min\add* tuɣa igga.
\v 36 Netta iqqen akides ijj n řɛahd, ḥima ad ggen iɣarruba nni i ɣa ineddhen ɣar Tarcic. Nitni bnan iɣarruba \add nni\add* di Ɛiṣyun-Jabar.
\v 37 \add Maca\add* Aliɛazar, mmis n Dudawahu zi Marica, ittnebba x Yahucafaṭ, inna: “Minzi teqqned ijj n řɛahd ak-d Axaziya, aqa SIDI yarẓa řexdayem nnec.” \add Ammu\add* imsar aqa ttwarẓen iɣarruba ařami war zemmaren ad nedhen ɣar Tarcic.
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Řeḥkamet iɛeffnen n Yuram
\m 
\v 1 Yahucafaṭ igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud. Mmis Yahuram idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \x ◘ \xo 21:1 \xt [2 Ij. 8:16-24]\x*
\v 2 Aytmas, iḥenjiren n Yahucafaṭ \add tuɣa aten d\add* Ɛazarya, Yaḥiyil, Zakariyya, Ɛazaryahu, Mixayil d Cafaṭya. Ina marra \add tuɣa aten d\add* iḥenjiren n Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Israil.
\v 3 Babatsen iwca asen aṭṭas n terzifin n nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ iɣřan uřa d tineddam ifaryen di Yahuda, maca tageldit iwca i-tt i Yahuram, maɣar wanita \add tuɣa\add* d amenzu.
\m 
\v 4 \add Umi\add* ikkar-dd Yahuram x tgeldit n babas uca imneɛ di tizemmar nnes, inɣa marra aytmas s ssif, uřa d ca n řḥukkam n Israil.
\v 5 Yahuram \add tuɣa ɣares\add* tnayen u-třatin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tmenya n iseggʷusa di Urcalim.
\v 6 Netta yuyur deg webrid n ijeǧiden n Israil, am mammec tuɣa tegga taddart n Axab, maɣar yeǧis n Axab tedweř d tamɣart nnes. Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.
\v 7 \add Maca\add* SIDI war ixs ad yareddeǧ Dawud di ṭṭweɛ n Řɛahd i igga ak-d Dawud, uca uřa umi \add d as\add* tuɣa inna, aqa ad as iwc řebda ijj n řefnar zzat i tiṭṭawin nnes, i netta u i iḥenjiren nnes.
\m 
\v 8 Deg wussan nnes ixtutteř Idum s uɣewweɣ zi sadu ifassen n Yahuda, uca ggin ijj n ujeǧid x yixef nsen.
\v 9 Iɛdu Yahuram ak-d marra imeqqranen nnes d marra ikarruten nnes \add n umenɣi\add*. Aqa ikkar s ǧiřet u iɣřeb x ayt n Idum inni tuɣa i d as dd-innḍen, i netta u i imeqqranen n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add*.
\v 10 \add Waxxa amenni\add* xtuttřen \add ayt n\add* Idum s uɣewweɣ zi jar ifassen n Yahuda, ař ass-a. Di řweqt nni beɛda iɣewweɣ uřa d Libna, maɣar tuɣa Yahuda iḥeyyed x SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nnes.
\m 
\v 11 Igga Yahuram uřa d řegɛudi x idurar n Yahuda. Netta yarra imezdaɣ n Urcalim ad ssfesden ixef nsen \add s irebbiten nneɣni\add*, \add wah,\add* tuɣa iɛarn Yahuda ɣar man aya.
\v 12 Tiweḍ-dd ɣares ict n tebrat n unabi Iliya, teqqar: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n babac Dawud: ‘Maɣar war tuyured x ibriden n babac Yahucafaṭ u x ibriden n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda,
\v 13 maca tuyured x ibriden n ijeǧiden n Israil, uca tarrid Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim ad ssfesden ixef nsen \add s irebbiten nneɣni\add*, deg webrid n farq-cɣeř n taddart n Axab, u minzi cek tenɣid uřa d aytmac zi taddart n babac, inni tuɣa icnan xak,
\v 14 xzar, \add x uyenni\add* SIDI ad cek iřqef s ict n tecti d tameqqrant jar řgens nnec d iḥenjiren nnec d temɣarin nnec d marra agřa nnec.
\v 15 Cek simant nnec ad tewḍid deg ijj n řehřac n tekrict iqesḥen, ař dd ɣa teffeɣ \add ɛad\add* tekrict nnec ɣar barra zi ssibbet n řehřac i ittduman.’”
\m 
\v 16 SIDI issehweř x Yahuram arruḥ n Ifilisṭiniyyen d Weɛraben, inni izedɣen x uɣezdis n \add ayt n\add* Kuc.
\v 17 Nitni geɛɛden ɣar Yahuda, udfen ɣar tammurt u ksin marra agřa nni \add iǧan\add* di taddart n ujeǧid, uřa d iḥenjiren nnes d temɣarin nnes, ařami war d as iqqim mɣir Yahuyaḥaz, amaẓuẓ n iḥenjiren nnes.
\v 18 Awarni aya iwta i-t SIDI s yijj n řehřac war izemmar ad \add zzayes\add* iggenfa.
\v 19 Umi \add tuɣa netta ihřec ammu\add* ass iḍfar umas, uca teɛdu řweqt ařami ɛdun tnayen n iseggʷusa, imsar, aqa takrict nnes teffeɣ-dd ɣar barra, u netta immut s řeḥřiq d ameqqran. Řgens nnes war d as issarɣ ca tmessi am \add ggin\add* timessi i řejdud nnes.
\v 20 Netta \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tnayen u-třatin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tmenya n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Netta ifna, war xas indeb ḥed. Neḍřen t di tendint n Dawud, \add maca\add* war iǧi deg imeḍřan n ijeǧiden.
\b
\b
\c 22
\s1 Ajeǧid Axazya ittwaneɣ s ufus n Yahu
\m 
\v 1 Imezdaɣ n Urcalim ggin Axazya, mmis amaẓuẓ, d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes, maɣar marra aytmas imeqqranen tuɣa ttwanɣen zeg ict n bandiyya i tuɣa dd-tudef ak-d Weɛraben ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar. \add Ammu i\add* idweř Axazya, mmis n Yahuram, d ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 22:1 \xt [2 Ij. 8:25-29; 9:27-29]\x*
\v 2 Axazya \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tnayen u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa, umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem ijj n useggʷas di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Ɛatalya, yeǧis n Ɛumri.
\v 3 Netta yuyur deg ibriden n taddart n Axab, maɣar yemmas d tamcawart nnes di \add marra\add* tuɛeffna i igga.
\v 4 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, am taddart n Axab, maɣar awarni i řmewt n babas tuɣa \add inni n taddart n Axab\add* d imcawaren nnes ařami ikka x uzeǧif.
\m 
\v 5 Netta iḍfar ccwar nsen uca iffeɣ ak-d Yuram, mmis n Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, i umenɣi ak-d Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram, ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad uca ayt n Aram ɣeřben x Yuram.
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* yareggʷeḥ maḥend ad yarzu di Yazraɛil agenfu zeg iyezzimen nni i d as tuɣa ggin \add ayt n\add* Aram umi immneɣ di Ramut ak-d ujeǧid nsen, Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram. Ihwa-dd Ɛazarya, mmis n Yahuram, ajeǧid n Yahuda, \add ɣar din\add*, ḥima ad issijj x Yuram, mmis n Axab, di Yazraɛil, umi tuɣa ihřec.
\v 7 Areddeǧ n Axazya tuɣa zi AREBBI umi dd-yusa ɣar Yuram. Umi dd-yiweḍ \add din\add*, iffeɣ ak-d Yuram ɣar Yahu, mmis n Nimci, wenni tuɣa idhen SIDI, maḥend ad iqḍa x taddart n Axab.
\v 8 Umi iqḍa Yahu řḥukm x taddart n Axab, imsar, aqa yufa řḥukkam n Yahuda d iḥenjiren n aytmas n Axazya, \add inni\add* i tuɣa ittsexxaren i Axazya, uca inɣa i-ten.
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* yarzu x Axazya. Nitni ṭṭfen t am tuɣa innuffar di Samarya uca iwyen t ɣar Yahu. Nɣin t u neḍřen t, minzi nnan: “Netta d mmis n Yahucafaṭ, wenni yarezzun x SIDI s marra uř nnes.” \add Ammu\add* war iqqim i taddart n Axazya uřa d ijj wenni di iǧa jjehd ḥima ad iḥkem am ujeǧid.
\b
\s1 Yuwac war ittwaneɣ s ifassen n Atalya
\m 
\v 10 \add Umi\add* Ɛatalya, yemmas n Axazya teẓra, aqa mmis immut, tekkar, tᵉteḥḥa marra tarwa n ujeǧid n taddart n Yahuda. \f ◼ \fr 22:10 \fk tarwa\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzariɛet’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 22:10 \xt [2 Ij. 11:1-3]\x*
\v 11 \add Maca\add* Yahuciba, yeǧis n ujeǧid, teksi Yuwac, mmis n Axazya, uca texḍef i-t zi jar iḥenjiren n ujeǧid nni ittwanɣen, uca tessidef i-t ak-d tenni t issuṭuḍen deg wexxam n tassut. \add Ammu\add* i tegga Yahuciba, yeǧis n ujeǧid Yahuram, tamɣart n ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ - maɣar nettat d učmas n Axazya - tessnuffar i-t i Ɛatalya u tanita war t tenɣi ca.
\v 12 Setta n iseggʷusa iqqim innuffar ɣarsen di Taddart n AREBBI u tuɣa Ɛatalya tḥekkem x temmurt.
\b
\b
\c 23
\s1 Yuwac d ajeǧid ameẓyan x tgeldit n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa issejhed Yahuyadaɛ ixef nnes uca igga ijj n řɛahd \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d imeqqranen x mya, Ɛazarya, mmis n Yeruham d Ismaɛil, mmis n Yuḥanan, d Ɛazarya, mmis n Ɛubid, d Maɛasiya, mmis n Ɛadaya, d Ilicafaṭ, mmis n Zikri. \x ◘ \xo 23:1 \xt [2 Ij. 11:4-20]\x*
\v 2 Nitni kkin x \add temmurt\add* n Yahuda, ssmunen Ilawiyyen zi tneddam n Yahuda uřa d izeǧifen \add n tudrin\add* n ibabaten n Israil uca usin-dd ɣar Urcalim.
\v 3 Marra agraw \add n řgens\add* igga ijj n řɛahd ak-d ujeǧid di Taddart n AREBBI u netta inna asen: “Xzar, mmis n ujeǧid ad idweř d ajeǧid, am mammec i t inna SIDI x iḥenjiren n Dawud!”
\v 4 Yumur i-ten, inna: “D man aya i ɣa teggem: ict n ttuřut nwem, inni n ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen i ɣa yadfen deg \add wass n\add* ssebt, ad ɛessen ɣar tewwura.
\v 5 Ict n ttuřut \add ad tbedd\add* ɣar taddart n ujeǧid u ict n ttuřut ɣar Tewwart n Dsas u marra řgens \add ad ibedd\add* di řemraḥat n Taddart n SIDI.
\v 6 Uřa d ijj war ittidef ɣar Taddart n SIDI, mɣir ikehhanen d \add ayt n\add* Lawi nni ittsexxaren, ad adfen, maɣar nitni d imqeddasen u marra řgens ad iḥḍa min ittxeṣṣan ad ittwaḥḍa i SIDI.
\v 7 Ayt n Lawi ad quwwaren i ujeǧid, \add kuř\add* aryaz s řesnaḥ nnes deg ufus nnes, u wenni i ɣa yarzun ad yadef ɣar Taddart ad ittwaneɣ. Kenniw ad teqqimen ak-d ujeǧid ɣar twasit nnes u ɣar wuffuɣ nnes. \x ◘ \xo 23:7 \xt Asa. 14:1, 4, 5\x*
\m 
\v 8 Ayt n Lawi d marra Yahuda ggin am mammec marra min \add i d asen\add* yumur ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ, uca iwyen kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add* iryazen nnes nni yudfen di ssebt, uřa d yinni dd-iffɣen di ssebt, maɣar akehhan Yahuyadaɛ war iwci řeɛwacar i terbiɛin.
\v 9 Akehhan Yahuyadaɛ iwca i imeqqranen x mya lansat d tseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* iqesḥen i tuɣa iǧan n ujeǧid Dawud, tinni \add tuɣa iǧan\add* di Taddart n AREBBI.
\v 10 Issbedd řgens, kuř ijj \add s\add* lansa nnes deg ufus, zeg uɣezdis afusi n Taddart ař aɣezdis azeřmaḍ n Taddart, ɣar uɛalṭar u ɣar Taddart, \add ammu i\add* dd-quwwaren nitni i ujeǧid.
\v 11 Nitni ssuffɣen-dd mmis n ujeǧid ɣar barra uca ggin as ttaj \add n weɛzař\add* uca wcin as Cchadet. \add Ammu\add* i t ggin d ajeǧid, uca Yahuyadaɛ d iḥenjiren nnes dehnen t, nnan: “Tudart i ujeǧid!”
\m 
\v 12 \add Umi\add* tesřa Ɛatalya řḥess n řgens i dd-yusin ttazzřen ɣar din uca ssemɣaren ajeǧid, tudef-dd ɣar řgens di Taddart n SIDI.
\v 13 Teẓra, u xzar, ajeǧid ibedd ɣar upilar ɣar wadaf, u imeqqranen d \add inni ittsuḍen di\add* řebwaq \add bedden\add* ɣar ujeǧid. Marra řgens n temmurt ifraḥ u isuḍ di řebwaq. \add Uřa d\add* imedyazen ak-d dduzanat n lmusiqa inni issnen mammec ɣa ṣebbḥen \add bedden din\add*. \add Xenni\add* tcarreg Ɛatalya arruḍ nnes uca tesɣuy: “Tamenziwt, tamenziwt!”
\m 
\v 14 \add Maca\add* yumur ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ i imeqqranen n mya, inni i tuɣa iǧan x řɛeskar, inna asen: “Suffɣem tt-i-dd jar iseddiyyen \add n řɛeskar\add* ɣar barra uca nɣem s ssif wi tt ɣa iḍfaren.” Maɣar akehhan tuɣa inna: “War tt neqqem di Taddart n SIDI!”
\v 15 Nitni ssarsen xas ifassen uca \add umi\add* iwḍen ɣar wadaf n Tewwart n Iysan \add ɣar\add* taddart n ujeǧid, nɣin tt dinni.
\m 
\v 16 Igga Yahuyadaɛ ijj n řɛahd jar as-dd d marra řgens d ujeǧid, ḥima ad iřin d ijj n řgens i SIDI.
\v 17 \add Xas uca\add* yudef marra řgens ɣar zzawect n Baɛal u hedmen tt. Iɛalṭaren nnes d řexyařat nnes arẓin ten qaɛ. U nitni nɣin Mattan, akehhan n Baɛal, zzat i iɛalṭaren.
\v 18 Igga Yahuyadaɛ tasexxart di Taddart n SIDI deg ufus n ikehhanen n \add ayt n\add* Lawi nni tuɣa ibḍa Dawud \add di terbiɛin\add* i Taddart n SIDI, ḥima ad qeddmen tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ n SIDI am mammec tura di Ccariɛa n Musa, s řefraḥet d izřan, am t iweṣṣa Dawud.
\v 19 Netta issbedd iɛessasen x tewwura n Taddart n SIDI, maḥend uřa d ijj mammec ma igga mařa ixmej, war din ittidef ca.
\v 20 Netta yiwi imeqqranen x mya, d ayt n jjehd, d ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa jar řgens d marra řgens n temmurt uca issehwa ajeǧid zi Taddart n SIDI, u nitni udfen ɣar taddart n ujeǧid zi Tewwart Yuɛřan uca ssɣimen ajeǧid x řɛarc n tgeldit.
\v 21 Marra řgens n temmurt ifarḥ u tandint tedweř tarsa, awarni umi nɣin Ɛatalya s ssif.
\b
\b
\c 24
\s1 Řeḥkamet n Yuwac x Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Yuwac \add tuɣa\add* ɣares sebɛa n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem arebɛin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Ḍibya zi Bi’r-Sebɛa. \x ◘ \xo 24:1 \xt [2 Ij. 12:1-22]\x*
\v 2 Yuwac igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, marra ussan i tuɣa akehhan Yahuyadaɛ iddar.
\v 3 Yahuyadaɛ yiwi as tnayen n temɣarin u netta ijja-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin.
\v 4 Awarni uya tuɣa inwa Yuwac s wuř, ḥima ad iɛdeř Taddart n SIDI.
\v 5 Issmun ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen, inna asen: “Kkem x tneddam n Yahuda u yarwem ijj n řqedd n nnuqart di kuř aseggʷas zi marra Israil, ḥima ad tɛedřem Taddart n AREBBI. Bdam deɣya s uya!” \add Maca\add* Ilawiyyen war qeǧqen ca.
\m 
\v 6 Ajeǧid iřaɣa i uzeǧif Yahuyadaɛ, inna as: “Mayemmi war tesseqsid Ilawiyyen x mammec dd-iffeɣ wesmuni zi Yahuda d Urcalim n tewhibt n usgeɛɛed n Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, uřa n wegraw n Israil di ṭṭweɛ n Uqiḍun n Cchadet?
\v 7 Aqa iḥenjiren n Ɛatalya taɛeffant arẓin Taddart n AREBBI uca ssmuṭṭiyen marra řeqcuɛ iqeddsen n Taddart n SIDI ɣar ‘Ibaɛlen’.”
\m 
\v 8 Ajeǧid yumur, ḥima ad ggen ict n tṣenduqt u nitni ssarsen tt barra ɣar tewwart n Taddart n SIDI.
\v 9 Xenni řaɣan di Yahuda d Urcalim, ḥima ad yarwen i SIDI tawhibt n usgeɛɛed nni igga Musa, amsexxar n AREBBI, x Israil di řexřa.
\v 10 Marra imeqqranen d marra řgens tuɣa farḥen u nitni iwyen-dd \add tiwhibin\add* uca nḍaren tent di tṣenduqt ařami teccur.
\v 11 Di řweqt umi dd-ssidfen tasenduqt x řumur n ujeǧid s ufus n Ilawiyyen uca ẓrin aqa \add dayes\add* aṭṭas n nnuqart, imsar, aqa yusa-dd umarir n ujeǧid d uweqqaf n ukehhan ameqqran uca ssexwan nitni tasenduqt, ssgeɛɛden tt u iwyen tt \add ɛawed\add* ɣar wemcan nnes. Ammu i ggin nitni ass iḍfar umas uca ssmunen-dd aṭṭas n nnuqart.
\m 
\v 12 Ajeǧid d Yahuyadaɛ wcin aya \add xenni\add* i imḍebbaren n řxedmet di ṭṭweɛ n Taddart n SIDI. Nitni cran isuydayen d ineqqacen n ukeccuḍ, ḥima ad ɛedřen Taddart n SIDI, uřa d imziřen n wuzzař d nnḥas, ḥima \add uřa d nitni\add* ad ɛedřen Taddart n SIDI.
\v 13 Ixeddamen tuɣa xeddmen řebda u sadu ufus nsen tuyur řxedmet nican ɣar zzat. Nitni arrin Taddart n AREBBI am mammec tt tuɣa amezwaru u arnin di řemten nnes.
\v 14 Řami kemmřen nitni \add řxedmet\add*, iwyen min iqqimen n nnuqart zzat i wudem n ujeǧid u zzat i Yahuyadaɛ uca igga zzayes řeqcuɛ i Taddart n SIDI, řeqcuɛ i tsexxart u i tewhibin n wecmaḍ, tiɣenjayin d řeqcuɛ n wureɣ d nnuqart. Marra ussan nni \add ikka\add* Yahuyadaɛ \add iddar\add*, ttawyen řebda tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i Taddart n SIDI.
\m 
\v 15 Yahuyadaɛ iwsar u uzan ɣares wussan \add n tudart\add*, uca immut. Netta tuɣa ɣares mya u-třatin n iseggʷusa umi immut.
\v 16 Neḍřen t jar ijeǧiden di tendint n Dawud, maɣar tuɣa igga min iǧan nican di Israil, am i AREBBI, am i Taddart nnes.
\m 
\v 17 Awarni i řmewt n Yahuyadaɛ usin-dd řḥukkam n Yahuda uca bendqen i ujeǧid, uca isřa ɣarsen ujeǧid.
\v 18 Nitni semḥen di Taddart n SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen, uca sexxaren i trebbin n cwarti d řexyařat n l’aṣnam. \add Xenni\add* idweř uduqqez d ameqqran \add n weɣḍab\add* x Yahuda u x Urcalim di ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet nsen.
\v 19 Netta issekk jar asen inabiyyen, ḥima ad ten yarra ad ɛeqben ɣar SIDI. Nitni cehden xasen, maca war d asen sřin ca. \f ◼ \fr 24:19 \fk Netta\ft - wanita d SIDI.\f*
\v 20 Arruḥ n AREBBI ihwa-dd x Zakariyya, mmis n ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ. Netta ibedd x ijj n ddruj zzat i řgens, inna asen: “Ammu i iqqar AREBBI: ‘Mayemmi tᵉttɛeddam x řumurat n SIDI? \add Ammu\add* war tᵉttefřiḥem ca. Minzi tḥeyydem x SIDI, ad xawem iḥeyyed Netta.’”
\v 21 Nitni ggin xas ict n tmeɛmuč u ḥejjaren t x řumur n ujeǧid di řemraḥ n Taddart n SIDI.
\v 22 Ajeǧid Yuwac war ixarreṣ di tmexsiwt icewwaren, tenni i d as tuɣa isscen Yahuyadaɛ, babas \add n Zakariyya\add*, uca \add Yuwac\add* inɣa mmis \add n Yahuyadaɛ\add*. Umi immut, inna Zekariya: “SIDI ad t iẓar, ad yarzu \add ad t ixřef\add*!”
\m 
\v 23 Ɣar uneqřeb n useggʷas, imsar, aqa issgeɛɛed řɛeskar n Aram x Yuwac. Nitni usin-dd ɣar Yahuda d Urcalim u sshellken zi řgens marra řḥukkam n řgens uca ssekken marra takeccaḍt nsen ɣar ujeǧid n Dimacq.
\v 24 Waxxa tuɣa řɛeskar n Aram drus n yeryazen waha, aqa SIDI igga asen ijj n řɛeskar d ameqqran deg ufus nsen, umi nitni ḥeyyden x SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen. Nitni ggin řeḥkamat x Yuwac.
\v 25 Umi xas ffɣen nitni, aqa jjin t ihřec aṭṭas. Ggin xas imsexxaren nnes ict n tmeɛmuč di ssibbet n idammen i issizzeř Yuwac jar iḥenjiren n ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ. Nɣin t am iǧa di tassut nnes. Neḍřen t di tendint n Dawud, maca war t nḍiřen ca di tmeḍřin n ijeǧiden.
\v 26 Ina d inni i xas iggin ict n tmeɛmuč: Zabad, mmis n Cimɛa, Taɛammunect, u Yahuzabad, mmis n Cimrit, Tamu’abect.
\v 27 X iḥenjiren nnes u x řqedd n min i xas ggin \add inabiyyen\add* u x dsas n Taddart n AREBBI, xzar, aqa \add man aya marra\add* yura di tira n wedlis n ijeǧiden. Mmis Amaṣya idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 25
\s1 Aɣelleb n Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, x Idum
\m 
\v 1 Amaṣya \add tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tesɛa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Yahuɛaddan, \add tuɣa-tt\add* zi Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 25:1 \xt [2 Ij. 14:1-22]\x*
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, maca war iǧi s wuř imun \add qaɛ\add*.
\v 3 Umi issemten tagelda nnes, imsar, aqa inɣa imsexxaren nnes, inni i tuɣa inɣin babas ajeǧid.
\v 4 Maca iḥenjiren n iqettařen war ten inɣi ca, am mammec \add t\add* yura deg wedlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n Musa i di iweṣṣa SIDI, inna: “Ibabaten war ttwaneqqen di ssibbet n iḥenjiren \add nsen\add* u iḥenjiren war ttwaneqqen di ssibbet n ibabaten \add nsen\add*, maɣar kuř ijj ad ittwaneɣ x ddnub \add n yixef\add* nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 25:4 \xt Aɛwd. 24:16; Ḥiz. 18:20\x*
\m 
\v 5 Amaṣya issmun \add ayt n\add* Yahuda uca issbedd i-ten ɛlaḥsab řaǧat n ibabaten, ak-d imeqqranen x wařef u ak-d imeqqranen x mya i Yahuda d Binyamin marra. Netta isedd i-ten zi ɛicrin iseggʷusa sennej uca yufa jar asen teřt-myat-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* ttwafarzen, ḥima ad ffɣen ak-d řɛeskar, inni ittwadarrben x uḥric d tseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* tameqqrant.
\v 6 Netta icra myat-ařef n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen zi Israil s mya talint n nnuqart.
\m 
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ɣares ijj n weryaz n AREBBI, inna: “\add A\add*, ajeǧid, war ttejji řɛeskar n Israil akidek itteffeɣ, maɣar SIDI war iǧi ak-d Israil, ak-d marra arrawen \add nni\add* n Ifrayim.
\v 8 \add Maca\add* mařa texsed ad traḥed \add ɛad\add* ffeɣ, egg i-t, \add iwa\add* iři d aryaz deg umenɣi. AREBBI ad cek issneqřeb zzat i wudem n řeɛdu, maɣar AREBBI ɣares tizemmar maḥend ad iɛawen u ad issneqřeb.”
\v 9 Amaṣya inna i weryaz n AREBBI: “Maca min ɣa imsaren s mya talint i wciɣ i terbiɛin n \add řɛeskar n\add* Israil?” Aryaz n AREBBI inna: “SIDI ɣares ktar zi man aya ḥima ad ac t iwc.”
\v 10 Uca iɛzeř Amaṣya tirbiɛin \add n řɛeskar\add* i tuɣa ɣares dd-yusin zi Ifrayim, ijja i-tent ad areggʷeḥent ɣar wemcan nsen. \add Xenni\add* iřqef i-ten uxeyyeq ameqqran x Yahuda uca ɛeqben s tefqeḥt d ufugem ɣar wemcan nsen.
\m 
\v 11 Amaṣya igga taryast, indeh řgens nnes. Iffeɣ ɣar teɣzurt n Tmeǧaḥt, inɣa ɛecra-ařaf \add n yeryazen\add* zeg ayt n Saɛir.
\v 12 \add Ɛawed\add* ḥebbsen ayt n Yahuda ɛecra-ařaf \add n yeryazen\add* am ddaren, uca iwyen ten ɣar tqiccat n jjarf uca ɛarnen ten ssenni ɣar swadday ařami ftuttyen marra.
\v 13 \add Maca\add* iryazen n terbiɛin n řɛeskar nni tuɣa ijja Amaṣya ad ɛeqben ařami war kidsen dd-tteffɣen ɣar umenɣi, hejmen x tneddam n Yahuda, zi Samarya ař Bayt-Ḥurun, uca nɣin zzaysen teřt-ařaf \add n yeryazen\add* uca ḥewwsen takeccaḍt tameqqrant aṭṭas.
\m 
\v 14 Awarni řeɣřeb x ayt n Idum, řami dd-iɛqeb Amaṣya, yiwi netta irebbiten n ayt n Saɛir uca issbedd i-ten zzates uca ibendeq zzatsen uca issbexxar asen.
\v 15 Uca yarɣa weɣḍab n SIDI x Amaṣya, uca issekk ijj n unabi ɣares. Wanita inna as: “Mayemmi tarzud irebbiten n řgens \add nni\add*, inni i tuɣa war izemmaren ad fekken řgens nsen zeg ufus nnec?”
\v 16 Umi netta issiweř \add ammu\add*, imsar, aqa inna as: “Ma ggin cek d amcawar n ujeǧid? Bedd, mayemmi i cek i ɣa wten?” \add Xenni\add* ibedd unabi, inna: “\add Řexxu\add* ssneɣ, aqa SIDI iɛzem ḥima ad cek yareddeǧ, minzi teggid aya u war tesřid ɣar ccwar inu.”
\b
\s1 Taxessart n Yahuda deg umenɣi ak-d Israil
\m 
\v 17 Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, imcawar. Issekk \add ireqqaṣen\add* ɣar Yuwac, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz, mmis n Yahu, ajeǧid n Israil, inna: “As-dd, ejj aneɣ ad nemmeřqa \add i umenɣi\add*.”
\v 18 \add Maca\add* Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil, issekk \add ijj n ureqqaṣ\add* ɣar Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, inna as: “Cbarq ak-d isennanen \add i iɣemmyen\add* x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan, issekk \add ict n tebrat\add* ɣar tengelt x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan, inna: ‘Ewc yeǧic d tamɣart i mmi!’ \add Maca\add* ijj n řweḥc i \add din yuyuren\add* x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan, ikka uca iɛfes x cbarq ak-d isennanen.
\v 19 Teqqared \add ak-d ixef nnec\add*: ‘Xzar, aqa ɣeřbeɣ x Idum!’, u \add řexxu\add* tudef nnfaxet ɣar wuř nnec ḥima ad tarzud x ccan ktar. Qqim di taddart nnec, \add minzi\add* mayemmi ɣa tɣeḍřed ixef nnec di řɣar u ad tewḍid, cek d Yahuda akidek?”
\v 20 \add Maca\add* Amaṣya war ixs ad iseř, maɣar man aya yusa-dd zi AREBBI maḥend ad ten iwc deg ufus \add nsen\add*, minzi nitni arzun irebbiten n Idum.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil. Netta d Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, mmeřqan \add i umenɣi\add* ɣar Bayt-Cams, i iǧan di Yahuda.
\v 22 Yahuda ittwaɣřeb zzat i wudem n Israil uca nitni arewřen, kuř ijj ɣar uqiḍun nnes.
\v 23 Yaḥuyaḥaz, ajeǧid n Israil, iṭṭef Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, mmis n Yuwac, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz di Bayt-Cams uca yiwyi i-t ɣar Urcalim. \add Dinni\add* igga ict n tazzit di řḥiḍ n Urcalim, zi Tewwart n Ifrayim ař Tewwart n Teɣmart, x ijj n webrid n arebɛa-mya n iɣaǧen.
\v 24 Yiwi marra ureɣ d nnuqart d marra řeqcuɛ i ittwafen di Taddart n AREBBI u deg ixxamen n txubay n taddart n ujeǧid \add uřa d\add* imerhanen, uca iɛqeb ɣar Samarya.
\m 
\v 25 Amaṣya, mmis n Yuwac, ajeǧid n Yahuda, iddar \add ɛad\add* xemmesṭac n iseggʷusa awarni i řmewt n Yuwac, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz, ajeǧid n Israil.
\v 26 Min iqqimen n imezruyen n Amaṣya, imezwura d ineggura, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n ijeǧiden n Yahuda d Israil?
\v 27 Zeg wami iḥeyyed Amaṣya x SIDI, ggin xas ict n tmeɛmuč di Urcalim, maca netta yarweř ɣar Laxic. \add Xenni\add* ssekken \add iryazen\add* awarni as uca nɣin t dinni.
\v 28 Iwyen t-i-dd x yeysan uca neḍřen t jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Yahuda.
\b
\b
\c 26
\s1 Ɛuzziya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, řeḥřac nnes d řmewt nnes
\m 
\v 1 \add Xas uca\add* yiwi marra řgens n Yahuda Ɛuzziya, wenni tuɣa ɣar iǧa seṭṭac n iseggʷusa, ggin t d ajeǧid deg wemcan n babas Amaṣya. \x ◘ \xo 26:1 \xt [2 Ij. 15:1-7]\x*
\v 2 Netta ibna Ilat u yarra i-t \add deg ufus\add* n Yahuda, awarni řami igga ujeǧid ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes.
\v 3 Ɛuzziya \add tuɣa\add* ɣares seṭṭac n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tnayen u-xemsin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Yakulya zi Urcalim.
\v 4 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, igga nican am mammec tuɣa igga babas Amaṣya.
\v 5 Netta tuɣa yarezzu x AREBBI deg wussan n Zakariyya, wenni tuɣa i d as isseřmad maḥend ad iggʷed AREBBI, uca issehwen AREBBI abrid nnes deg wussan i di tuɣa yarezzu x SIDI.
\m 
\v 6 Netta iffeɣ uca immneɣ ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen uca igga ict n tazzit di řḥiḍ n Jat u di řḥiḍ n Yabna d řḥiḍ n Acdud. Netta ibna tineddam ɣar Acdud u di \add temmurt n\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen.
\v 7 AREBBI ibedd akides ḍidd i Ifilisṭiniyyen u ḍidd i Weɛraben, inni izeddɣen di Jur-Baɛl, u ḍidd i Imaɛuniyyen.
\v 8 Wcin ayt n Ɛammun ljizya i Ɛuzziya uca idweř yisem nnes ittwassen ař wadaf n Miṣra, maɣar netta tuɣa idweř ijhed aṭṭas.
\v 9 Di Urcalim issbedd Ɛuzziya ṣṣumɛat ɣar Tewwart n Teɣmart u ɣar Tewwart n Teɣzurt u ɣar Tɣemmurt uca issemten i-tent.
\v 10 Netta ibna \add ɛawed\add* ṣṣumɛat di řexřa uca iɣza aṭṭas n wanuten, maɣar ɣares řebhayem aṭṭas di Temmurt Iwaṭan u di řwaṭa \add yuɛřan\add*. Tuɣa ɣares ifeǧaḥen d ayt n tzayart deg idurar uřa deg iyyaren iɛarṣen, maɣar netta tuɣa ittexs tafeǧaḥt.
\m 
\v 11 Ɛuzziya tuɣa ɣares \add ɛawed\add* ijj n řɛeskar n iɛeskariyyen imdarrben, tteffɣen ɣar umenɣi di terbiɛin, ɛlaḥsab lɛadad i tuɣa ittwasedd zzaysen s ufus n umarir Yaɛiyil d uweqqaf Maɛasiya, s řumur n Ḥananya, ijj zi řḥukkam n ujeǧid.
\v 12 Řqedd imun n izeǧifen x \add řaǧat n\add* ibabaten, n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, \add tuɣa\add* ařfayen u-setta-mya \add n yeryazen\add*.
\v 13 Sadu afus nsen \add tuɣa\add* din ijj n řɛeskar n teřt-mya u-sebɛa-ařaf u-xemsa-mya \add n yeryazen\add*, iɛeskariyyen imdarrben s jjehd \add iccuren\add* i umenɣi, ḥima ad wcen afus i ujeǧid ḍidd i řeɛdu.
\v 14 Ɛuzziya issewjed asen tiseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* d iḥricen d lkaskat x uzeǧif d warruḍ n wuzzař d řeqwas d iẓra n yiǧiy, i marra řɛeskar.
\v 15 Di Urcalim igga dduzanat ittwassuffɣen zeg imsuffɣen imiɣisen ḥima ad tent ggen x ṣṣumɛat u x tɣemmura ḥima ad zzaysent wten fřitcat u ad ḥejjaren iẓra imeqqranen. Ammu i idweř isem nnes icneɛ ɣar řaggʷaj, maɣar i netta umi tᵉttwagg twiza s řeɛjeb, ařami idweř yarni di jjehd.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Maca umi idweř ijhed, issgeɛɛed ixef nnes deg wuř nnes ařami issiweḍ \add ixef nnes\add* ɣar wareyyeb u iɣdar SIDI, AREBBI nnes, maɣar yudef ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI, ḥima ad issbexxar x uɛalṭar n řebxur.
\v 17 Akehhan Ɛazarya yuyur awarni as, u uyuren akides ikehhanen n SIDI d Ilawiyyen, tmenyin n yeryazen imeḥḍen. \f ◼ \fr 26:17 \fk Ɛazarya\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Ɛazar-Yahu’. \fk iryazen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘iḥenjiren’.\f*
\v 18 Nitni qaṭɛen i ujeǧid Ɛuzziya, nnan as: “War cek icuwwar, Ɛuzziya, maḥend ad tawyed řebxur i SIDI, mɣir i ikehhanen, arraw n Harun, inni ittwaqeddsen i tewhibt n řebxur. Ffeɣ zi Zzawect Iqeddsen, maɣar teɣdared u man aya war d ac dd-ittiwi ccan zzat i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.”
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* isɛar Ɛuzziya am iṭṭef řebxur i tewhibt n řebxur deg ufus nnes. Am isɛar \add ammu\add* x ikehhanen, iffeɣ as dd-řbarṣ di tenyart nnes, zzat i tiṭṭawin n ikehhanen di Taddart n SIDI, ɣar uɛalṭar n řebxur. \f ◼ \fr 26:19 \fk Ɛuzziya\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Ɛuzzi-Yahu’, ixs ad yini ‘Arebbi d jjehd inu’. \fk zzat i tiṭṭawin n\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzat i wudmawen n’.\f*
\v 20 \add Umi\add* inneqřeb ukehhan ameqqran Ɛazarya d marra ikehhanen ɣares, aqa da, dayes řbarṣ di tenyart nnes. Nitni ḥsaren t deɣya ad ssenni yaggʷej, uřa d netta simant nnes iqeǧeq ad iffeɣ, minzi SIDI tuɣa iwta i-t.
\v 21 Tuɣa ajeǧid Ɛuzziya ihřec s řbarṣ ař ass n řmewt nnes. Netta iqqim izeddeɣ deg ict n taddart tᵉttwaɛzeř, maɣar netta tuɣa ittwaqess zi Taddart n SIDI. Mmis Yutam tuɣa \add ittwařeqqem\add* x tzeddiɣt \add n ujeǧid\add* u iḥekkem x řgens n temmurt.
\m 
\v 22 Imezruyen iqqimen n Ɛuzziya, imezwura d ineggura, aqa izemm i-ten unabi Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ.
\v 23 Ɛuzziya igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Neḍřen t jar řejdud nnes deg iyyar n wenḍeř n ijeǧiden, maɣar nnan: “Aqa dayes řbarṣ!” Mmis Yutam idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 27
\s1 Yutam idweř d ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Yutam \add tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem seṭṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Yaruca, yeǧis n Ṣaduq. \x ◘ \xo 27:1 \xt [2 Ij.15:32-38]\x*
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t igga babas Ɛuzziya, maca netta war yudif ca ɣar Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI. Řgens \add maca\add* tuɣa \add ɛad\add* ifsed ixef nnes aṭṭas.
\v 3 Netta ibna Tawwart Yuɛřan n Taddart n SIDI. Uřa ɣar řḥiḍ n Ɛufil ibna aṭṭas.
\v 4 Ibna tineddam di Temmurt n Idurar n Yahuda u deg izeɣran ibna lqelɛat d ṣṣumɛat.
\v 5 Netta immneɣ ak-d ayt n Ɛammun u iɣřeb xasen, ařami ayt n Ɛammun ssiwḍen ɣares deg useggʷas nni \add ɛad\add* mya talint n nnuqart d ɛecra-ařaf n ikuruten n irden d ɛecra-ařaf ikuruten n imendi. Uřa deg useggʷas wiss tnayen d wiss třata ssiwḍen ayt n Ɛammun ɣares man aya ɛawed.
\v 6 \add Ammu i\add* idweř Yutam ijhed, maɣar issewjed ibriden nnes zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnes.
\m 
\v 7 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yutam, d marra imenɣan i immneɣ d marra ibriden nnes, aqa ttwazemmemen deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda.
\v 8 \add Tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem seṭṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim.
\v 9 Yutam igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř di tendint n Dawud. Mmis Aḥaz idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 28
\s1 Řeḥkamet n Aḥaz
\m 
\v 1 Aḥaz \add tuɣa\add* ɣares ɛicrin n iseggʷusa, umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem seṭṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Netta war iggi min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, am mammec \add igga\add* babas Dawud. \x ◘ \xo 28:1 \xt [2 Ij. 16:1-20]\x*
\v 2 Netta yuyur deg ibriden n ijeǧiden n Israil. Ɛawed igga řexyařat ifesyen i ‘Ibaɛlen’. \f ◼ \fr 28:2 \fk ibaɛlen\ft - aqa-ten d laṣnam.\f*
\v 3 Netta tuɣa ittawi-dd řebxur di teɣzurt n Bin-Hinnum u issecmeḍ iḥenjiren nnes di tmessi. Netta igga ɛlaḥsab jjɛayef nni ggin marra řegnus i xef yuẓẓeř SIDI zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil.
\v 4 Netta yiwyi-dd tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n řebxur x řegɛudi u x tewririn u sadu marra azɣar aziza.
\v 5 SIDI, AREBBI nnes, iwca i-t deg ifassen n ujeǧid n Aram. Nitni wtin t u ḥebbsen zzayes ijj n ubarru imɣar u iwyen ten ɣar Dimacq. Immewc Aḥaz deg ifassen n ujeǧid n Israil, wenni d as iwtin s ict n tecti d tameqqrant. \f ◼ \fr 28:5 \fk deg ifassen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘deg ufus’.\f*
\v 6 Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu, inɣa mya u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* deg ijj n wass di Yahuda, marra nitni d ayt n umenɣi, minzi nitni ḥeyyden x SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen.
\v 7 Zikri, ijj n bu-teɣruḍt zi Ifrayim, inɣa Maɛasiya, mmis n ujeǧid, d Ɛazriqam, ameḥḍay n Taddart, d Ilqana, wenni d wiss tnayen awarni i ujeǧid.
\v 8 Nedhen ayt n Israil zeg aytmatsen mitayen-ařef n temɣarin d iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin di tmeḥbast u ṭṭfen zzaysen ict n tkeccaḍt d tameqqrant. Iwyen takeccaḍt \add nni\add* ɣar Samarya.
\m 
\v 9 Dinni iǧa ijj n unabi n SIDI, qqaren as Ɛudid. Wanita iffeɣ, imsagar ak-d řɛeskar i dd-iɛeqben ɣar Samarya, inna asen: “Xzarem, minzi s wesɛar n SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, x Yahuda, igga i-ten deg ufus nwem u kenniw tenɣim ten s ijj n wesxeḍ yiweḍ ař ajenna.
\v 10 U řexxu ittɣiř awem ad teggem ayt n Yahuda d Urcalim sadu ufus nwem am yisemɣan d tiyya. Ma war kenniw iḍfar xenni umarwas ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nwem?
\v 11 Sřem-dd řexxu ɣari u arrem imeḥbas nni tḥebbsem zeg aytmatwem, maɣar řḥaduq n weɣḍab n SIDI \add i dd-yusa\add* xawem.”
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* ssbedden yeryazen-a zeg izeǧifen n iḥenjiren n Ifrayim \add ixef nsen\add* zzat i yinni dd-yareggʷeḥen zi řɛeskar: Ɛazarya, mmis n Yuḥanan, Baraxya, mmis n Macillimut, Ḥizqiya, mmis n Callum, d Ɛamasa, mmis n Hidlay.
\v 13 Nitni nnan asen: “War tzemmarem ad tessidfem imeḥbas danita, \add maɣar\add* nitni ad xaneɣ dd-arenyen amarwas zzat i SIDI. Ma ittɣiř awem \add nzemmar\add* ad narni \add ɛad\add* di ddnub nneɣ d umarwas nneɣ, waxxa \add ɛad\add* ɣarneɣ aṭṭas n imerwusa u řḥaduq n weɣḍab \add n AREBBI\add* aqa-t x Israil?”
\m 
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* semḥen yeryazen iḥezzmen s řesnaḥ deg imeḥbas d tkeccaḍt zzat i imeqqranen d marra agraw \add n řgens\add*.
\v 15 Iryazen, inni ittwasemman qbeř s ismawen nsen, kkaren uca thellan deg imeḥbas. Nitni ssyarḍen marra inni tuɣa iǧan d iɛaryanen s \add warruḍ zi\add* tkeccaḍt, ssyarḍen ten s warruḍ d tsiřa u wcin asen ad ccen, ad swen. \add Ɛawed\add* dehnen ten uca ssɣimen inni i tuɣa gguren ttenqarḍen x yeɣyař u \add ammu\add* iwyen ten ɣar aytmatsen ɣar Ariḥa, Tandint n Tcejjura n Tini. Awarni man aya ɛeqben nitni simant nsen ɣar Samarya.
\m 
\v 16 Di řweqt nni issekk Aḥaz \add ireqqasen\add* ɣar ijeǧiden n Accur, ḥima ad as wcen afus.
\v 17 Uřa d ayt n Idum usin-dd. Nitni wtin Yahuda u nedhen \add ten\add* di tmeḥbast.
\v 18 Ifilisṭiniyyen hejmen x tneddam n Temmurt Iwaṭan d ljanub n Yahuda uca ṭṭfen Bayt-Cams, Ayyalun, Jadirut, Suku d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen, Timnah d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen d Jimzu d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen uca zedɣen dinni.
\v 19 Maɣar SIDI issehwa Yahuda di ssibbet n Aḥaz, ajeǧid n Yahuda, minzi netta iffucceḥ di Yahuda, iɣdar SIDI.
\v 20 Tiɣlat-Filnasir, ajeǧid n Accur, yusa-dd ɣares. Netta igga xas bezzez u war t issejhed.
\v 21 Maɣar \add ɛad mařa\add* Aḥaz iksi \add agřa\add* zi Taddart n SIDI u zi taddart n ujeǧid u zi řḥukkam, iwca aya i ujeǧid n Accur, aqa man aya war d as ineffiɛ ca.
\m 
\v 22 Di řweqt i di ittwaḥṣar, yarni ujeǧid Aḥaz ɛad di řɣedran nnes zzat i SIDI.
\v 23 Netta iqeddem tiɣarṣa i irebbiten n Dimacq, inni xas iɣeřben, inna: “Maɣar irebbiten n ijeǧiden n Aram wcin asen afus, necc ad asen wehhbeɣ, ḥima ad ayi wcen afus ɛawed.” \add Maca\add* nitni dewřen d ssibbet n uweṭṭu nnes u n marra Israil.
\v 24 Aḥaz issmun řeqcuɛ zi Taddart n AREBBI uca yarẓa řeqcuɛ n Taddart n AREBBI di iwetwiten uca ibelleɛ tiwwura n Taddart n SIDI. Netta igga iɛalṭaren i yixef nnes di kuř taɣmart n Urcalim.
\v 25 Igga uřa d řegɛudi di kuř tandint n Yahuda, ḥima ad awyen řebxur i irebbiten nneɣni. \add Ammu i\add* isɛar netta SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nnes.
\m 
\v 26 Imezruyen iqqimen d marra ibriden nnes, imezwura d ineggura, xzar, aqa ttwazemmemen deg wedlis n ijeǧiden n Yahuda d Israil.
\v 27 Aḥaz igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Neḍřen t di tendint, di Urcalim, maca war t ssarsen ca deg imeḍřan n ijeǧiden n Israil. Mmis Ḥizqiya idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 29
\s1 Asizdeg n Zzawect Tameqqrant s ufus n Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Ḥizqiya idweř d ajeǧid umi \add tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa. Netta iḥkem tesɛa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Abiya, yeǧis n Zakariyya.
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t igga babas Dawud.
\v 3 Deg useggʷas amezwaru n řeḥkamet nnes, deg uyur amezwaru, yarzem tiwwura n Taddart n SIDI uca iɛdeř i-tent.
\v 4 Issidef ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen uca issmun i-ten x wazzay ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq.
\v 5 Inna asen: “Sřem-dd ɣari, \add a\add* Ilawiyyen. Sqeddsem ixef nwem uřa d Taddart n SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nwem, u kksem marra min ixemjen zi Zzawect Iqeddsen.
\v 6 Maɣar řejdud nneɣ tuɣa aten d iɣeddaren u ggin min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ. Nitni ḥeyyden xas, nnqeřben udmawen nsen zi Tzeddiɣt n SIDI uca arrin s weɛrur ɣar \add SIDI\add*.
\v 7 Ɛad uřa d tiwwura n wesqif n wadaf \add n Zzawect\add* bellɛen tent, ssxesyen řefnarat, war ssarɣen řebxur u war ssgiɛɛden \add ɛad\add* taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i AREBBI n Israil di Zzawect Iqeddsen.
\v 8 S uya yusa-dd uduqqez ameqqran \add n weɣḍab\add* n SIDI x Yahuda d Urcalim, uca Netta yarra i-ten d ict n řqecɛet n unexřiɛ d usiggʷed d tseḍḥact am mammec tᵉttwařam kenniw s tiṭṭawin nwem.
\v 9 Xzarem, řejdud nneɣ wḍan s ssif u iḥenjiren nneɣ, tiḥenjirin nneɣ d temɣarin nneɣ aqa aten di řeḥbes x uya.
\v 10 Řexxu aqa-tt ɣari deg wuř inu maḥend ad ggeɣ ijj n řɛahd ak-d SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, ḥima řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes ad xaneɣ ibeɛɛed.
\v 11 \add A\add* arrawen inu, war arexxum, minzi SIDI ifarz i kenniw, aqa ad tbeddem zzat i wudem nnes, ḥima ad as tsexxarem u ḥima kenniw ad as tiřim d imsexxaren nnes u ad \add as\add* tqeddmem řebxur.”
\m 
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* kkaren Ilawiyyen: Maḥat, mmis n Ɛamasay, d Yuwil, mmis n Ɛazarya, zeg iḥenjiren n Quḥat. Zeg warrawen n Marari, Qis, mmis n Ɛabdi, d Ɛazarya, mmis n Yahlayil. Zeg warrawen n Jarcun, Yuwax, mmis n Zimma, d Ɛidan, mmis n Yuwax.
\v 13 Zeg warrawen n Iliṣafan, Cimri d Yaɛiyil, u zeg warrawen n Asaf, Zakariyya d Mattanya.
\v 14 Zeg warrawen n Hayman, Yaḥiyil d Cimɛi, u zeg warrawen n Yadutun, Camɛiya d Ɛuzziyil.
\v 15 Nitni ssmunen aytmatsen uca ssqeddsen ixef nsen ɛlaḥsab řumur n ujeǧid wenni iɛemmden x wawařen n SIDI, ḥima ad ssizedgen Taddart n SIDI.
\v 16 Udfen ikehhanen ɣar Taddart n SIDI, ḥima ad tt ssizedgen uca ssuffɣen marra řexmej i ufin di Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI ɣar řemraḥ n Taddart n SIDI, uca Ilawiyyen ksin t, ḥima ad t awyen ɣar barra, ɣar teɣzart n Qidrun.
\v 17 Deg \add wass\add* amezwaru n uyur amezwaru bdan ad ssqeddsen \add Taddart\add* uca deg was wiss tmenya n uyur iwḍen nitni ɣar wesqif n wadaf \add n Zzawect\add* n SIDI. \add Ammu i\add* ssqeddsen Taddart n SIDI di tmenya n wussan. Deg wass wiss seṭṭac n uyur amezwaru tuɣa kemmřen \add řxedmet\add*.
\v 18 Nitni udfen ɣar ujeǧid Ḥizqiya, nnan: “Neccin nessizdeg marra Taddart n SIDI, aɛalṭar n wecmaḍ ak-d marra dduzanat nnes d tzewḍa s weɣrum n wescan ak-d marra dduzanat nnes.
\v 19 Marra řeqcuɛ i inḍar ujeǧid Aḥaz zi řeɣdar nnes deg wussan n tgelda nnes, neɛdeř i-ten u nessqeddes i-ten. Aqa aten zzat i uɛalṭar n SIDI.”
\m 
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* ikkar ujeǧid Ḥizqiya zic uca issmun imeqqranen n tendint uca igeɛɛed ɣar Taddart n SIDI.
\v 21 Nitni iwyen-dd sebɛa n ifunasen imeẓyanen, sebɛa n icarriyyen, sebɛa n izmaren d sebɛa n imuyan n iɣayḍen, maḥend \add ad iřin\add* d taɣarṣt n ddenb i tgeldit, řa i Zzawect Iqeddsen uřa i Yahuda, uca netta inna i warrawen n Harun, ikehhanen, ḥima ad ten qeddmen x uɛalṭar n SIDI.
\v 22 Ɣarṣen i ifunasen uca sseřqan ikehhanen i idammen uca ruccen ten x uɛalṭar. Nitni ɣarṣen uřa i icarriyyen uca zeǧɛen idammen x uɛalṭar. Ɣarṣen uřa i izmaren uca zeǧɛen idammen x uɛalṭar.
\v 23 Nitni iwyen-dd imuyan i tɣarṣt n ddenb zzat i wudem n ujeǧid d wegraw \add n řgens\add*, uca ssarsen xasen ifassen nsen.
\v 24 Ikehhanen ɣarṣen asen u s idammen nsen ssizedgen aɛalṭar zi ddenb, ḥima ad ggen aṣřaḥ i marra Israil, maɣar ajeǧid tuɣa igga taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣt n ddenb \add nni\add* i marra Israil.
\v 25 Netta issbedd Ilawiyyen di Taddart n SIDI s taǧunin n wuzzař d řgambriyat d lharpat, ɛlaḥsab řumur n Dawud d Jad, amwařaw n ujeǧid, d unabi Natan, minzi řumur-a tuɣa i dd-yusa zi SIDI s uqemmum n inabiyyen.
\v 26 Ayt n Lawi bedden \add din\add* ak-d dduzanat \add n lmusiqa\add* n Dawud u ikehhanen ak-d řebwaq.
\m 
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* yumur Ḥizqiya ad awyen taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ x uɛalṭar. Di tsaɛɛet i di tebda tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, ibda uřa d azehhed i SIDI s řebwaq u s dduzanat \add n lmusiqa\add* n Dawud, ajeǧid n Israil.
\v 28 Marra agraw \add n řgens\add* ibendeq, am ttɣennajen u ttsuḍan di řebwaq. Man aya marra ikka ařami tᵉttwakemmeř tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.
\v 29 \add Umi\add* ikemmeř usiweḍ n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, iwḍa ujeǧid x ifadden nnes d marra inni tuɣa ɣares iǧan, uca bendqen.
\v 30 Awarni uya inna ujeǧid Ḥizqiya d řḥukkam i Ilawiyyen, ad ssɛuǧan SIDI s wawařen n Dawud u n umwařaw Asaf. Ssɛuǧan \add ɛad\add* s řefraḥet, \add xenni\add* uḍaren uca bendqen.
\m 
\v 31 Ḥizqiya yarra-dd, inna: “Řexxu kenniw tᵉttwařeqqmem \add d ikehhanen\add* i SIDI. Asettiw-dd uca awyem-dd tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n uqadi i Taddart n SIDI.” \add Xas uca\add* yiwi-dd wegraw \add n řgens\add* tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n uqadi, u marra inni i ɣar tt tuɣa di řxadar nsen, iwyen-dd tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ.
\v 32 Řqedd n tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i dd-yiwi wegraw \add n řgens\add*, aqa-t di sebɛin n ifunasen d mya n icarriyyen d mitayen n izmaren. Nitni marra ttwawyen-dd d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI.
\v 33 Tiwhibin iqeddsen aqa atent di setta-mya n ifunasen d teřt-ařaf n wuǧi.
\v 34 Maca aqa din drus n ikehhanen, u nitni war zemmaren ad ssarxun tiřmect n marra tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ. S uya ɛawnen ten aytmatsen Ilawiyyen, ařami kemmřen řxedmet u ařami ikehhanen nneɣni tuɣa ssqeddsen ixef nsen, minzi Ilawiyyen tuɣa seggden deg wuř ktar zeg ikehhanen ḥima ad ssqeddsen ixef nsen.
\v 35 Tuɣa din ɛawed aṭṭas n tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ ak-d tadunt n tewhibin n řehna d tewhibin n useyyeb i tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ. \add Ammu\add* i tᵉttwaɛdeř tsexxart n Taddart n SIDI.
\v 36 Ḥizqiya d marra řgens farḥen x min tuɣa issewjed AREBBI i řgens, maɣar tamesřact tᵉttwagg břa ma ad as ggen řeḥsab.
\b
\b
\c 30
\s1 Řɛid n Taɣarṣt n Useɛdu deg wussan n řḥukm n Ḥizqiya
\m 
\v 1 \add Awarni uya\add* issekk Ḥizqiya \add ireqqasen\add* ɣar marra Israil d Yahuda u yura tibratin i Ifrayim d Manassa, ḥima ad dd-asen ɣar Taddart n SIDI di Urcalim ad ggen \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 2 Maɣar imcawar ujeǧid ak-d řḥukkam nnes d marra agraw \add n řgens\add* di Urcalim, ḥima ad ggen \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu deg uyur wiss tnayen,
\v 3 maɣar nitni war zemmaren ad t ggen di řweqt \add nnes ittwaggen\add*, minzi aṭṭas n ikehhanen war ttwaqeddsen ca am dd-ittřiq, u řgens war tuɣi imun \add ɛad\add* di Urcalim.
\v 4 Tamesřact-a tuɣa-tt nican di tiṭṭawin n ujeǧid u di tiṭṭawin n marra agraw \add n řgens\add*.
\v 5 Nitni ggin, ad barrḥen di marra Israil zi Dan ař Bi’r-Sebɛa, ḥima ad dd-asen ad ggen \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, di Urcalim, maɣar war tt ggin aṭṭas \add n řweqt\add* am mammec tuɣa tura.
\m 
\v 6 Ireqqasen n tazřa kkin s tebratin n ujeǧid d řḥukkam nnes deg ufus x marra Israil d Yahuda, u \add barrḥen\add* am mammec t yumur ujeǧid, nnan: “Kenniw, ayt n Israil, dewřem-dd ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n Ibrahim, Isḥaq d Israil, \add xenni\add* Netta ad dd-idweř ɣar yinni innejmen zeg ufus n ujeǧid n Accur, ɣar yinni i ɣarwem iqqimen.
\v 7 War ttiřim am řejdud nwem d aytmatwem, inni iɣdaren SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen, ařami ten isellem Netta ɣar unexřiɛ, am mammec tᵉttwařam \add s yixef nwem\add*.
\v 8 War sseqsaḥem řexxu irawen nwem, iřim am řejdud nwem. Wcem afus i SIDI u asem-dd ɣar Zzawect nnes Iqeddsen tenni issqeddes Netta i řebda. Sexxarem i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, \add xenni\add* ad xawem iḥeyyed řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes.
\v 9 Mařa kenniw tdewřem-dd ɣar SIDI, ad afen aytmatwem d iḥenjiren nwem arreḥmet zzat i wudem n yinni i-ten iḥebbsen ařami ɣa dd-dewřen ɣar temmurt-a. Maɣar SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d bab n uḥinni d arreḥmet u Netta war xawem issḥeyyid ca udem mařa kenniw tdewřem-dd ɣares.”
\m 
\v 10 \add Ammu\add* i uyuren ireqqasen n tazřa zi tendint ɣar tendint, \add kkin\add* x temmurt n Ifrayim d Manassa ař Zabulun, maca \add iwdan\add* ḥeccen xasen u kkwaren ten \add iwdan\add*.
\v 11 Maca ca n yeryazen zi Acir, Manassa d Zabulun sswaḍɛen ixef nsen uca usin-dd ɣar Urcalim.
\v 12 Uřa di Yahuda indeh ufus n SIDI uca igga ad ḍfaren řumur n ujeǧid u n řḥukkam ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI, s wuř d ijjen.
\v 13 Munen waṭṭas \add n yewdan zi\add* řgens di Urcalim, ḥima ad ɛeyyden Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun deg uyur wiss tnayen. \add Ammu i tuɣa din\add* ijj n wegraw \add n řgens\add* d ameqqran aṭṭas.
\m 
\v 14 Nitni kkaren u kksen iɛalṭaren nni \add iǧan\add* di Urcalim. Kksen uřa d marra iɛalṭaren n řebxur uca nḍaren ten di teɣzart n Qidrun.
\v 15 Deg wass wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur wiss tnayen ɣarṣen nitni i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu. Ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen iwḍen ad seḍḥan u bdan ad ssqeddsen ixef nsen uca iwyen tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ ɣar Taddart n SIDI.
\v 16 Nitni bedden deg wemcan nsen am mammec i teggur ɣarsen ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa n Musa, aryaz n AREBBI. Ikehhanen zeǧɛen idammen \add nni ksin\add* zeg ifassen n Ilawiyyen.
\v 17 Minzi aṭṭas deg wegraw \add n řgens\add* tuɣa war ssqeddsen ixef nsen. S uya ttwaggen Ilawiyyen x tɣarṣt n izmaren n \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i marra inni war izdigen, ḥima ad ten ssqeddsen i SIDI.
\v 18 Maɣar azyen ameqqran n řgens, \add zzaysen\add* aṭṭas zi Ifrayim d Manassa d Issakar d Zabulun, tuɣa war ssizedgen ixef nsen. Nitni ccin \add Taɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu war iǧi am mammec tura. Maca Ḥizqiya iẓẓuǧ i nitni, inna: “SIDI icna, iři Netta ad igg aṣřaḥ i nitni, \f ◼ \fr 30:18 \fk ifdi\ft - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*
\v 19 \add x\add* kuř ijj wenni inwan ad yarzu s marra uř nnes x AREBBI, SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nnes, waxxa war iǧi s usizdeg \add i ittřiqen\add* i Zzawect Iqeddsen.”
\v 20 Isřa SIDI ɣař Ḥizqiya uca issgenfa řgens.
\m 
\v 21 \add Ammu\add* i ɛeyyden ayt n Israil, inni tuɣa innyarwen di Urcalim, sebɛa n wussan n Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun s řefraḥet tameqqrant. Ayt n Lawi d ikehhanen ssɛuǧan SIDI ass x wass s jjehd n dduzanat \add n lmusiqa\add* \add i uɛuǧi\add* n SIDI.
\v 22 Issiweř Ḥizqiya ɣar wuř n marra Ilawiyyen inni ɣar teǧa řefhamet icnan n tussna n SIDI. Ccin sebɛa n wussan zi tɣarṣa di řweqt ittwaggen \add n řɛid\add*, \add am\add* tuɣa iwyen tiwhibin n řehna u qadan SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen.
\v 23 \add Umi\add* imcawar wegraw \add n řgens\add* marra maḥend ad t ggen ict n twařa nneɣnit i sebɛa n wussan, arnin nitni \add ɛad\add* sebɛa n wussan \add ccuren\add* s řefraḥet,
\v 24 maɣar Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, tuɣa iwca ařef n ifunasen imeẓyanen d sebɛa-ařaf n wuǧi uca řḥukkam tuɣa wcin ařef n ifunasen imeẓyanen d ɛecra-ařaf n wuǧi. Ijj n ubarru n ikehhanen tuɣa ssqeddsen \add ixef nsen zzaysen\add*.
\m 
\v 25 Ifarḥ marra wegraw \add n řgens\add* n Yahuda, uřa d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen d marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n yinni dd-yusin zi Israil, uřa d ibarraniyyen nni dd-yusin zi Israil d yinni izeddɣen di \add temmurt n\add* Yahuda.
\v 26 Tuɣa din řefraḥet d tameqqrant di Urcalim, maɣar zeg wussan n Suliman, mmis n Dawud, ajeǧid n Israil, tuɣa war imsar am uya di Urcalim.
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* bedden ikehhanen n Ilawiyyen uca barken řgens. Tmijja nsen tᵉttwaseř, maɣar taẓaǧit nsen tudef ɣar Tzeddiɣt Tamqeddest nnes deg ujenna.
\b
\b
\c 31
\s1 Aɛdař n řxedmet di Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 Awarni řami kemmřen s man aya marra, ffɣen-dd marra ayt n Israil nni tuɣa din iǧan ɣar tneddam n Yahuda u arẓin imayḍuten \add iqeddsen\add*, hedmen tirebbin n cwarti uca kksen řegɛudi d iɛalṭaren zi marra Yahuda d Binyamin. \add Ammu i ggin uřa\add* di Ifrayim d Manassa ařami tt kemmřen. \add Awarni uya\add* ɛeqben marra ayt n Israil, kuř ijj ɣar wagřa nnes, \add marra nitni\add* ɣar tneddam nsen.
\m 
\v 2 Ḥizqiya issbedd tirbiɛin n ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen ɛlaḥṣab tirbiɛin nsen, kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab tasexxart nnes: ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ u i tewhibin n řehna, ḥima ad sexxaren, ad qadan u ad ssɛuǧan di tewwura n řemrageḥ n řɛeskar n SIDI.
\m 
\v 3 \add Netta iwca\add* uřa d tawhibt n ujeǧid zeg wagřa nnes i tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ, i tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ ɣar tuffut u ɣar tmeddit, uřa d tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i wussan n ssebt, i uyuren imaynuten u i řeɛyudat ittwaggen, am mammec tura di Ccariɛa n SIDI.
\v 4 Netta inna i řgens, i imezdaɣ n Urcalim, ad wehhben tasɣart n ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen, ḥima ina \add zemmaren\add* ad iřin jehden di tɣuri n Ccariɛa n SIDI.
\v 5 \add Umi\add* dd-iffeɣ wawař nni, iwyen-dd ayt n Israil s ufeyyeḍ \add zeg\add* usuffeɣ amezwaru n imendi, n binu n jdid d zzect d tamment u zi marra řɣiǧet n yeyyar. Iwyen uřa d řeɛcur zi marra s ufeyyeḍ.
\v 6 Tarwa n Israil d Yahuda, inni izedɣen di tneddam n Yahuda, iwyen uřa d řeɛcur zeg ifunasen u zeg wuǧi uřa d řeɛcur n tewhibin iqeddsen nni tuɣa ssqeddsen i SIDI, AREBBI nsen, uca wcin \add ten\add*, ggin \add zzaysen\add* iɛurrac.
\v 7 Deg uyur wiss třata bdan nitni ad \add zzaysen\add* ggen iɛurrac zi tisi u deg uyur wiss sebɛa kemmřen tt.
\v 8 \add Umi\add* Ḥizqiya d řḥukkam usin-dd u ẓrin iɛurrac nni, barken SIDI d řgens nnes Israil.
\v 9 Isseqsa Ḥizqiya ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen x iɛurrac nni.
\v 10 Ɛazarya, akehhan ameqqran zi taddart n Ṣaduq yarra-dd xas, inna: “Zeg wami dd-nekkar ad nawi tawhibt n usgeɛɛed ɣar Taddart n SIDI, aqa ɣarneɣ min ɣa necc ař tyawant uca ɛad iqqim aṭṭas iceṭṭ, maɣar SIDI ibarek řgens nnes, ařami iqqim řqedd-a n waṭṭas iceṭṭ.”
\m 
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna Ḥizqiya, ad sswejden ixxamen n Taddart n SIDI, u nitni sswejden ten.
\v 12 Nitni ssidfen tawhibt n usgeɛɛed d řeɛcur d tewhibin iqeddsen din s řaman. Kunanya, Alawi, ameḥḍay, d umas Cimɛi, wenni d wiss tnayen, tuɣa aten x man aya \add marra\add*.
\v 13 Yaḥiyil, Ɛazazya, Naḥat, Ɛasa’il, Yarimut, Yuzabad, Iliyil, Yismaxya, Maḥat, Banaya \add tuɣa aten d\add* iweqqafen sadu ufus n Kunanya d Cimɛi, umas, x řumur n ujeǧid Ḥizqiya u n Ɛazarya, ameḥḍay n Taddart n AREBBI.
\v 14 Quri, mmis n Yimna, Alawi, aɛessas n tewwart ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq, \add ittwagg\add* x tewhibin n řxaḍar n AREBBI, ḥima ad ibḍa tawhibt n usgeɛɛed n SIDI d tewhibin iqeddsen qaɛ.
\v 15 Ɛadan, Minyamin, Yecuɛa, Camɛiya, Amarya d Cakunya bedden s řmanet ɣar uɣezdis nnes ɛlaḥṣab tirbiɛin nsen, ḥima ad wezzɛen di tneddam n ikehhanen i aytmatsen, am i imeqqranen, am i imeẓyanen,
\v 16 maca \add war iǧi\add* i yinni ittwazemmemen di lista n jjadira n yeryazen i ɣar iǧa třata n iseggʷusa sennej, aqa marra inni dd-yusin ɣar Taddart n SIDI i řxedmet n kuř ass i wass nni, i řxedmet nsen di tsexxart nsen, ɛlaḥsab tirbiɛin nsen.
\v 17 Azemmen di lista n jjadira n ikehhanen \add tuɣa-t\add* ɛlaḥṣab tudrin n ibabaten nsen, \add maca\add* \add azemmem\add* n Ilawiyyen zi ɛicrin n iseggʷusa sennej, \add tuɣa-t\add* ɛlaḥsab tasexxart nsen, ɛlaḥsab tirbiɛin nsen.
\v 18 \add Nitni wezzɛen\add* i yinni ittwazemmemen di lista n jjadira ak-d marra tarwa nsen d temɣarin nsen d iḥenjiren nsen d tḥenjirin nsen zi marra agraw \add n řgens\add*, maɣar nitni ggin s řaman umi ssqeddsen ixef nsen s tidett.
\v 19 Jar warrawen n Harun, ikehhanen, deg iyyaren n ddmani n tneddam nsen, di kuř tandint, \add tuɣa din\add* iryazen nni ittwazemmemen s ismawen \add nsen\add* ḥima ad wcen tasɣart i marra awtem jar ikehhanen u i marra inni ittwazemmemen di lista n jjadira jar Ilawiyyen.
\m 
\v 20 \add Ammu\add* i igga Ḥizqiya di marra Yahuda. Netta igga min iǧan icnan d iseggden d nican zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnes.
\v 21 Marra řxedmet i ibda di ṭṭweɛ n tsexxart n Taddart n AREBBI u di ṭṭweɛ n Ccariɛa d tewṣeyyet ḥima ad yarzu \add ammu\add* AREBBI, igga i-tt s marra uř nnes uca ifřeḥ.
\b
\b
\c 32
\s1 Ahejjem n Sanḥarib d weɛqeb nnes
\m 
\v 1 Awarni temsarin-a d wescan-a n řaman, yusa-dd Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur. Netta yudef ɣar Yahuda uca inneḍ i tneddam ifaryen, ittɣiř as ad tent iṭṭef i yixef nnes. \x ◘ \xo 32:1 \xt [2 Ij. 18:13-37; 19:1-37; Ica. 36:1-22; 37:1-38]\x*
\v 2 Iẓra Ḥizqiya, aqa Sanḥarib yusa-dd uca inwa ad iḥjem x Urcalim.
\v 3 Netta imcawar ak-d řḥukkam nnes d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt nnes, maḥend ad netyen tařawin n waman barra i tendint, u nitni wcin as afus.
\v 4 Iwyen-dd aṭṭas zi řgens uca netyen marra tařawin uřa d teɣzart i d ittazzřen di řwesṭ n temmurt, nnan: “Mayemmi i dd ɣa yasen ijeǧiden n Accur uca ad afen aṭṭas n waman?”
\v 5 Netta issejhed \add tandint\add*, iɛdeř marra řḥiḍ i tuɣa ittwarẓen d iwetwiten uca yarra i-t ad igeɛɛed ař ṣṣumɛat. U ɣar barra \add iɛdeř ɛad\add* ijj n řḥiḍ nneɣni. Netta issejhed lqelɛa n tendint n Dawud uca igga aṭṭas n lansat d tseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add*.
\v 6 Netta igga ikumandaren n řɛeskarat x řgens uca issmun i-ten ɣares deg wazzay n tewwart n tendint uca issiweř ařami daysen igga uř, inna:
\v 7 “Iřim d iryazen u iřim tmeḥḍem, war ttnexřiɛem zzat i wudem n ujeǧid n Accur uřa zzat i wudem n marra řɣaci nni ɣares iǧan, maɣar \add Wenni\add* ɣarneɣ aqa-t deg waṭṭas x wenni ɣares. \x ◘ \xo 32:7 \xt 2 Ij. 6:16; Yḥ. 16:33; 1 Yḥ. 4:4 \x*
\v 8 Ɣares ijj n uɣiř n weysum \add n bnadem\add*, \add maca\add* ɣarneɣ SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, ḥima ad aneɣ iwc afus u ḥima ad immneɣ amenɣi nneɣ.” Uca řgens ittecceř x wawařen n Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 32:8 \xt Irm. 17:5, 1 Yḥ. 4:4\x*
\b
\m 
\v 9 Awarni man aya issekk Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur, imsexxaren nnes ɣar Urcalim, am tuɣa netta zzat i Laxic d marra řḥukkam nnes akides. \add Issekk i-ten\add* ɣar Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, u ɣar marra \add řgens n\add* Yahuda nni \add iǧan\add* di Urcalim, inna:
\v 10 “Ammu i inna Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur: ‘Min xef tᵉttecřem kenniw, zeɛma kenniw \add tzemmarem\add* ad teqqimem di Urcalim am tᵉttwaḥṣarem?
\v 11 Ma war yarezzu Ḥizqiya ad kenniw iɣwa, ḥima ad kenniw isellem i řmewt zi řaẓ d ufadi xmi iqqar: SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, ad aneɣ ifekk zeg ufus n ujeǧid n Accur!?
\v 12 Ma war ikkis Ḥizqiya nni uřa d řegɛudi nnes d iɛalṭaren nnes, u \add ma war\add* issiweř netta ak-d Yahuda d Urcalim, inna: Mɣir i yijj n uɛalṭar ad tbendqem u ad xas tawyem řebxur!?
\v 13 Ma war tessinem kenniw min ggiɣ necc d řejdud inu s marra řegnus n temmura? Ma fekken irebbiten n řegnus n temmura nni tammurt nsen zeg ufus inu?
\v 14 Man wen zi jar marra irebbiten n řegnus nni x qḍan řejdud inu, tuɣa izemmar ad issenjem řgens nnes zeg ufus inu, ařami AREBBI nwem izemmar ad kenniw ifekk zeg ufus inu?
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, war ttejjim Ḥizqiya ad kenniw icmet u \add war t ttejim\add* ad kenniw issɣekkwi ammu. War tᵉttiqqam ca, maɣar uřa d ijj n arebbi zi man ma řgens niɣ tageldit tuɣa izemmar ad ifekk řgens nnes zeg ufus inu niɣ zeg ufus n řejdud inu. Mecḥař qell ɛad AREBBI nwem ad kenniw ifekk zeg ufus inu!’” \f ◼ \fr 32:15 \fk Ḥazaqiya\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Ḥazaqi-Ya-hu’, min ixs ad yini ‘Arebbi d jjehd inu’.\f*
\m 
\v 16 Uca imsexxaren nnes ssiwřen ɛad ktar ḍidd i SIDI AREBBI u ḍidd i umsexxar nnes Ḥizqiya.
\v 17 Netta yura ɛawed tibratin ḥima ad isseḥqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, u ḥima ad xas issiweř daysent, uca inna: “Am mammec irebbiten n řegnus n temmura, inni war izemmaren ad fekken řgens nsen zeg ufus inu, ammu war izemmar AREBBI n Ḥizqiya ad issenjem řgens nnes zeg ufus inu!”
\v 18 Nitni sɣuyen s jjehd s yiřes n Tyahudect ɣar řgens n Urcalim nni \add ibedden\add* x řḥiḍ ḥima ad ten ssiggʷiden u ad ten ssxarewḍen, maḥend zemmaren ad ṭṭfen tandint.
\v 19 Nitni ssiwřen x AREBBI n Urcalim am x irebbiten n řegnus n \add marra\add* tammurt, inni \add iǧan\add* mɣir řxedmet n iwdan waha.
\m 
\v 20 Ajeǧid Ḥizqiya d unabi Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, ẓẓuǧen x man aya, řaɣan ɣar ujenna.
\v 21 Uca issekk-dd SIDI ijj n lmalak, wenni iqḍan x marra ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen d řḥukkam d imeqqranen di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n ujeǧid n Accur. \add Xenni\add* idweř-dd netta ɣar temmurt nnes s řeḥya x uɣembub. Umi dd-yusa ɣar taddart n arebbi nnes, aqa inni dd-iffɣen zi arrimet nnes, nɣin t s ssif.
\v 22 Ammu i issenjem SIDI Ḥizqiya d imezdaɣ n Urcalim zeg ufus n Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur, u zeg ufus n marra. Netta tuɣa issareyyeḥ i-ten ɣar marra iɣezdisen nsen.
\v 23 Aṭṭas i dd yiwyen tiwhibin ɣar SIDI di Urcalim, uřa d řeqcuɛ iɣřan ɣar Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Ssenni tuɣa ɣares řewqar d ameqqran di tiṭṭawin n marra řegnus.
\b
\s1 Řehřac n Ḥizqiya, asgenfi nnes d řmewt nnes
\m 
\v 24 Deg wussan nni idweř Ḥizqiya ihřec s ijj n řeḥřac ineqqen ařami tuɣa iggur ad immet. Iẓẓuǧ ɣar SIDI u wanita issiweř-dd ɣares uca iwca as-dd ict n řeɛřamet. \x ◘ \xo 32:24 \xt [2 Ij. 20:1-21; Ica. 38:1-22; 39:1-8]\x*
\v 25 \add Maca\add* Ḥizqiya war iggi ɛlaḥsab tcuni i d as ittwassecnen, maɣar uř nnes idweř dayes nnfaxet. \add X uya\add* yusa-dd ijj n uduqqez d ameqqran n weɣḍab xas, x Yahuda u x Urcalim.
\v 26 Ḥizqiya \add maca\add* isswaḍeɛ ixef nnes di ssibbet n nnfaxet n wuř nnes, am netta am yimezdaɣ n Urcalim, ařami aduqqez d ameqqran n weɣḍab n SIDI war xasen dd-yusi deg wussan n Ḥizqiya.
\v 27 Ḥizqiya tuɣa ɣares agřa d ccan s waṭṭas. Netta igga i ixef nnes ixxamen n txubay i nnuqart, i wureɣ, i yeẓra iɣřan, i řeɛṭur, i tseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* u i marra min iǧan d řeqcuɛ iɣřan.
\v 28 \add Igga uřa d\add* tixubay i řɣiǧet n imendi, i binu n jdid d zzect, uřa d řkurit i marra řmař d řeɛraṣi ifaryen i tḥimriwin.
\v 29 Netta igga tineddam i yixef nnes u tuɣa ɣares aṭṭas n wuǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin, maɣar AREBBI tuɣa iwca as ijj n wagřa imɣar aṭṭas.
\v 30 Ḥizqiya wanita tuɣa ɛawed ibelleɛ uffuɣ n waman n \add teɣzart n\add* Jiḥun \add i iǧan\add* sennej qaɛ. Netta yarra aman nican ɣar wadday ɣar řɣarb n tendint n Dawud, maɣar Ḥizqiya tuɣa ifřeḥ di marra min igga.
\v 31 \add Maca\add* zi ssibbet n imendubiyyen n řḥukkam n Babil inni ɣares dd-ittwassekken, ḥima ad sseqsan x řeɛřamet imɣaren tenni tuɣa di temmurt, aqa ijja i-t AREBBI, ḥima ad t iqeǧeb, ḥima ad issen marra \add min iǧan\add* deg wuř nnes. \f ◼ \fr 32:31 \fk imendubiyyen\ft - niɣ ‘ssufara’.\f*
\m 
\v 32 Imezruyen iqqimen n Ḥizqiya d tmexsiwt nnes icewwaren, xzar, aqa man aya \add marra\add* ittwazemmem di řewḥiy n unabi Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, u deg wedlis n ijeǧiden n Yahuda d Israil. \f ◼ \fr 32:32 \fk Ḥazaqiya\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Ḥazaqi-Ya-hu’, min ixs ad yini ‘Arebbi d jjehd inu’.\f*
\v 33 Ḥizqiya igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Neḍřen t \add deg wenḍeř\add* yuɛřan qaɛ n imeḍřan n warrawen n Dawud. Marra Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim ssecnen as řewqar ɣar řmewt nnes. Mmis Manassa idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 33
\s1 Řeḥkamet iɛeffnen n Manassi, ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Manassa \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tenɛac n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem xemsa u-xemsin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 33:1 \xt [2 Ij. 21:1-18]\x*
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, am jjɛayef n řegnus nni tuɣa issuffeɣ SIDI zi zzat n wudem n ayt n Israil zi řwart nsen.
\v 3 Netta ibda ad iɛdeř řegɛudi nni tuɣa ihdem babas Ḥizqiya. Netta issbedd iɛalṭaren i ‘Ibaɛlen’ uca igga tirebbin n cwarti uca ibendeq zzat i marra řɛeskar n ujenna uca iɛbed asen.
\v 4 Issbedd ɛawed iɛalṭaren di Taddart n SIDI i x inna SIDI: “Di Urcalim \add ad ssmetneɣ\add* Isem inu i řebda.”
\v 5 Netta ibna \add ɛawed\add* iɛalṭaren i marra řɛeskar n ujenna di tnayen n řemraḥat n Taddart n SIDI.
\v 6 Netta ijja ad kken iḥenjiren nnes di tmessi di Teɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum, igga s tbezgiwt d tgezzant d tseḥḥart, u yiwi-dd inni issawařen ak-d imettan d igezzanen. Igga aṭṭas min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI maḥend ad t isɛar.
\v 7 Issbedd ijj n řexyař ineqcen nni igga di Taddart n AREBBI, i x tuɣa inna AREBBI i Dawud u i mmis Suliman: “Di Taddart-a u di Urcalim, tenni farzeɣ zi marra tiqebbař n Israil, ad ssmetneɣ Isem inu i řebda.
\v 8 Necc war ttejjiɣ aḍar n Israil ad ittwakkes ɛad zi temmurt nni uriɣ i řejdud nwem, mařa nitni mɣir ad ḥḍan marra min i d asen umureɣ maḥend ad t ggen, ɛlaḥsab marra Ccariɛa d marra tiweṣṣa d marra lfarayiḍ \add nni d asen immewcen\add* s ufus n Musa.”
\v 9 Manassa ijja Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim ad weddaren, ařami ggin d aɛeffan x řegnus i x tuɣa iqḍa SIDI zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil.
\m 
\v 10 \add Iwa,\add* SIDI tuɣa issiweř i Manassa u i řgens nnes, maca nitni war d as wcin ca taynit.
\v 11 SIDI issekk ɣarsen ikumandaren n řɛeskar n ujeǧid n Accur. Nitni ḥebbsen Manassa s tsennarin, carfen t s tnayen n ssnaseř n nnḥas uca jjin t ad yuyur \add ammu\add* ɣar Babil.
\v 12 Umi t iḥṣar Netta ammu, izaweg wanita zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, u isswaḍeɛ ixef nnes ař ṭṭarf zzat i wudem n AREBBI n řejdud nnes.
\v 13 Iẓẓuǧ ɣares uca Netta ijja ad issarḍa Ixef nnes zzayes s tẓaǧit yuǧɣen nnes u yarra i-t-i-dd ɣar Urcalim. \add Xenni\add* issen Manassa, aqa SIDI d AREBBI.
\v 14 Awarni uya ibna řḥiḍ n barra i tendint n Dawud, ɣar uɣezdis n řɣarb n Jiḥun di teɣzurt, u \add ibna i-t\add* ař Tawwart n Iseřman, iquwwar \add řḥiḍ\add* uřa d Ɛufil uca issgeɛɛed \add Manassi\add* řḥiḍ aṭṭas. Igga uřa d ikumandaren n řɛeskar di marra tineddam ifaryen n Yahuda.
\v 15 Netta ikkes irebbiten iɣriben d řexyař n ṣṣanam zi Taddart n SIDI uřa d marra iɛalṭaren nni tuɣa ibna x wedrar n Taddart n SIDI di Urcalim, uca immenḍar i-ten barra i tendint.
\v 16 Netta igga \add ɛawed\add* aɛalṭar n SIDI uca iqeddem xas tiwhibin n řehna d tewhibin n uqadi uca inna i \add ayt n\add* Yahuda ad ɛebden SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 17 Maca řgens yarni ɛad yiwi tiɣarṣa x řegɛudi, maca mɣir i SIDI, AREBBI nsen, waha.
\m 
\v 18 Imezruyyen iqqimen n Manassa d tẓaǧit nnes ɣar AREBBI nnes uřa d awařen n imwařawen nni ɣares issiwřen deg Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, xzar, man aya \add marra ittwazemmem\add* deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil.
\v 19 Taẓaǧit nnes d mammec ijja \add AREBBI\add* ad ittwasseṣřeḥ Ixef nnes s tẓaǧit yuǧɣen nnes, uřa d marra ddnub nnes d řeɣdar nnes d imucan mani ibna řegɛudi u issbedd tirebbin n cwarti d řexyařat ineqcen qbeř ma ittwasswaḍeɛ, xzar, man aya \add marra\add* ittwazemmem deg wawařen n imwařawen.
\v 20 Manassa igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Neḍřen t di taddart nnes. Mmis Amun idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\s1 Amun, ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 21 Amun \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tnayen u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tnayen n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 33:21 \xt [2 Ij. 21:19-26]\x*
\v 22 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, \add nican\add* am mammec t igga babas Manassa. Amun iqeddem tiɣarṣa i marra řexyařat ineqcen i tuɣa igga babas Manassa uca isexxar asen.
\v 23 Netta war isswaḍeɛ ixef nnes zzat i wudem n SIDI, am mammec isswaḍeɛ babas Manassa ixef nnes, maca Amun wanita yarni \add waha\add* deg umarwas.
\v 24 Imsexxaren nnes ggin xas ict n tmeɛmuč uca nɣin t di taddart nnes.
\v 25 Řgens n temmurt \add maca\add* nɣin marra inni tuɣa iggin tameɛmuč x ujeǧid Amun. Řgens n temmurt ggin mmis Yuciya d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \f ◼ \fr 33:25 \fk Yuciya\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Yuci-Yahu’. Isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘D wenni i issgenfa i-t SIDI’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 34
\s1 Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Yuciya \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tmenya n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem waḥit u-třatin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 34:1 \xt [2 Ij. 22:1-20]\x*
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta yuyur deg ibriden n babas Dawud, war iffiɣ \add x webrid\add* \add řa ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ.
\v 3 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenya n řeḥkamet nnes, umi t tuɣa ɛad d aḥudri, ibda ad yarzu x AREBBI n babas Dawud. Deg useggʷas wiss tenɛac ibda ad issizdeg Yahuda d Urcalim zi řegɛudi, zi trebbin n cwarti u zi řexyařat ineqcen d řexyařat ifesyen.
\v 4 Zzat i tiṭṭawin nnes hedmen iɛalṭaren n ‘Ibaɛlen’, uca izdem netta ipilaren n arebbi n tfuct nni xasen dd-ibanen sennej. Tirebbin n cwarti d řexyařat ineqcen d řexyařat ifesyen yarẓa i-ten di iwetwiten uca iddez i-ten u taɛejjajt nsen yareyyec i-tt x imeḍřan n yinni tuɣa d asen dd-yiwyen taɣarṣt.
\v 5 Issarɣ iɣsan n ikehhanen x iɛalṭaren nsen. \add Ammu\add* i issizdeg Yahuda d Urcalim.
\v 6 Uřa ɣar tneddam n Manassa d Ifrayim d Cimɛun, \add wah,\add* ař Naftali, ɣar marra iɣezdisen n imucan nsen ittwareddǧen,
\v 7 ihdem iɛalṭaren. Netta iřbez tirebbin n cwarti d řexyařat ineqcen, iddez i-tent, uca izdem \add ɛawed\add* marra ipilaren n arebbi n tfuct di marra Israil. Awarni uya iɛqeb-dd ɣar Urcalim.
\m 
\v 8 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenṭac n řeḥkamet nnes, awarni řami issizdeg tammurt d Taddart, issekk netta Cafan, mmis n Aṣalya, d Maɛasiya, ameqqran n tendint, d Yuwax, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz, amarir n umezruy, ḥima ad ɛedřen Taddart n SIDI, AREBBI nnes. \f ◼ \fr 34:8 \fk Aṣalya\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Aṣal-Yahu’. \fk Maɛasiya\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Maɛasi-Yahu’.\f*
\v 9 Nitni usin-dd ɣar Ḥilqiya, arrays n ikehhanen, u wcin as nnuqart i dd-ittwawyen di Taddart n AREBBI, d tenni dd-yarwen Ilawiyyen nni tuɣa iɛessen ɣar wadaf, zeg ufus n Manassa d Ifrayim, zi marra min iqqimen n Israil, zi marra Yahuda d Binyamin u zi marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim.
\v 10 Nitni wcin tt deg ufus n yinni tuɣa iggin řxedmet, inni \add iǧan\add* x Taddart n SIDI, uca ina wcin tt i yinni iggin řxedmet di Taddart n SIDI, maḥend ad ɛedřen u ad ssjehden Taddart.
\v 11 Nitni wcin tt i iḥrayfiyyen u i imaṣṣuten i tmesɣiwt n tṣuḍar ittwassuydan u \add i tmesɣiwt\add* n ukeccuḍ i tḥenya n uɛarreḍ, maḥend ad ggen tiɣurfin i tudrin, tinni ijjin ijeǧiden n Yahuda ad arxun.
\v 12 Iryazen xedmen s řaman. Yaḥat d Ɛubadya, Ilawiyyen zeg iḥenjiren n Marari, tuɣa aten d iweqqafen xasen, uřa d Zakariyya d Macullam zeg iḥenjiren n Quḥat, ḥima ad seyyaren. Ilawiyyen, marra tuɣa ttḥakan di dduzanat n lmusiqa,
\v 13 \add tuɣa aten ɛawed\add* x yinni yarebbun řeḥmeř. Nitni d imseyyaren i marra inni tuɣa ixeddmen di řexdayem ifarzen. \add Ttwařeqqmen\add* zeg Ilawiyyen uřa d imariren d imeḥḍayen d iɛessasen n tewwura.
\m 
\v 14 \add Umi\add* ksin \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart nni tuɣa dd-iwyen di Taddart n SIDI, yufa ukehhan Ḥilqiya adlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n SIDI, \add i tuɣa d asen immewcen\add* x ufus n Musa.
\v 15 Ḥilqiya iṭṭef deg wawař, inna i umarir Cafan: “Necc ufiɣ adlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa di Taddart n SIDI.” Uca iwca Ḥilkiya adlis i Cafan.
\v 16 Cafan yiwi adlis ɣar ujeǧid. Netta ixebbar ajeǧid, inna: “Marra min umuren i imsexxaren nnec, aqa tteggen t.
\v 17 Nitni ssfarrɣen \add temnyat n\add* nnuqart i ufin di Taddart n SIDI uca wcin tent deg ufus n iweqqafen u n yinni itteggen řxedmet.”
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* iḥaja umarir Cafan i ujeǧid \add ammu\add*, inna: “Akehhan Ḥilqiya iwca ayi ijj n wedlis!” Cafan iɣra zzayes x ujeǧid.
\v 19 Umi isřa ujeǧid awařen n Ccariɛa, imsar, icarreg netta arruḍ nnes.
\v 20 Yumur ujeǧid i Ḥilqiya u i Axiqam, mmis n Cafan, u i Ɛabdun, mmis n Mixa, u i umarir Cafan i Ɛasaya, amsexxar n ujeǧid, inna:
\v 21 “Uyurem, seqsam SIDI di ṭṭweɛ inu u di ṭṭweɛ n min iqqimen di Israil u di Yahuda x wawařen n wedlis i ittwafen. Maɣar asɛar n SIDI nni xaneɣ ittwazeǧɛen, aqa-t d ameqqran, minzi řejdud nneɣ war ḥḍin ca awař n SIDI, ḥima ad ggen am mammec marra min yurin deg wedlis ittwannḍen.”
\m 
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* yuyur Ḥilqiya ak-d yinni \add ittwassekken\add* zeg ujeǧid ɣar tnabit Xulda, tamɣart n Callum, mmis n Tuqahat, mmis n Ḥasra, wenni ibedden x řehri n warruḍ. Nettat tezdeɣ deg wezyen nneɣni n Urcalim uca ssiwřen akides x man aya.
\v 23 Nettat tenna asen: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Inim i weryaz nni kenniw ɣari dd-issekken:
\v 24 ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Xzar Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ tuɛeffna x wemcan-a u x imezdaɣ nnes, marra nnɛaři i yurin deg wedlis nni zzayes ittwaɣaren zzat i wudem n ujeǧid n Yahuda,
\v 25 maɣar nitni ḥeyyden xafi u iwyen tiwhibin n řebxur i irebbiten nneɣni ařami d ayi sɛaren s marra řexdayem n ifassen nsen. Asɛar inu ad ittwazeǧeɛ x wemcan-a u war ixessi.
\v 26 \add Maca\add* i ujeǧid n Yahuda, wenni kenniw dd-issekken da, ḥima ad tesseqsam SIDI, ad as tinim: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: X wawařen nni tesřid:
\v 27 Maɣar idweř wuř nnec yarḍeb u tesswaḍɛed ixef nnec zzat i wudem n AREBBI umi tesřid i wawařen nnes x wemcan-a u x imezdaɣ nnes, u umi tesswaḍɛed ixef nnec uca tcarrged arruḍ nnec u trud zzat i wudem inu, s uya sřiɣ Necc ɛawed ɣarek, iqqar SIDI.
\v 28 Xzar, ad cek ssmuneɣ ɣar řejdud nnec u ad tᵉttwassarsed deg wenḍeř nnec s řehna u tiṭṭawin nnec war ttwiřint ca marra tuɛeffna nni ɣa ssiwḍeɣ x wemcan-a u x imezdaɣ nnes.’” Nitni ɛawden awař-a i ujeǧid.
\m 
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* issekk ujeǧid \add ireqqasen\add* uca issmun marra imeqqranen n Yahuda d Urcalim.
\v 30 Igeɛɛed ujeǧid ɣar Taddart n SIDI ak-d marra iryazen n Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim, ak-d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen u ak-d marra řgens, zeg umeqqran ař ameẓyan, u ɣrin xasen marra awařen n wedlis n Řɛahd nni tuɣa ittwafen di Taddart n SIDI.
\v 31 Ajeǧid ibedd deg wemcan nnes uca iqqen Řɛahd zzat i wudem n SIDI, ḥima ad iḍfar SIDI u ḥima ad iḥḍa řumurat nnes d cchadat nnes d tweṣṣa nnes s marra wuř nnes u s marra řeɛmar nnes u ḥima ad igg awařen n Řɛahd-a i yurin deg wedlis-a.
\v 32 Netta ijja marra inni iǧan di Urcalim d Binyamin, ad kkaren \add ḥima ad t ssmetnen\add* uca imezdaɣ n Urcalim ggin ɛlaḥsab Řɛahd n AREBBI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen.
\v 33 Ikkes Yuciya marra jjɛayef \add n ṣṣanam\add* zi temmura n ayt n Israil u yarra marra inni \add izedɣen\add* di Israil ttsexxaren i tsexxart n SIDI, AREBBI nsen. Marra ussan \add n tudart\add* nnes war ḥeyyden ca zeg weḍfar n SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen. \f ◼ \fr 34:33 \fk Yuciya\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Yuci-Yahu’. Isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘D wenni i issgenfa i-t SIDI’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 35
\s1 Ajeǧid Yuciya iɛeyyed Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n Useɛdu
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* igga Yuciya \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i SIDI di Urcalim. Ɣarṣen i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu deg wass wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur amezwaru. \x ◘ \xo 35:1 \xt [2 Ij. 23:21-23]\x*
\v 2 Netta issbedd ikehhanen ɣar imucan n tɛessast nsen uca igga daysen uř ɣar řxedmet di Taddart n SIDI.
\v 3 Inna i Ilawiyyen, inni isseřmaden marra Israil, inni tuɣa iqeddsen i SIDI: “Sarsem Ttabut iqeddsen di Taddart nni ibna Suliman, mmis n Dawud, ajeǧid n Israil. War d awem ittxeṣṣa \add ɛad\add* ad tarbum ddqeř x tɣarḍin nwem. Sexxarem řexxu i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, u i řgens nnes Israil.
\v 4 Swejdem ixef nwem, \add am tᵉttwasettfem\add* ɛlaḥsab tudrin n ibabaten nwem, ɛlaḥsab tirbiɛin nwem, am mammec tt yura Dawud, ajeǧid n Israil, u am mammec tt yura mmis Suliman.
\v 5 Sbeddem ixef nwem di Zzawect Iqeddsen, \add am tᵉttwasettfem kenniw\add* ɛlaḥsab tirbiɛin n řaǧat n ibabaten, zzat i tawmat nwem, ayt n řgens, \add am tᵉttwasettfem\add* ɛlaḥsab asettef n řaǧat n jjed n Ilawiyyen. \f ◼ \fr 35:5 \fk řgens\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘iḥenjiren n řgens’ niɣ ‘arrawen n řgens’.\f*
\v 6 Ɣarṣem i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu u sqeddsem ixef nwem. Swejdem tt i aytmatwem, maḥend ad ggen ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI \add i immewcen\add* s tsexxart n Musa.”
\m 
\v 7 Iwca Yuciya uǧi, izmaren d imuyan imeẓyanen i tarwa n řgens. Marra aya tuɣa i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i marra inni din iǧan. Tuɣa řqedd nsen třatin-ařef, u \add xenni ɛawed\add* teřt-ařaf n ifunasen d tfunasin. Marra aya i dd-yusin zeg wagřa n ujeǧid.
\v 8 Wcin řḥukkam nnes ict n tewhibt n usgeɛɛed am tewhibt s řxaḍar i řgens, i ikehhanen u i Ilawiyyen. Ḥilqiya, Zakariyya d Yaḥiyil, imeḥḍayen n Taddart n AREBBI, wcin i ikehhanen i \add Tɣarṣa n\add* Useɛdu ařfayen u-setta-mya zeg wuǧi u \add sennej man aya ɛad\add* teřt-mya n ifunasen d tfunasin.
\m 
\v 9 Kunanya, Camɛiya d Nataniyil, aytmas, d Ḥacabya, Yaɛiyil d Yuzabad, imeqqranen n Ilawiyyen, wcin i Ilawiyyen i \add Tɣarṣa n\add* Useɛdu xemsa-ařaf zeg wuǧi u \add xenni\add* xemsa-mya n ifunasen d tfunasin.
\m 
\v 10 \add Ammu i\add* sswejden i řxedmet. Ikehhanen tuɣa bedden deg wemcan nsen u Ilawiyyen di terbiɛin nsen, ɛlaḥsab řumur n ujeǧid.
\v 11 Nitni ɣarṣen i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu uca ikehhanen zeǧɛen idammen zeg ifassen nsen, u kksen Ilawiyyen \add zzaysent\add* iřmawen.
\v 12 Nitni ḥuzen \add iziynat i\add* tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ ḥima ad asen \add tent\add* wcen, i řefruɛ n řaǧat n ibabaten, i warrawen n řgens, ḥima ad tent wehhben d taɣarṣt i SIDI, am mammec tura deg wedlis n Musa uca ammu \add i iggin\add* ak-d ifunasen d tfunasin.
\v 13 Xenni cenfen \add Taɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu tiwa i tmessi am mammec teǧa di lqaɛida. Iziynat iqeddsen nneɣni cenfen ten di marmitat d iṭenjiren d tiqsiřin uca iwyen \add tent\add* deɣya ɣar marra řgens. \x ◘ \xo 35:13 \xt Uf. 12:9\x*
\v 14 Awarni aya sswejden uřa i yixef nsen u i ikehhanen, maɣar ikehhanen, arrawen n Harun, tuɣa řhan ak-d uwehheb n tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tadunt ař ǧiřet. \add Awarni aya\add* sswejden Ilawiyyen i yixef nsen u i ikehhanen, arrawen n Harun.
\m 
\v 15 Imedyazen, iḥenjiren n Asaf, \add tuɣa bedden\add* deg wemcan nsen, ɛlaḥsab řumur n Dawud, Asaf, Hayman d Yadutun, amwařaw n ujeǧid, uca iɛessasen n tewwura \add bedden\add* ɣar kuř tawwart. Tuɣa war ittxeṣṣi ad jjen řxedmet nsen, maɣar aytmatsen, Ilawiyyen, sswejden asen \add Taɣarṣt n Useɛdu\add*.
\m 
\v 16 Marra tasexxart n SIDI teɛdeř \add mliḥ\add* deg wass nni i uḥeṭṭu \add n Řɛid\add* n \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu u i uwehheb n tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ x uɛalṭar n SIDI ɛlaḥsab řumur n ujeǧid Yuciya.
\v 17 Ayt n Israil, inni \add din\add* iǧan, sswejden i \add Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu deg wass nni, u sebɛa n wussan \add ggin nitni\add* Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun.
\v 18 War din tuɣi di Israil bu \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu am wa zeg wussan n unabi Camwil. Uřa d ijjen zeg ijeǧiden n Israil war iggi \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu am mammec t igga Yuciya ak-d ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen u ak-d marra Yahuda d Israil, nni \add din\add* iǧan, u ak-d imezdaɣ n Urcalim.
\v 19 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenṭac n tgelda n Yuciya ittwagg \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu wanita.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Awarni marra aya, umi ikemmeř Yuciya Taddart, iffeɣ-dd Naxu, ajeǧid n Miṣra, ɣar Lfuraṭ ḥima ad immneɣ ak-d Karkamic. Uca Yuciya iffeɣ-dd i umsagar akides.
\v 21 Naxu issekk-dd ɣares ireqqasen, inna: “Min din jar ayi-dd d cek, \add a\add* ajeǧid n Yahuda? War iǧi ɣarek i dd ffɣeɣ ass-a, maca ɣar ict n taddart \add nneɣni\add* tenni ittmenɣan akidi. Inna ayi AREBBI ittxeṣṣa ayi ad qeǧqeɣ. S uya ḥeyyed x AREBBI, wenni akidi iǧan, niɣ ad cek yareddeǧ.”
\v 22 \add Maca\add* Yuciya war issneqřeb aɣembub nnes zzayes, maca igga ixef nnes war iǧi d netta ḥima akides immneɣ, u netta war isři ɣar wawařen n Naxu \add inni dd yusin\add* zeg uqemmum n AREBBI, maca yusa-dd ɣar umenɣi di teɣzurt n Majiddu.
\v 23 Maca imjebbaden n řqews řeqfen ajeǧid Yuciya. \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid i imsexxaren nnes: “Nedhem ayi ssenni, maɣar yezmeɣ aṭṭas!”
\v 24 Imsexxaren nnes ksin t deg ukarru uca nedhen t deg ijj n ukarru nneɣni nni ɣares iǧa, uca iwyen t ɣar Urcalim. Immut \add dinni\add* uca neḍřen t deg imeḍřan n řejdud nnes. Marra Yahuda d Urcalim ceḍnen x Yuciya.
\v 25 Igga Irmiya ict n yezři n wecḍan x Yuciya. Ař ass-a marra imedyazen d tmedyazin ssawařen x Yuciya deg izřan nsen n wecḍan, minzi nitni ggin tt d ict n tewṣeyyet di Israil. Xzar, aqa-ten ttwazemmemen deg Izřan s Igejduren.
\m 
\v 26 Imezruyen i iqqimen n Yuciya d tmexsiwt nnes icewwaren ɛlaḥsab min yurin di Ccariɛa n SIDI,
\v 27 \add wah,\add* imezruyen nnes, imezwura d ineggura, aqa ttwazemmemen deg wedlis n ijeǧiden n Israil d Yahuda.
\b
\b
\c 36
\s1 Yahuyaḥaz, ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Ksin řgens n temmurt Yahuyaḥaz, mmis n Yuciya, uca ggin t d ajeǧid di Urcalim deg wemcan n babas.\x ◘ \xo 36:1 \xt [2 Ij. 23:31-35]\x*
\v 2 Yahuyaḥaz \add tuɣa\add* ɣares třata u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa, umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem třata n iyuren di Urcalim.
\v 3 Ajeǧid n Miṣra ikkes i-t \add d ajeǧid\add* zi Urcalim uca igga i temmurt ijj n multa n mya talint n nnuqart d ict n talint n wureɣ.
\v 4 Ajeǧid n Miṣra igga umas Alyaqim d ajeǧid x Yahuda d Urcalim. Netta ibeddeř isem nnes ɣar Yahuyaqim. \add Maca\add* umas Yahuyaḥaz iṭṭef i-t Naxu uca yiwyi i-t ɣar Miṣra.
\b
\s1 Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 5 Yahuyaqim \add tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem ḥiṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nnes. \x ◘ \xo 36:5 \xt [2 Ij. 23:36-37; 24:1-7]\x*
\v 6 Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, iffeɣ \add i umenɣi\add* akides uca icarf i-t s tnayen n ssnaseř n nnuqart, ḥima ad t yawi ɣar Babil.
\v 7 Yiwi Nabuxadnaṣṣar uřa d \add ijj n wezyen\add* n řeqcuɛ zi Taddart n SIDI ɣar Babil uca issars i-ten di zzawect nnes di Babil.
\v 8 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yahuyaqim d jjɛayef i igga u min ittwafen ḍidd nnes, xzar, \add marra\add* aya ittwazemmem deg wedlis n ijeǧiden n Israil d Yahuda. Mmis Yahuyakin idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\s1 Yahuyakin, ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 9 Yahuyakin \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tmenṭac n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem třata n iyuren d ɛecra n wussan di Urcalim. Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 36:9 \xt [2 Ij. 24:8-17]\x*
\v 10 Ɣar ubeddeř n useggʷas ijja ujeǧid Nabuxadnaṣṣar ad t yawi ɣar Babil s řeqcuɛ iɣřan zi Taddart n SIDI. Netta igga umas Ṣidqiya d ajeǧid x Yahuda d Urcalim.
\b
\s1 Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, di tmeḥbast ɣar Babil
\m 
\v 11 Ṣidqiya tuɣa ɣares waḥit u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem ḥiṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 36:11 \xt [2 Ij. 24:18-20; 25:1-12; Irm. 52:1-30]\x*
\v 12 Igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, war isswaḍeɛ ixef nnes zzat i wudem n unabi Irmiya \add wenni issiwřen\add* x řumur n SIDI.
\v 13 Uřa d netta iɣewweɣ x ujeǧid Nabuxadnaṣṣar, wenni t ijjin ad ijjaǧ ɣar AREBBI. Netta issemḥeḍ iri nnes uca isseqseḥ uř nnes maḥend war dd-iddikkʷiř ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 14 U marra imeqqranen n ikehhanen uřa d řgens ruḥen, aggʷejen aṭṭas di řeɣdar nsen, \add ggin\add* am mammec marra jjɛayef n řegnus. Nitni ssxemjen Taddart n SIDI tenni tuɣa issqeddes di Urcalim.
\m 
\v 15 SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen issekk-dd ɣarsen \add inehharen\add* s ufus n ireqqasen nnes, řexxu niɣ řexmin, maɣar Netta tuɣa izziǧiz as řgens nnes d Tzeddiɣt nnes.
\v 16 Maca nitni stehzan zeg ireqqasen n AREBBI u sseḥqaren awařen nnes. Nitni ggin taḍṣa x inabiyyen nnes, ařami isɛar SIDI x řgens nnes u war iqqim ɛad usgenfu.
\v 17 Netta igga ajeǧid n Ikaldaniyyen ad ɣarsen dd-iffeɣ, wenni inɣin iḥudriyyen nsen s ssif di Taddart n Zzawect nsen Iqeddsen. Netta war issɛizz x iḥudriyyen niɣ x teɛzariyyin uřa x iwessura d imeccaybuten. AREBBI iwca i-ten marra deg ufus nnes.
\v 18 Marra řeqcuɛ n Taddart n AREBBI, \add řeqcuɛ\add* imeqqranen d imeẓyanen, uřa d txubay n Taddart n SIDI d txubay n ujeǧid d řḥukkam nnes, aqa marra aya yiwyi i-t ɣar Babil.
\v 19 Nitni sscemḍen Taddart n AREBBI, hedmen řḥiḍ n Urcalim uca qqden marra řeqṣur nnes s tmessi u areddǧen marra řeqcuɛ iɣřan aṭṭas zzayes.
\v 20 Wi iqqimen zi ssif indeh i-ten ɣar lmenfa ɣar Babil, uca dewřen nitni d imsexxaren i netta u i iḥenjiren nnes ař řeḥkamet n tgeldit n Lfurs,
\v 21 - ḥima ad ittwasseqfeř wawař n SIDI \add i issiweř\add* s uqemmum n Irmiya - ařami teksi tammurt \add iseggʷusa nnes\add* n ssebt. Marra ussan n wareddeǧ tuɣa tammurt tareyyeḥ, ařami kemmřen sebɛin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 36:21 \xt Ɛiz. 1:1-3, Irm. 25:12, 29:10, Dan. 9:2\x*
\b
\s1 Aɛqab n řgens s ufus n Kurac
\m 
\v 22 \add Maca\add* deg useggʷas amezwaru n ujeǧid Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs - ḥima ad ittwakemmeř wawař n SIDI s uqemmum n Irmiya - issekkar-dd SIDI buḥbeř n Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs, uca ijja wanita ad dd-iffeɣ ijj n ubarreḥ di marra tageldit nnes, uřa di tira, maḥend ad yini: \x ◘ \xo 36:22 \xt [Ɛiz. 1:1-3; Irm. 25:12; 29:10; Dan. 9:2]\x*
\v 23 “Ammu i iqqar Kurac, ajeǧid n Lfurs: ‘SIDI, AREBBI n ijenwan, iwca ayi marra tigeldiwin n temmurt uca Netta igga xafi ad bniɣ ict n Taddart i Netta di Urcalim di Yahuda. Ejj ad igeɛɛed qaɛ man wen zzaywem zi marra řgens nnes! Ad yiři SIDI, AREBBI nnes, akides!’” 
